en_US_description: In pure, soft cashmere, the Reykjavik scarf is a luxurious way to wrap up in cold weather. Woven using a jacquard technique to reproduce Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, it is available in grey with fluorescent pink or red with beige. Its generous dimensions also make it perfect for travel.

For Fall-Winter 2018, the Very Zipped Tote handbag takes on an autumnal feel. Made from khaki-green leather with eggshell-color details, it is accented with silver-color hardware. The delicately braided edges are the embodiment of Louis Vuitton craftsmanship and style.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The PM model has a detachable strap for cross-body carry.

With its subtle tone-on-tone Monogram pattern in classic navy blue, the Nightfall stole is an elegant choice for evening or any special occasion. Woven of pure, luxurious cashmere yarns, the fabric is brushed for an extremely soft finish.

Suitable both for business and special occasions, this easy-going tie is available in a broad range of colour options. The Maison's iconic Monogram motif is reproduced as a printed pattern, giving the appearance of a woven tie.

The House continues to reveal new facets of Vernis leather with an unexpected reinterpretation of one of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic shapes: the Alma BB. The audacious color and Monogram canvas trim gives it a stunningly disruptive feel.
The compact, Rivets Chain wallet boasts an array of practical features, including credit card slots, a coin compartment and a removable chain with a key holder.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in emblematic Epi leather with a colorful bonded lining, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.

The textured background of this pure-silk jacquard tie creates a tone-on-tone check, overlaid with a subtle pattern of Monogram Flowers and LV initials. Cut with a classic 8cm blade, in Navy, Grey or Medium Blue, it enhances business or formal attire.

An update on an iconic piece, the LV Chain bracelet has been refreshed for the new season. The hardware features the Louis Vuitton signature, meticulously etched on both sides. The metal chain has an aged silver-color finish, and the bracelet is available in two classic hues for a timeless look.

The ladylike Cherrywood PM in glossy patent leather features a top handle and removable strap trimmed with Monogram canvas. A fashionable daily companion, it opens wide for easy access to the roomy interior. An embossed LV logo and heritage tuck lock are discreet yet distinctive signatures.

The Pop Monogram Square in pure silk presents the season’s fresh twist on the iconic pattern. The central Monogram Flower is composed of a playful mix of straps, chains and locks – all historic House leatherwork signatures. Stripes and dots add a modern touch to this on-trend screen-printed scarf, an ideal gift for Monogram fans.

The Confidential Monogram shawl features Louis Vuitton's hallmark Monogram motif and a bold pattern of chains, locks and straps. A subtle allover tone-on-tone print is incorporated into the lively design. This effortlessly elegant shawl, woven from a delicate cotton and silk blend, is of generous proportions, making it perfect for a variety of looks.

These square LV Player sunglasses present a sporty look with their laminated acetate frames, brow bar and two-tone color. Nods to the House's hallmarks include the Damier signature engraved on the temples and tips, a Louis Vuitton signature on the side and LV Initials on the lenses. Solid-colored sun lenses complete this elegant design.

This special edition of the Victorine wallet belongs to the seasonal Wild theme, which brings together leopard print - a focus of Nicolas Ghesquière's Prefall 2018 collection for Louis Vuitton - with Monogram canvas and corduroy-effect leather. With its neat proportions and distinctive envelope-style flap, this is the perfect compact wallet for every day.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Damier Ebene canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

A tribute to the House's iconic creations, the Jeu de Louis BB Bandeau scarf features a motif of instantly recognizable accessories spanning Louis Vuitton history. Vivid colorways and a board-game-style print make for a playful piece crafted from pure silk. Art nouveau and Monogram Flowers inspired by the Asnières house add a romantic touch to the slim scarf.

This season, the ultra-compact Zippy Coin Purse comes in Monogram canvas ornamented with playful stickers, evoking turn-of-the-last-century travel with its steam ships and Louis Vuitton trunks. The compact interior holds all the essentials – small change, credit cards and bills – while a zip-around closure keeps them safe.
Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format. It is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men.

The Essential V chain necklace takes its inspiration from the graphic V motif which Nicolas Ghesquière introduced at his first runway show for Louis Vuitton. This now iconic signature is interpreted in colored lacquer and decorated with studs referencing the House's historic trunks. The delicate chain is finished with a clasp and LV Circle ornament.

Landscape emerged as a major theme for Fall-Winter 2018 menswear. The mysterious, mineral-gray pattern is transposed to this Monogram Landscape stole, an enveloping piece crafted from a blend of cashmere and silk yarns. Both soft and warm, it is a stylish choice for warding off chills, from mid-season through winter.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern forms the background of this elegant stole with an intriguing fade-out effect. Its generous dimensions make it easy to style in different ways, while its airy blend of silk and cotton is ideal for mid-season.

The LV Circle reversible belt presents two different looks, each with a statement-making effect. On one side is the House's iconic Monogram canvas, with solid-colored calf leather on the other. It features a round brass buckle with a mirrored plaque and an LV Circle logo in either a gold- or silver-tone finish.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, this stylish stole combines the iconic Damier pattern with a playful palm tree print and rainbow Louis Vuitton signature. Its generous dimensions and airy blend of silk and cotton make it a versatile piece, ideal for mid-season.

In calf-lined Monogram canvas or punchy red Epi leather, the new Crazy In Lock bracelet wears a charming heart-shaped padlock, finely engraved with the LV Circle signature.  This feminine, collectible piece makes a most romantic little gift.

This extra-long silk bandeau presents a new print: signature Malletage combines with Monogram Flowers and LV initials for a slim scarf with on-trend attitude. The black-and-red version is accented with a Monogram allover; the light-pink model features classic Damier check.

The House makes a fresh fashion statement with new Monogram Blossom: flowers of smooth calfskin decorate the iconic canvas for an artful, feminine effect. With its chain strap and gleaming transformable lock, this model takes an outfit from desk to dinner.

From the exclusive capsule collection, the Vivienne stole is woven of luxurious cashmere and silk yarns. The mascot’s playful image is set against a background of Monogram Eclipse, a pattern featured on this season’s men’s leather goods. Signed “Louis Vuitton Forever,” the stole is available in pop-up stores only.

Pop Art-inspired iconographic patches give the LV Stories BB bandeau an eye-catching finish. Sprinkled with distinctive House emblems, including the Monogram Flower and the trunk padlocks, this piece blends the classic with the contemporary. This playful theme appears across the Leather Goods, Shoes and Accessories lines.

Inspired by historic Louis Vuitton signatures, the Bangle Family bracelets are available in three different shapes, widths and finishes. They can be collected and coordinated to create an entirely personal look. This medium square bangle with a silver color is debossed with the iconic Monogram pattern. Its hinged design makes it easy to open and close.

The Graceful MM looks fresh and feminine in supple Damier Azur canvas. This spacious hobo has a lightweight, body-friendly design that makes it perfect for every day. The flat handle sits easily on the shoulder, while emblematic details, such as the leather name tag, reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Crafted from a silk-wool blend, the Sparkle LV Monogram shawl is a sophisticated design. Embroidered Monogram Flowers decorate each corner, embellished with a dash of sequins and beads for a jewel-like finish. The generous proportions of the shawl make it a versatile piece, which can be worn over the shoulders or around the neck.

Inspired by the Art of Travel, the double-sided Time Trunk Monogram shawl features images of vintage trunk fittings on a background of Monogram jacquard. Actual metal studs heighten the print’s astonishing trompe-l’oeil effect. Woven of silk and wool, with a plain back, this enveloping shawl coordinates perfectly with the season’s leather goods.

The Morningram belt displays the Louis Vuitton signature on its elegant Monogram canvas strap. The versatile belt can be reversed, showcasing the stylish calf leather that gives the belt a new dimension. A bold brass buckle with gold-color finishing effortlessly completes the look.

Suitable both for business and special occasions, this easy-going tie is available in a broad range of colour options. The Maison's iconic Monogram motif is reproduced as a printed pattern, giving the appearance of a woven tie.

The playful animal prints on these new Animalle bandeaus are part of a collectible capsule, new this season. Woven of pure silk, the skinny scarves can be worn looped around the neck or knotted on the handles of a favorite bag. A very cool gift idea.

The Monogram Split tie has a statement appeal thanks to its inspired jacquard weave. The intricate detailing of its signature Monogram Split motif provides a subtle contrast with the block-color background. Silk fabric elevates this piece and creates a soft finish.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel heritage and the casinos of Macau, the Gambling plate necklace is both stylish and versatile: each of the plates is reversible and features different House signatures, including the iconic Monogram and Damier patterns, allowing for varied combinations. The chain adjusts to three different lengths.

Spotlighting the iconic LV Twist buckle, the reversible LV Twist belt offers two different, stylish looks in one. On one side, glamorous leopard-print calf leather coordinates with the Prefall 2018 collection. On the other, Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas offers a more relaxed, yet still elegant, option.

Modern weaving techniques and timeless elegance define the Summergram Monogram shawl. In a lightweight silk and cotton blend, this impeccably crafted piece features the iconic Monogram print uplifted by striped graphic accents. Fringed edges and a woven Louis Vuitton signature add stylish touches.

Refined and sophisticated, this timeless stole is a must-have for any wardrobe. Woven from precious cashmere, it is a perfect day-to-evening companion that will match both casual and more elegant looks.
The Porte-Documents Voyage PM looks effortlessly stylish in masculine Taiga leather. With smooth leather trimmings and a spacious interior, it combines luxury and practicality.

The sporty chic solution for your daily adventures, this Discovery Messenger PM is remarkably comfortable to carry. Fashioned in extra supple Damier Infini leather, it’s a distinctively lowkey bag for the sophisticated man.

Elegant in black Taiga leather, one of Louis Vuitton's signature materials, the ultra-slim Pince wallet will slip easily into a jacket or trouser pocket. Its key feature is an articulated metal clip to secure banknotes or tickets, while it also offers two flat pockets and four credit card slots.

Featuring the Louis Vuitton baton signature, which was a standout at the Fall-Winter 2018 show, the Horizon City scarf has a contemporary look. Expertly made from a blend of cashmere and wool, this is a chic addition to any cold weather wardrobe.

The Pochette Félicie looks elegant in glossy Monogram Vernis patent leather, which is embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern. This adaptable, envelope-style design, which features two removable inside pockets and a removable metal chain, can be worn on the shoulder or hand-carried as a clutch.

The iconic LV Circle and Monogram Flower intertwine to create the Filigram ring. This piece is crafted from gold-color brass. Inspired by lace, the feminine detailing has an eye-catching look. It is sized in small, medium or large for the perfect fit.

Upside-down, these LV Initials are a hallmark of the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection. Designed by Kim Jones the bold pink logo emblazons this Danube PM city bag, crafted of Monogram Ink canvas. Compact, yet roomy enough for essential belongings, it features an adjustable strap for shoulder- or cross-body wear.

Épi inspires Nicolas Ghesquière. His fresh interpretation of the Cluny bag will thrill aficionados of the signature House leather. The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour palette totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

The fashionable mini size of Capucines PM lends an intense pop of contrasting colors to wardrobe styles from classic to daring. Finished with shiny color accents, the Capucines PM comes with a removable shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

The Pochette Félicie in Monogram Empreinte leather is embossed with Louis Vuitton's emblematic Monogram pattern. The envelope-style design features two removable inside pockets and a removable gold-color chain, and can be worn on the shoulder or hand-carried as a clutch.

A miniature version of Louis Vuitton's iconic Petite Malle handbag, the Essential Trunk in Romantic Blossom Epi leather is the most elegant way to carry a few precious essentials. Its removable chain offers different carry options, while it can also accessorize a larger bag.

Blending a Pop Art influence with iconic House motifs, the LV Stories square is a statement piece. The scarf is decorated with designs including the padlock and key, and Monogram Flowers. With a background that recalls the House's iconic Monogram canvas, this style echoes the theme found across Leather Goods, Accessories and Shoes this season.

Featuring an embossed leaning LV Circle logo, this new interpretation of the Metropole belt is available in two colour options. Its iconic Epi leather is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's leather goods and shoe collections.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Monogram canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

Named for its distinctive House detailing, the LV Iconic 35mm belt features a large gold-color LV logo at the buckle. The black calf leather strap is detailed with gold-tone studs, in either a Monogram Flower motif or a dotted line, both creating a striking look.

This iconic reversible belt is now available in two color combinations that perfectly match the Maison's leather goods. The association of Damier Infini leather with Damier canvases will suit both casual and more daring looks.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton patches, this branded scarf has a sporty flavour reminiscent of American college sport teams. Available in two colours, it is an easy-to-wear piece ideal for city/casual looks.
The Porte-Documents Voyage PM looks effortlessly stylish in masculine Taiga leather. With smooth leather trimmings and a spacious interior, it combines luxury and practicality.

Inspired by the iconic studs from Louis Vuitton's trunks, these must-have earrings are a twisted classic. They can be customized with replacement palladium and pink gold studs to form a variety of unique combinations.

Featuring a finely crafted man silhouette, the Mr Louis bag charm and key holder is both playful and luxurious in style. The metal tips are engraved with LV Initials for a refined effect. Keys are secured on a silver ring and the charm can be fixed to a bag or garment with the snap closure.

This reinterpretation of the Croisette handbag in Damier canvas features a colorful leather lining and an emblematic metallic clasp inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Fresh and feminine, it can be used as a large wallet or a small, chic evening pouch, either with or without its removable chain.

Get the statutory & desirable attitude with the Very Tote Bag. Supple slender handles provide a modern look and carrying comfort while the V signature and the beautiful nods give it a rich, bright feel. The cleverly organized interior has 2 large compartments as well as a zipped pocket for your valuables.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Inspired by the traditional college backpack, thisDiscovery Backpack in supple Taiga leather is incredibly body-friendly. It’s perfect for any man looking for an understated yet sophisticated bag in which to carry his everyday essentials.

Fashioned from Monogram canvas, this one-handled Georges BB bag boasts numerous details inspired by Louis Vuitton’s iconic trunks including a tufted bi-color stripe and signature gold colored lock. Its unexpectedly spacious and well-organized interior, with two separate compartments, make it the perfect bag for active women.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Crafted in Monogram Eclipse canvas and calf leather on one side and pure calf leather on the other, this 14mm Reversible Bracelet for men features a dark-green LV Initials buckle. The combination of darker Monogram canvas prints with calf leather is a look featured in the Men's Fall 2018 Pre-collection.

The LV Initiales reversible belt is a timeless and versatile piece. Honoring the history of Louis Vuitton, the Monogram canvas side captures the spirit of the House, whilst the burgundy calf leather on the reverse provides a contrasting look. A brass buckle with gold finishing crowns this chic belt.

Compact, versatile and totally on-trend, this Pochette Voyage MM in Taiga leather can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy wallet is playfully revisited for the seasonal LV Stories collection. In Epi leather, it is embellished with silver-tone studs and elaborately crafted patches inspired by the House's heritage of travel and trunk-making. They bring a colorful touch to this practical wallet with its secure, zip-around format.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. Crafted of grained Taurillon leather, this city bag that takes care of business, with ample room for papers and files.

With its iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas sheathed directly onto metal, this must-have necklace has a sophisticated masculine feel. Like an amulet, its cylindrical charm opens to provide its wearer with a secret hiding place.

Inspired by the iconic padlock from Louis Vuitton's trunks, this feminine piece makes a perfect Christmas or Valentine's Day gift. Mounted on a fine gold chain, it glitters with sparkling micro-paving in white strass.

The Monogram ring features coated canvas, a subtle reminder of the black trimmings of Louis Vuitton's luxury leather goods. This piece comes in a distinctive overlap design and signature engraving, making it suitable for both formal and casual occasions. Black- and silver-color finishing give this ring a modern, masculine feel.

A striking mix of matte and glossy gold calfskin gives this new Petite Malle a futuristic look. A high-impact accessory for evening, lined with sheepskin in the signature Malletage print, it can be carried as a clutch or worn cross-body for hands-free ease.

With its cool ”schoolbag” shape in a trendy small size, the Mylockme BB makes a big fashion statement. Crafted of soft calf leather, the bag’s long chain strap can be doubled for short-shoulder carry or worn cross-body. A sleek choice for every day, it has room for all the essentials.
Blooming reinterprets the Maison's iconic LV Circle and Monogram Flower signatures as dangling charms. A perfect gift, these feminine earrings will provide the finishing touch for any look.

The LV World Square celebrates the spirit of travel. Set against an allover Monogram background, silk-screened animal prints create a map motif, framed by trompe-l’oeil details drawn from the House’s trunk-making history. Woven of pure silk, this bold yet timeless signature scarf coordinates with the season’s leather goods and shoe collections.

Pleasingly classic lines and supple Taiga leather make the Anton Pochette an ideal option for every day. Compact and comfortable to carry, this new model features refined detailing: witness the discreet metal signature on the bag’s front pocket.

A theme seen across shoes, accessories and leather good this season, the LV Stories animation comes to the Cosmetic Pouch PM in Monogram canvas. The pouch’s playful printed and embroidered “stickers” pay homage to the House’s history as trunk makers.

In Epi leather, the iPhone X & XS Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.

The elegant Mylockme wallet in soft calf leather echoes the sleek design of the Mylockme handbag collection. Its envelope-style flap is secured with an LV Initials accessory, while its practical interior includes two large compartments and several pockets. The flat front pocket offers easy access to items such as tickets.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Damier Ebene canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

The LV World Square celebrates the spirit of travel. Set against an allover Monogram background, silk-screened animal prints create a map motif, framed by trompe-l’oeil details drawn from the House’s trunk-making history. Woven of pure silk, this bold yet timeless signature scarf coordinates with the season’s leather goods and shoe collections.

The Monogram Split tie has a statement appeal thanks to its inspired jacquard weave. The intricate detailing of its signature Monogram Split motif provides a subtle contrast with the block-color background. Silk fabric elevates this piece and creates a soft finish.

Iconic House signatures are delicately reinterpreted to create the Filigram choker. The Monogram pattern and LV Circle are woven into a gold-color mesh for a subtle and feminine look. The size of the piece can be adjusted using the chains for the perfect fit.

Celebrate the return of LV Vernis leather with this Hot Springs Mini-Backpack in patent leather and Monogram canvas. As cute as it is versatile, this is the fashionable everyday bag you’ve been waiting for all year.
This woven tie combines the Maison's iconic Monogram motif with a coloured gradient. Ideal for business looks, it offers a subtly twisted way of playing stripes.
This classic striped tie combines a gradient effect with a contrasting Monogram motif. An ideal choice for business and formal looks, it makes a perfect gift.

Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers. The elegant twist between Black and Grey will bring a touch of brightness to the line.

For Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition of cute animals featuring iconic House signatures. This adorable bird bag charm is crafted from mink fur with Epi leather and Monogram canvas details.

With a corail barrel-shaped metal fastener elegantly inscribed with the “Louis Vuitton” signature, this Keep It Bracelet in black calf leather was designed for the Men's Fall 2018 Pre-collection. It can be stacked with other thin cord bracelets for a fashionably casual look. Simple yet elegant, it makes a great gift.

Showcasing the brand new Monogram White canvas, this new animation of the Reverso buckle makes a strong fashion statement. The reversible option makes it two belts in one, with a summery white side complemented by casual navy.

Launched in Fall-Winter 2017, the Blurrygram Monogram shawl fuses the classic Monogram motif with an elegant gradient design. Crafted from a soft silk and cotton blend, this subtle piece is finished with a fringed hem for a modern feel. It comes in three complementary colors to accentuate an array of styles.

The new Monogram Blossom motif literally brings a fresh dimension to the iconic canvas: artful leather appliqués create contrast and texture on this City Steamer, a structured and roomy bag that makes a fashionable day-to-business companion.

These cute accessories play with iconic Louis Vuitton codes to bring animals to life as playful bag charms and key holders. Ideal gifts, they coordinate perfectly with the Maison’s leather goods lines and can be personalized with hot-stamped initials.
The Amerigo wallet combines timeless style with ultra-functionality. Its compact design is made of convenient features, while remaining slim enough to fit into a jeans back pocket.

Edgy and versatile, this fashionable bandeaux celebrates the Maison's iconic Twist bag. Like the other pieces in this exclusive capsule, it is a perfect gift that can be wrapped around the bag's handles or worn around the neck or wrist.

Featured at the Cruise 18 show, this new model revisits the iconic Noé design with a modern twist. The mix of supple Monogram canvas and rigid cowhide leather highlights House craftsmanship, for a light, versatile city bag that’s timeless and fashionable, too.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.

Pleasingly classic lines and supple Taiga leather make the Anton Pochette an ideal option for every day. Compact and comfortable to carry, this new model features refined detailing: witness the discreet metal signature on the bag’s front pocket.

Louis Vuitton's classic Speedy 25 handbag is reinterpreted for Fall-Winter 2018 in distinctive transformed Damier canvas. Trompe l’oeil details and painterly luggage 'stickers' inspired by the House's trunk making heritage add playful accents to an iconic model of the House. Brushed gold-color hardware gives the bag a subtle sheen, while elements such as a double smartphone pocket lend it practicality.

As part of the Epi Stripes special edition, the Zippy wallet in black Epi leather is reinterpreted with a graphic red and white stripe, inspired by Louis Vuitton's tradition of personalizing its clients' trunks and bags. Each color is stitched separately. This iconic wallet features numerous pockets and compartments in a secure, zip-around format.

The Graceful PM looks fresh and feminine in supple Damier Azur canvas. This spacious hobo has a lightweight, body-friendly design that makes it perfect for every day. The flat handle sits easily on the shoulder, while emblematic details, such as the leather name tag, reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.

With its elegant pleats and discreet LV signature in the sophisticated perforated leather, this Babylone BB is devilishly stylish. Its handle covered in ultra-comfortable sheepskin and the practical interior pockets make it the functional choice for women on the go.

The LV Timeless stole, crafted from a luxurious cashmere blend, is both lightweight and warm. Featuring an allover Monogram pattern, the scarf is accented with silver thread for a refined finish. This updated version of a classic design comes in a Petal Pink hue, creating a feminine aesthetic.

Whether you’re looking for discreet fashion statement or just a versatile everyday bag, this sporty Outdoor Messenger is the great choice. Inspired by the Spring Summer 2018 Show, it’s fashioned in our suppler Taiga leather for a surprisingly body-friendly feel.

The new Monogram Blossom motif literally brings a fresh dimension to the iconic canvas: artful leather appliqués create contrast and texture on this City Steamer, a structured and roomy bag that makes a fashionable day-to-business companion.  This item has very limited availability.  Please call 1.866.VUITTON for more details.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. The iconic Keepall 45 holdall, the original soft travel bag, is a stylish and practical choice for a weekend away.

A genuine fashion statement, this new Reverso model associates two new Monogram canvas colors with more classic versions for a strong visual effect. Fully reversible, it will complement both daring looks and more casual styles.

Glossy Monogram Vernis patent leather, embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, complements the elegant design of the Sarah wallet. This envelope-style wallet, which closes with a gold-tone press-stud, features a comprehensive array of pockets and credit card slots, including a zipped compartment for coins.

An edgy look inspired by piercings, these mismatched double-chain earrings have an original design that envelopes the ear lobe. Their rich details feature iconic Louis Vuitton elements, including trunk studs and the LV Circle signature.

This visually striking Twist Tote with its velvety black polka dots embroidered on white Epi grained leather is a continuation of the pop art theme explored by Nicolas Ghesquière in his shows. The unique embroidery technique makes the motif particularly striking. This Twist Tote will bring an eye-catching and graphic accent to any look yet is easily paired thanks to its timeless black and white color palette.

For the Epi Stripes collection, the Sarah wallet in Epi leather is reinterpreted with a bold red and white stripe, referencing Louis Vuitton's tradition of personalizing its clients' luggage. Each color is stitched separately, while the LV initials are also picked out in red. This envelope-style wallet offers a variety of convenient features.

The classic Sarah wallet in Damier canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by a colorful leather lining. It combines an elegant, envelope-style exterior with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The Marignan Messenger in Monogram canvas and grained leather is the quintessence of everything that makes Louis Vuitton bags the very definition of elegance. The on-trend colors will bring instantaneous modernity and freshness to any outfit.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Matchpoint collection mixes sporty details with luxury know-how on stylish designs adapted to the lifestyles of modern men. This supple all-in-one wallet in Damier Cobalt canvas features separate compartments for professional and personal phones, as well as numerous other pockets and credit card slots. It can be carried around the wrist or slipped inside a bag.

Warm and enveloping, this voluminous wool-and-silk blend shawl features an allover of a new, larger Monogram pattern, which is sure to delight fans of the iconic motif. Finished with delicate fringe and a woven “Louis Vuitton Paris” signature.

Available in two colors, this new simple tour bracelet is embellished with a feminine mobile chain. Anchored in Louis Vuitton codes, it features delicate Monogram Flower and LV signature motifs on its metallic studs.

Featuring an all-over Monogram pattern twisted with a flowery background, this feminine piece references the Maison's heritage with its Louis Vuitton trunk frame. It is available in two summery colours.

Inspired by the Men's Pre-collection Fall-Winter 2018, the Gambling cufflinks are a reference to Louis Vuitton's travel heritage and to Macau, famous for its casinos. With their stylish silver-color finish and intricately inlaid Monogram Flowers and LV Initials, these dice-shaped cufflinks are an elegant and discreetly signed accessory.

Louis Vuitton's historic Karakoram pattern comes to the Zippy Wallet for Winter 2018. Ruby-red and luminous-white grained cow leathers come together with engraved gold-finish studs in a bold motif that energizes this emblematic wallet.

This Surene BB handbag is an adorable mini-tote bag in supple Monogram Empreinte leather, featuring a subtle tone-on-tone embossed Monogram print. The gold-color chain handles with two calf-leather shoulder pads brings color and elegance to a classic comfortable bag. The removable leather nametag adds that final touch of LV sophistication.

The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour strap totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

The LV Circle reversible belt is detailed with a striking LV Circle logo buckle. The strap is available in black Epi leather and in signature Monogram canvas, each with a contrasting effect on the reverse and different buckle colors. This is a reinterpretation of an iconic style, updated in new combinations and with sleek finishes.

With a design inspired by vintage trunk stamps from the House archives, the aptly named Giant Square makes a big fashion statement. Woven of a soft blend of cotton, silk and wool, this versatile piece can be styled in any number of fashionable ways

The elegant Anton backpack makes a polished impression in any professional setting. Fashioned of durable Taiga leather, it features impeccably crafted heritage details: note the top handle, subtle tone-on-tone signature tab, and metal zip pulls.

A perfect match for this season's Monogram Constellation Denim ties, this pocket square offers an iconic motif in an easy-going and recognizable pattern. The red version coordinates with the season's other red pieces.

Presenting the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag PM, a statement piece destined to become a fashionable wardrobe staple. Made from smooth quilted calfskin, it features a removable handle with a colorful “Louis Vuitton” signature. An aged-metal finish adds richness to the bag’s hardware and sliding chain, which adapts to long- and short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

A soft, hexagonal shape gives the LV Chamade model an original twist. The faceted acetate frame is accented with iconic “trunk” studs and Essential V inserts on the temples. Offered in black or tortoise shell, this style can be fitted with corrective lenses.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière refreshes the City Steamer giving it a new supple feel thanks to grained calf leather. The handles and strap in exotic python leather add a touch of glamour. With its two carrying options and large capacity, this City Steamer is a great alternative for active women who require a practical bag but don’t want to sacrifice style.

Combining fine-grained calf leather with iconic Monogram canvas, this stylish, trendy compact wallet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Double V bag. The original double flap conceals a secret pocket, which is ideal for tickets or coins.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.
On this striking key holder and bag charm, the iconic LV Initials signature is inlaid with brightly colored lacquer for a playful, modern look.

A versatile day-to-evening piece, this versatile shawl features an all-over Monogram motif embellished with a frame of shiny Monogram flowers. The innovative "fil coupé" technique adds femininity and refinement.

Inspired by Kansai Yamamoto's contribution to the SS18 Cruise collection, this notebook is a nomadic object for collectors everywhere. Its graphic print is inspired by Japanese style and the explosive energy of Manga.

This Backpack PM model is made from Monogram Titanium coated canvas, a signature material introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 show. An easy-to-wear casual style, it features textile-and-leather trim and Titanium-color hardware. Compact yet roomy inside, it accommodates daily essentials with ample pockets and compartments.

For Fall 2018, the versatile Zippy Wallet is fashioned from iconic Damier Ebene canvas, accessorized with gold-color studs all over the flap. The Cerise red lining perfectly offsets the classicism of the Damier Ebene canvas, while the roomy interior and an all-round zip make it perfect for carrying your daily essentials.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.

With details, such as silver studs, inspired by Louis Vuitton's trunk-making heritage, the Legacy Enchape bag charm and key holder evokes the spirit of travel. Smooth, calf leather tabs are expertly lined with the iconic Monogram canvas. Keys are secured on the ring, while the snap closure can be fixed to bags or clothing.

Featuring a games board motif from the archives, the pure silk Jeu de Louis square vividly illustrates the history of Louis Vuitton. Hallmark prints including Damier and Monogram are mixed with playful symbols such as pawns and dice. The fun design retains all the qualities of an iconic accessory, making it a truly timeless piece.

This new version of the Maison's must-have LV Twist belt makes a strong visual impact with its metallic studs and eyelets. Combining timeless black calf leather with bi-galva finishing, it will upgrade both fashion silhouettes and more edgy looks.

This distinctive Tote crafted of Monogram Shadow leather is a major fashion piece from the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection. The very supple, subtly embossed cowhide is a pleasure to handle and carry. Detailed with black metal hardware, the Tote features a removable, zipped leather pouch for valuables and a secure hook closure.  This style may not be available until a later date. Please contact Client Services at +1.866.VUITTON for more details.

Featuring a fashionable round shape with a single metal bar at the bridge, Lanai is an ultra-modern frame for street-style silhouettes. Metal rims are twinned with an acetate shell at the front, with Damier details adding a discrete signature.

A perfect Chinese New Year gift, this playful yet refined necklace celebrates the Year of the Dog. Engraved with the Louis Vuitton’s iconic Monogram signature, it coordinates with the Maison’s textiles and a matching leather bracelet.

The LV Circle reversible belt is detailed with a striking LV Circle logo buckle. The strap is available in black Epi leather and in signature Monogram canvas, each with a contrasting effect on the reverse and different buckle colors. This is a reinterpretation of an iconic style, updated in new combinations and with sleek finishes.

Monogram canvas and smooth calfskin combine in the Saintonge, a compact bag with a youthful vibe. The leather lends contrast and volume to the design, and the tassels are a playful touch. With its top handle and long strap, the bag can be styled in different ways.

This braided cord bracelet features a spring hook-style clasp in echo to the technical, sporty vibe of the SS18 show. Available in two Monogram canvas color options, it is the perfect accessory for an edgy, contemporary look.

The Dorian mirror is an elegant object for both travel and the home. Its natural leather handle and buckle, inspired by handbags, give it a feminine touch, while its detachable cover in iconic Monogram canvas protects it on the go.

The eye-catching Logomania Rainbow scarf in wool and silk offers two looks in one: one side is woven with a multi-colored Monogram pattern and has a warm wool feel, while the other features the Monogram pattern on rainbow stripes and feels soft and silky.
The iconic Reykjavik scarf gets a luxurious revamp with this exceptional fur and cashmere piece. Embellished with generous fox fur, it will bring a daring touch of elegance to any wintry outfit.

This Surene BB handbag is an adorable mini-tote bag in supple Monogram Empreinte leather, featuring a subtle tone-on-tone embossed Monogram print. The gold-color chain handles with two calf-leather shoulder pads brings color and elegance to a classic comfortable bag. The removable leather nametag adds that final touch of LV sophistication.

The LV Capucines bag charm and key holder is inspired by its namesake handbag. The combination of metal and leather in the LV Initials signature is an ode to the heritage and expertise of the House. This elegant piece also features a dual function clasp.

Featuring a striking fluorescent color inspired by the Men’s Fall/Winter 18 collection, these Clockwise Sunglasses offer a blend of sport and street style. Their trendy double bar combines with a flat front to create very modern look. Engraved LV initials and Louis Vuitton logos add a subtle touch of branding.

The Twist Chain wallet is one of Louis Vuitton's new classics, featuring the iconic Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers. This special editon combines two emblematic materials: black Epi leather and Monogram canvas, which is appliquéd in a bold V motif inspired by the House archives.

The LV City 35mm Reversible Belt offers a stylish choice between two different leather finishes. Plain calf leather on one side creates a sophisticated look, while the embossed Damier motif on the other provides a more branded option. The brand new LV buckle is the ideal width for suits and comes with shiny black ruthenium finish for a tone-on-tone effect.
These stylish sunglasses feature on-trend round lenses and transparent frames integrating a flash of color. The round shape particularly suits square and oval faces.

Echoing the stylish, casual design of the Lockme II handbag, this compact wallet in soft calf leather is secured with a distinctive LV initials press stud. Its extremely functional interior boasts a variety of pockets and compartments.

Dressed in fresh, feminine new colorways for spring, the season’s Capucines models display delicate contrasts. In sizes to suit every need or silhouette, these now-classic handbags are crafted of full-grain Taurillon leather lined with smooth calfskin.

Iconic symbols from Louis Vuitton collections mix and merge with the Monogram pattern in the Pop Confidential bandeau. The new lively print lends this piece a playful and feminine dimension. Crafted in pure silk, it adds a feeling of luxury to each wear. This versatile accessory makes a great gift for Monogram fans.

The Zippy Lockme wallet in supple calf leather combines the iconic design of the Zippy wallet with the key signatures of the fashionable Lockme collection: the LV Initials accessory and the front pocket offering easy access to items such as tickets. The Zippy Lockme contains numerous pockets and compartments within a secure, zip-around format.

As part of the Epi Blooming Corners limited edition, the Victorine wallet in black Epi leather is embellished with hot-pink corners in the shape of Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers. Recalling the historic trunks, this playful detail complements this neat envelope wallet, which packs a range of convenient features into its compact dimensions.

The Lockingram bracelet combines three iconic Louis Vuitton motifs in reference to the House's rich history. The padlock charm, a detail often found on Louis Vuitton's leather goods, takes center stage. A Monogram canvas strap with a calf leather lining, and hardware shaped in the Monogram Flower, complete the bracelet.

This elegant wallet combines iconic Damier canvas with soft, fine-grained calf leather and a statement clasp inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Its well-designed interior offers an array of functional pockets and slots.

Referencing Louis Vuitton's art of travel, the Zippy wallet in iconic Monogram canvas is embellished with colorful trompe-l'œil details inspired by the historic trunks. This ingenious design includes an array of pockets and compartments within a secure, zip-around format. This collectible edition belongs to the Trunk Summer 2018 theme taking in accessories and leather goods.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom on the front of this pure-silk screen-printed bandeau, with an allover Monogram pattern on the reverse. Available in a range of summery shades, this slim scarf can be styled in a variety of ways. Perfect for gifting.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Created for the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection, the Speedy 40 makes a strong style statement, whether slung over the shoulder or carried by hand. The supple Monogram Shadow leather features a tone-on-tone embossed pattern – a subtle yet unmistakable House signature. Black hardware and black textile straps accentuate this bag’s resolutely masculine look.

Featuring the Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers, the Twist Chain wallet is one of Louis Vuitton's most recognizable designs. Combining leopard print, Monogram canvas and corduroy-styled leather, this special edition is part of the seasonal Wild capsule, inspired by the Prefall 2018 collection.
Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format. It is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men.

The Duffle Time Trunk handbag presents a playful twist on House signatures for Fall-Winter 2018. A painterly effect on transformed Monogram canvas calls attention to bright, historical luggage stickers. Buckled straps and gold-tone studs nod to the House's trunk-making roots, creating a trompe l’oeil effect in the process. Aged silver-color hardware completes the bag's vintage-inspired look.

This Zipped Tote is crafted from supple, high-gloss Monogram Glaze, an innovative twist on the House’s signature coated canvas. Trimmed with natural cowhide and detailed with black metal hardware, this hybrid bag is equipped with two concealable straps that transform the tote into a body-friendly backpack. The roomy interior can hold a workday’s or weekend’s essentials.

The LV City 35mm Reversible Belt offers a stylish choice between two different leather finishes. Plain calf leather on one side creates a sophisticated look, while the embossed Damier motif on the other provides a more branded option. The brand new LV buckle is the ideal width for suits and comes with shiny black ruthenium finish for a tone-on-tone effect.

The savoir faire of the House is encapsulated in this playful Vivienne bag charm and key holder. Natural mink fur, pear tree wood, and Louis Vuitton’s recognizable Monogram Flower create this friendly mascot. Featuring an oversize fur hoodie, Vivienne doubles as a versatile bag charm and key holder.

Part of this season’s Flower Studs capsule collection, the Capucines Compact Wallet in Taurillon leather is decorated with Monogram Flowers, outlined with silver-color studs. Fashioned from colored leather, the all-over flower pattern, also seen on the Capucines handbag, brings a dash of color to this compact wallet.

This new metal model offers an innovative blend of Monogram canvas and rubber on the temples, making it extremely comfortable to wear. Available in a choice of Monogram Ebene or Monogram Eclipse, it is ideal for round and oval face shapes.

An update on the House's historical Cannes beauty case, the Cannes handbag nods to vintage styling in textured Epi leather. A sleek silhouette and silver-color hardware distinguish the elegant piece, whose dual handles offer multiple carrying options. The compact interior holds the essentials while a zip-around closure keeps belongings secure.
A tribute to Louis Vuitton's leather goods know-how, this stylish key holder and bag charm combines emblematic Taiga leather in black and electric blue with an iconic LV-engraved padlock.

The perfect stole for summer, in a lightweight blend of cotton and silk. Monogram Flower “dots” create a playful 3D effect, for a modern take on a classic pattern. Offered in easy-going blue or feminine pink, it adds a sunny touch to warm-weather looks.
Inspired by the Lockme II bag and its trendy yet casual shape, Lockme II wallet in soft calf leather offers a modern style combined with optimal functionalities.

The Damier Shuffle sunglasses stand out thanks to their lightweight structure and modern design in black and silver, featuring a distinctive double bridge and top bar engraved with Louis Vuitton's signature Damier pattern. The fashionable round shape, emphasized by the double rim, suits square and oval faces.

The blue-to-white gradient of the Capucines Cloudy evokes a calm and misty horizon. It is an elegant color story for a chic, versatile bag that will elevate every summer silhouette. Crafted of Taurillon leather, this PM model features an edge-dyed top handle and a removable strap for a crossbody carry.

Whether you’re looking for discreet fashion statement or just a versatile everyday bag, this sporty Outdoor Messenger is the great choice. Inspired by the Spring Summer 2018 Show, it’s fashioned in our suppler Taiga leather for a surprisingly body-friendly feel.

With its cool ”schoolbag” shape in a trendy small size, the Mylockme BB makes a big fashion statement. Crafted of soft calf leather, the bag’s long chain strap can be doubled for short-shoulder carry or worn cross-body. A sleek choice for every day, it has room for all the essentials.

Part of the family of bag charms celebrating the animals of the Chinese zodiac, the limited edition Pig Bag Charm and Key Holder features a cute padded pig crafted from Monogram canvas and calf leather. An homage to historic Louis Vuitton materials, the pig’s eye is formed by a classic stud reminiscent of those used on the House’s trunks.

Crafted with details that evoke our emblematic trunks, this Twist MM is right on trend for this summer. Iconic Epi leather mixes with Monogram canvas for a lightly signed option on this strong seasonal story.

This edition of the indispensable bumbag combines the House’s colorful signature Epi leather with Damier Graphite canvas in a playful patchwork pattern. A stylish addition to any casual look, this belt bag is practical, too, for keeping essential items close at hand and secure, with a zipped closure and silver-color metal buckle fastener.

Louis Vuitton invites you to travel with peace of mind, tracing your connected luggage in the main worldwide airports. Get notified on your smartphone or your Tambour Horizon after landing: to know whether your luggage has arrived in the right airport or not. The services are accessed exclusively by downloading and using the Louis Vuitton App application.

The quintessential evening accessory, this captivating Louise clutch is fashioned from satin-smooth calfskin and embellished with a sparkling, richly crafted signature lock. Faceted Swarovski® crystals in two brilliant hues are individually set around the gold-finished LV initials, for a precious effect as dazzling as a night in Paris.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy Organizer is revisited as part of the Epi Patchwork collection, combining blue and gray Epi leather with accents of Damier Graphite canvas. With its neat proportions and secure zip-around format, this organizer is the perfect solution to keep essential documents and payment methods in one place.

For a slightly more casual feel, this Armand Messenger PM with its crafted details is the modern choice for your new attaché. Very body-friendly thanks to the supple Taurillon leather, you can literally carry it all day every day.

Now there’s wallet that fits perfectly into the House’s fashionable mini-handbags: the Twist XS Wallet in Epi leather with silver-color hardware. Nicolas Ghesquiere’s iconic Twist Lock has been resized, transformed into a small piece of jewelry, to give a precious touch to this extra small wallet.
This ultra-feminine edition of the Twist bag is as fresh as it is stylish. The design blends vibrant colors and crafted details into a new and poetic take on the classic Monogram Flower motif.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this elegant wallet is crafted from supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature. The striking two-tone color scheme complements this sleek design, which is large enough to hold all the daily essentials.

Complementing Louis Vuitton's Summer 2018 capsule collection, this casual reversible belt in Damier Cobalt canvas offers two stylish looks in one: a rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on one side and a playful jungle print on the other.

The Pop Monogram Square in pure silk presents the season’s fresh twist on the iconic pattern. The central Monogram Flower is composed of a playful mix of straps, chains and locks – all historic House leatherwork signatures. Stripes and dots add a modern touch to this on-trend screen-printed scarf, an ideal gift for Monogram fans.

Crafted from Monogram Titanium canvas, which featured at the Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show, the Cosmos wallet is an elegant way to keep cash, cards, tickets and papers in one safe place. The gray canvas is complemented by a front pocket in Louis Vuitton's iconic natural cowhide leather, which is embossed with the House signature.
Perfect to twist a business look, this playful tie combines classic dots with a tone-on-tone trunks pattern symbolizing Louis Vuitton. Available in a range of classic colours, it is a perfect gift.

In a choice of two new colors, the LV Initiales belt is an update on a design from Louis Vuitton's permanent collection. It is crafted from Damier canvas with a calf leather border, in reference to the House's leather goods edit. LV Initials in silver-color brass, inlaid with lacquer, complete this refined piece.

The design of this LV List stole takes a cue from the season’s ready-to-wear collection. Woven of a luxe cashmere-and-silk blend, it is a soft, warm accessory, ideal for mid-season to winter wear. Its graphic good looks have a cool fashion edge, yet the stole is easy to wear and coordinate with virtually any look.

The Victorine Wallet, made from supple Monogram Empreinte leather, has been carefully designed to create a small wallet able to hold as much as a long one. Thanks to a protective coating, the leather resists scratches, rubbing and fading. This compact and practical wallet easily slips into any bag.

This reversible piece provides two belts in one, with its colored Monogram Illusion and timeless black calf leather. Featuring a graphic LV Pyramide buckle, it is a modern branded accessory to brighten up any outfit.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Slim and chic, the reversible Slender 35mm belt in Taiga leather comes in two timeless and versatile color combinations. The ideal accessory for business suits, it features a finely crafted ardillon buckle in silver-finished brass.

The new mix of Damier Ebene canvas and lightly grained calf leather produces an urban-chic model with a decidedly youthful, modern vibe. A casual style with a fashionable twist, the Clapton is compact yet it holds a long wallet, a phone and other essentials with ease.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Discovery Backpack in Monogram Eclipse canvas has a sporty vibe. Green and black hardware lends a stylish touch to this versatile bag equipped with multiple pockets and a secure hook-and-eye closure. Comfortable textile back straps and a top handle provide different carry options.

A soft, hexagonal shape gives the LV Chamade model an original twist. The faceted acetate frame is accented with iconic “trunk” studs and Essential V inserts on the temples. Offered in black or tortoise shell, this style can be fitted with corrective lenses.

With their round shape and mix-material structure, these Nue au Soleil sunglasses are highly in vogue. The tubular temples are detailed with the iconic Louis Vuitton Monogram, while the double bridge in gold-color metal creates a striking focal point. These sunglasses can be fitted with corrective lenses.

A luxurious way to stay warm and look cool, this winter stole is woven of softest cashmere and silk. The strong graphic design highlights the Louis V. signature as an allover, with a single element colored in a rainbow gradient. Offered in bold black with white or in off-white with gentle blue.

This Speedy 30 handbag spotlights the House’s travel legacy. Supple Damier Ebene canvas takes on a contemporary feel with printed and embroidered travel “stickers”. The top handles and a removable strap give this versatile bag multiple carry options.

Decorated with the iconic LV Circle signature first used on our historic trunks, this Bumbag is for the fashion conscious. Compact and crafted in supple Epi leather, it’s ideal for transporting your daily essentials.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this sporty piece features a pattern made up of colourful trunk stamps. Available in two colour options, it is a playful hat to wear alone or combined with its matching scarf.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle meticulously inlaid with a blue lacquered piece , this reversible belt offers two looks in one: graphic and iconic on the Damier canvas side, bold and stylish on the calf leather side.

The sweet Japanese treats known as “hanami” inspired the ultra-feminine details on this new Capucines model. The Monogram Flower is rendered in satin, lambskin and colorful beads, for a fresh, playful look that is totally in tune with spring silhouettes.

Crafted from Monogram Ink canvas, which was inspired by the Louis Vuitton archives, the Voyager belt coordinates with the accessories and leather goods collection. Complemented by a bold coral-color buckle, it is lined with calf leather and features a leather loop with an LV-engraved rivet.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.

The Filigram bracelet is defined by its delicate detailing. Crafted in a subtle mesh design evocative of lacework, the gold-color metal also features the classic LV Circle and Monogram Flower throughout. It is complemented with a golden clasp for the perfect fit and is part of a feminine range of coordinating accessories.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière introduces the Trunk Clutch in supple Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas, a soft-sided reinterpretation of the iconic Petite Malle. This soft-sided clutch continues Louis Vuitton’s reimagining of its heritage as trunk makers and boasts signature details like the S-lock clasp and a sheepskin interior lining with a Malletage print.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

The New Wave compact wallet is crafted from exceptionally smooth, supple calf leather, which is quilted with a wave pattern inspired by a historic Louis Vuitton trunk. Lightweight and space-efficient, this envelope-style wallet offers a variety of pockets and credit-card slots. The flap is signed with an iconic LV Initials accessory.

The Blooming Flowers BB bag charm and key holder is a nod to the distinctive Monogram Flowers print. The use of Epi leather, metal and Monogram coated canvas is a testament to the expertise of Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. This floral charm is the perfect size to hook onto the zipper of small leather goods.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.
This cotton-jacquard summer stole displays an allover, contrasted Monogram print. Deep-dyed for saturated color, it's an easy-to-wear accessory for casual warm-weather looks.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.

The Epi Patchwork edition of the Christopher backpack makes a strong style statement with a mix of richly colored leather and Damier Graphite canvas. Robust and functional, this PM model is equipped with adjustable shoulder straps, a top handle for another carry option, and multiple pockets, inside and out. The leather flap with a press-stud closure keeps belongings secure.

Big, bold polka dots team up with House signature straps, chains, locks and the LV Circle logo on this Monodots Monogram shawl. The four corners display variations in patterns and color, for a host of creative styling options. Jacquard-woven of silk and wool yarns, the shawl’s generous dimensions wrap the wearer in lightweight warmth.

This Voyager 35mm Belt gives pride of place to the new Monogram Titanium canvas, introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Lined with calf leather, it also features iconic natural leather details that will acquire a distinctive patina over time. The roller on the ardillon buckle is engraved with a discreet Louis Vuitton signature.

The LV Initiales reversible belt is a timeless and versatile piece. Honoring the history of Louis Vuitton, the Monogram canvas side captures the spirit of the House, whilst the burgundy calf leather on the reverse provides a contrasting look. A brass buckle with gold finishing crowns this chic belt.

Refined yet trendy, this necklace reinterprets the Maison's iconic Monogram motif. A flower-shaped pink quartz stone is mounted inside a metal frame engraved with the Monogram pattern, for a refined signature look.
Real New Classic of the House, the Twist MM chain bag is the ideal size for a day-to-evening companion, worn either over the shoulder or cross-body on its long, sliding chain.

A key story for SS 18, Monogram Blossom brings an arty new mood to the House’s iconic canvas. The flower appliqués in smooth black calfskin lend this Petite Malle an edgy allure. Inside, the luxe sheepskin lining features the signature Malletage pattern.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Mixing Iconic Epi leather with emblematic Monogram canvas and silver-color studs, this Twist MM handbag takes on a fashionable rock edge. Grained leather and coated canvas are stitched together to reproduce Vuitton's emblematic V signature in a perfectly symmetric pattern that stretches from the bag's flap to its body. This reimaging of one of the House's New Classics is a testament to the House’s inimitable leatherworking expertise.

This sophisticated shawl is a perfect day-to-evening piece that will match any outfit. Metallic gold studs complement glamorous black to make this collector's item a must-have for Monogram lovers everywhere.
Launched in Fall 2017, the St Sulpice is already a classic LV chain bag. The smart metallic lock, contrasting leather edging, and adorable size make this BB version your go-to everyday chic solution.

The Twist MM handbag debuts a fresh look for Winter 18. Fashioned from Epi leather and embellished with the signature Twist lock, it features a short chain handle braided with contrasting leather. A colorful LV charm adds a playful touch to this on-trend, crafted model. Both the charm and the leather shoulder strap are removable, for extra versatility.

Inspired by the Normandy bag, this soft and feminine wallet elegantly combines Louis Vuitton's historic Damier canvas with supple Taurillon calf leather. Its cleverly designed interior can hold everyday essentials.

The Daily Monogram bracelet is a rigid open-back bracelet featuring Monogram Flowers in gold- or silver-tone metal on lacquer. It comes in an assortment of statement colors, making it ideal for collecting and gifting.

The LV Circle reversible belt is a distinctive fashion accessory. Patent leather on one side, and the world-renowned Monogram canvas on the reverse, make this slim piece a versatile companion. A striking gold-color medallion buckle displays the iconic LV signature.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Keepall Bandouliere 50, the original soft travel bag, is revisited for this special edition in key materials from the Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. Here, it comes in high-gloss Monogram Glaze canvas and features natural cowhide-leather trim, textile handles and a removable shoulder strap embossed with the House signature.
The iconic Reykjavik scarf gets a luxurious revamp with this exceptional fur and cashmere piece. Embellished with generous fox fur, it will bring a daring touch of elegance to any wintry outfit.

From the pen of Kim Jones comes this iteration of Vivienne, the jaunty Louis Vuitton mascot. She lends her playful presence to a limited edition of the Clémence Notebook, available only in the season’s pop-up spaces. Crafted of Monogram Eclipse canvas, the notebook’s cover coordinates with leather goods and accessories presented at the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection show. An ideal gift for writers, doodlers and travelers.

A perfect (and perfectly feminine) bag for business, this functional tote is embellished with a distinctive Monogram Flower padlock in gleaming golden metal. The smooth leather handles and detachable strap provide a variety of carry options, and the well-organized interior easily holds files and a laptop.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Metis Wallet is crafted from supple Monogram Empreinte leather with the celebrated Monogram pattern embossed on the leather. It features Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock, inspired by the historic trunks. Its roomy interior boasts two large gusseted compartments and a zipped coin pocket.

The emblematic Twist Chain wallet in Epi leather is a stylish and versatile design which can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

A new take on Louis Vuitton’s Monogram ID theme, the LV Tab bag charm and key holder features iconic padlock details and a masculine design. Vibrant Lava orange Epi leather combines with laser-cut LV Initials to make a street-style statement. This versatile accessory functions as a bag charm or key holder.

A bold, contrasting LV Circle signature defines the two-tone Cardiff scarf. It is crafted from cozy wool and cashmere, which has been brushed and scratched for maximum softness, woven together using the jacquard technique. Fringed edges add contemporary flair to this versatile piece.

The Magic Monogram stole features the classic Monogram pattern combined with a romantic floral print for a feminine update. This reimagined style comes in three versatile hues to complement a variety of moods. Crafted with a hint of cashmere, the stole's generous dimensions make it a cozy accessory on cooler days.

A close look reveals that this Gambling stole is printed with new and archival House signatures, arranged in a playing-card pattern. Woven of a cotton-and-silk blend, this mid-season piece makes an on-trend addition to a casual masculine wardrobe. Generously sized, it can be styled in a number of different ways.

The Mylockme compact wallet in supple calf leather references the key signatures of the Lockme handbag: the envelope-style flap, the front pocket and the LV Initials accessory. Small enough to fit into any Lockme bag, this space-efficient design offers an array of pockets and credit card slots, including a zipped pocket for coins.

With their rich textures and distinctive Louis signature, these playful accessories will bring a trendy touch to any bag. Available in both leather and metal versions, they are a perfect match for the Maison’s ready-to-wear collections and shoes.

Introducing an exclusive capsule of silk-and-wool shawls: three different designs each feature an iconic animal and  signature motifs (LV initials, stripes  borrowed from historic trunks...) These collectible pieces add a cool, colorful flourish to casual or dressy looks.

The ultra-functional Zippy XL offers the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It is large enough to hold a smartphone (in a specific pocket), keys and passport, in addition to credit cards and cash. Elegant in Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, it can be carried by the handle for a sophisticated look.
The simple elegance of Epi leather. The peerless versatility of the Zippy wallet. The numerous card slots and compartments. The all-round zip. Quite the unbeatable combination.

The new mix of Damier Ebene canvas and lightly grained calf leather produces an urban-chic model with a decidedly youthful, modern vibe. A casual style with a fashionable twist, the Clapton is compact yet it holds a long wallet, a phone and other essentials with ease.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Beyond Monogram shawl offers a fun interpretation of a classic Louis Vuitton print. A graphic background featuring playful striped accents and contrasting large-scale Monogram motifs elevates the design. This soft silk-and-wool-blend accessory comes in a vibrant pink hue for a contemporary finish.

With its trendy, large pilot shape this lightweight, metal design is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes. The cutout V design on the bridge offers a distinctive branded signature with a contrasting matt/shiny effect. Mirror or more classic lenses available.

The Daily Confidential bracelet is crafted from calf leather and Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas for a two-tone effect. The materials are embellished with a metallic flower in a gold-color finish. A closer look at this new-season item reveals a clasp engraved in the House's iconic Monogram pattern.

Nicolas Ghesquière updated the Chantilly bag on its 40th anniversary. Made of Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas trimmed with calf leather, it features a redesigned, embellished padlock. An edgy piece with a boho-chic spirit, for day to after dark.

The soft white version of Romantic Blossom – a key motif for SS 18 – wraps this Petite Malle in delicate pink, blue and yellow flowers, printed on pristine Epi leather. This exclusive model can be carried as a clutch or worn hands-free, on a removable strap.

Coordinating with the Louis Vuitton leather goods collection, the Voyager belt in supple Monogram Eclipse canvas offers a smart-casual look. It is complemented by an LV-engraved metal buckle with a distinctive dark-green finish, and is fully lined with calf leather.

The Saint Michel bag combines two iconic materials - Monogram canvas and Epi leather - in a small, chic shape that is perfect for everyday essentials. The adjustable strap allows it to be carried on the shoulder or across the body, and its flap can be personalized with the owner's initials.

Edgy and versatile, this fashionable bandeaux celebrates the Maison's iconic Speedy bag. Like the other pieces in this exclusive capsule, it is a perfect gift that can be wrapped around the bag's handles or worn around the neck or wrist.

This Neverfull MM tote bag is fashioned of Monogram canvas and trimmed in natural leather. It pays tribute to the Louis Vuitton travel and trunk-making heritage with a mix of patches featuring House emblems, twisted in a playful and contemporary way. Spacious but not bulky, structured yet supple, the Neverfull is always exactly what you need it to be.

This edition of the Discovery Messenger PM is made from Dark Infinity calf leather, a material introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 show. Designed for cross-body carry, this compact model features a leather shoulder pad in Monogram Glaze coated canvas. Detailed with black-metal hardware, the bag is a stylish choice for every day.

For Fall-Winter 2018 Show Nicolas Ghesquière introduces a new nomade-shape: the Glasses Case handbag with the familiar Monogram print and a striking padlock closure. A mix of luxury materials, such as Epi leather and Monogram coated canvas, gives a luxurious feel. This bag is ideal for carrying essentials and can be worn across the body or on the shoulder thanks to the adjustable chain strap.

These Mascot Sunglasses combine trendy transparent mirror lenses with a design centered around the House’s iconic V signature. An intricate blend of acetate and metal, they are available in two stylish color combinations. Alongside the top bar’s metallic V and Monogram design, signatures include LV initials on the lenses and an engraved Louis Vuitton on the temples.

Influenced by the House's permanent Keep It collection, this stylish bracelet is a statement piece. The metal hardware is intricately engraved with the Louis Vuitton Paris signature. Crafted from Damier printed canvas, this bracelet is ideal as a statement accessory.

For summer, the graphic Monogram Confidential pattern is revamped in animal print to create the Leogram Confidential square. Tonal gray hues soften the eye-catching design, carefully screen printed on pure silk for an offbeat finish. Coordinating patterns can be found across the ready-to-wear and shoe lines.
Adorned with a bold camouflage pattern, this fashionable piece is ideal for a young and modern look. Available in two colour options, it coordinates perfectly with the Maison's shoe collection.
This fashion-forward piece is inspired by the season's Hawaiian theme. Available in five classic colours, the delicate floral will add a soft cool touch to any look.

Fashioned in classic Monogram canvas and signed with a “Louis Vuitton Paris” leather patch, this uber-functional Bumbag transforms sportwear into the very definition of casual chic. Wear it as a belt bag, cross-body or over the shoulder for a jauntier look.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

With details, such as silver studs, inspired by Louis Vuitton's trunk-making heritage, the Legacy Enchape bag charm and key holder evokes the spirit of travel. Smooth, calf leather tabs are expertly lined with the iconic Monogram canvas. Keys are secured on the ring, while the snap closure can be fixed to bags or clothing.

These square LV Player sunglasses present a sporty look with their laminated acetate frames, brow bar and two-tone color. Nods to the House's hallmarks include the Damier signature engraved on the temples and tips, a Louis Vuitton signature on the side and LV Initials on the lenses. Solid-colored sun lenses complete this elegant design.

Fashioned in Damier Azur coated canvas and leather patches adorned with trompe l'oeil screen prints of trunk corners and historic LV locks, this Speedy 30 is the very essence of LV style. For those who wish to flaunt their fashion credentials.

Floral prints take on a darker feel for Fall-Winter 2018 with the Twist MM handbag. Nicolas Ghesquière contrasts the vibrant blue Epi leather of this shoulder bag with intricate black and red flower motifs, resulting in an elegant design.

Bleached denim jeans inspired this new Monogram shawl. Silk and wool yarns are specially dyed to highlight the pattern’s contrast; the fabric is then screen-printed to create the “bleached” effect. It brings a touch of effortless cool to any casual look.

This casual-chic hobo style in the Maison’s iconic canvas features a Monogram Flower padlock in shiny golden metal – a distinctive new signature. Light, roomy and easy to open, the bag’s flat leather shoulder strap ensures comfortable all-day wear.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Pince wallet in stylish black and grey Damier Graphite canvas is an ultra-slim design that will slip easily into any pocket. In addition to four credit card slots and two flat pockets, it features an articulated silver-tone metal clip to securely hold banknotes or tickets.
The most stylish way to carry around money, cards and coins is the Zippy Wallet Vertical. In elegant smooth Taïga leather, it’s also supremely practical with numerous pockets and compartments.

The Pop Monogram Square in pure silk presents the season’s fresh twist on the iconic pattern.
