Timeless design and up-to-date details make the Kleber in Epi leather a wardrobe essential for the active woman. Functional features combine with fashionable touches (note the LV signatures and bold colour story) for a business bag with exceptional cachet.
Elegance is personified in the petite shape of the Pochette Metis. Made of supple Monogram empreinte leather, its compact dimensions open up to reveal many useful pockets and compartments.

The House continues to reveal new facets of Vernis leather with an unexpected reinterpretation of one of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic shapes: the Alma BB. The audacious color and Monogram canvas trim gives it a stunningly disruptive feel.

The LV Upside Down Zippy Organizer is a playful take on one of Louis Vuitton's iconic models: the ultimate zip-around wallet that keeps essentials, including cards, cash and passports, safely in one place. The famous LV Initials are mischievously turned on their head and printed in eye-catching coral pink on Monogram Ink canvas.

The Flore Wallet combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful calf leather for a playful, vibrant look. Its signature is the feminine Monogram flower press stud, which is partially covered in leather. The long wallet boasts multiple practical features, including a soft, microfiber-lined pocket to hold a phone.

Inspired by piercings, these Bionic Wings And Leaves Earrings evoke the spirit of Nicolas Ghesquière’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Designed to envelop the ear-lobe, they consist of two complementary pieces. The first - finished in gold with a subtle LV signature - features delicate leaves interspersed with LV Circles, while the second depicts a delicate wing with silver-color finish.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.

Soft textures meet muted colors in the Petit Damier scarf. Knit from pure wool using a high-precision technique, details of the iconic Damier patterning receive a polished new treatment in subtle inky tones. The LV Initials appear on a textile patch for a low-key logo finish.

The Alma PM Time Trunk handbag receives a fresh interpretation for Fall-Winter 2018 in contrasting leather elements, creating a trompe l’oeil effect. Inspired by the House's trunk-making heritage, the sophisticated Alma is crafted from transformed canvas with glossy leather accents, gold studs and lock details. This impeccably crafted piece is completed by a black trim, highlighting its structured shape.

Featuring both calf leather and edge-dyed Damier or Monogram canvas, the LV Treble bracelet pays homage to the House's esteemed leather goods. It is constructed from a trio of straps, braided together for a striking look. The piece is completed with a metal hook clasp in shimmering brass, with a silver-color finish.

The Astrid is an elegant one-handled city bag in delicate grained leather with a smooth leather stripe. Its structured shape and new signature metallic Monogram Flower lock make it a very practical yet ultra-desirable choice.

Its slim design and pure lines make the Anton Briefcase’s elegant silhouette as appropriate for work as the weekend. Whether you carry it by hand or wear it over the shoulder with the removable strap, you’ll be right on-trend.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.

Meet the modern travel jewelry case. With a leather handle inspired by our classic trunks, a removable pouch, and an elegant red microfiber interior, this classic and feminine Monogram wonder protects your earrings and necklaces, bracelets and rings.

The Daily Monogram cord eyewear chain is a tribute to the fairer seasons with its floral pattern and Flower Crown story inspiration. Monogram Eben canvas sets a distinctive theme, followed up with LV Initials engraved on the metal tips. An adjustable closing system means one size fits all.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, the House reimagines the Speedy Doctor in iconic Monogram canvas and black calf leather with bold yet elegant hardware. Inspired by the classic doctor’s bag, it brings a more rigid and structured shape to the ever popular range of Speedy soft travel bags.

This easy-to-wear style is a pure classic, perfect for every occasion. A choice of tortoiseshell acetates offers a play on colours, while the square shape offers a trendy look for round and oval faces.

Featuring both calf leather and edge-dyed Damier or Monogram canvas, the LV Treble bracelet pays homage to the House's esteemed leather goods. It is constructed from a trio of straps, braided together for a striking look. The piece is completed with a metal hook clasp in shimmering brass, with a silver-color finish.

Featuring the Maison's LV Circle signature, this double-tour calf leather strap is enhanced with a jewel-like metallic motif. Available in three colors, it is a discrete piece to accumulate or wear alone.

With its casual-chic design, the new St Sulpice in Monogram Empreinte leather is a sophisticated choice for day-to-evening. New, too, are the bag’s sliding chain and signature metal lock. Surprisingly roomy, it can be worn on the shoulder or cross-body.

The Pochette Weekend clutch in summery Damier Azur canvas references Louis Vuitton's travel heritage with trompe-l'œil details evoking the iconic trunks. Stylish and versatile, it can be transformed into a small shoulder bag thanks to its removable chain. This special edition belongs to the Trunk Summer 2018 collection of accessories and leather goods.

Part of an evening capsule collection, the Maverick tie in classic black stands out with an interplay of matte and shiny elements. The House's iconic Damier pattern has been reimagined in a graphic format, with jacquard fabric lending it textural richness. The sleek shape and timeless hue make this tie a refined staple.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

These LV Showdown Sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and light rimless structure. Thin all-metal temples create a hyper-modern feel, while specific Monogram lenses inject a unique touch of branding. Engraved LV initials and Louis Vuitton signatures supply the finishing touches for this fashion-forward piece.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

A special blend of silk and other yarns gives the Monogram Shine shawl its subtle shimmer. For this Leogram model, a tone-on-tone animal pattern is screen-printed atop an allover Monogram jacquard background. A fashionable day-to-evening accessory, this generously proportioned piece will enhance virtually any silhouette.
Elegant and businesslike, the Anton tote conceals an array of functional pockets and compartments within its sleek, timeless design. Handles and a removable shoulder strap offer two carrying options.

The Pinball LV square features a games-inspired print, giving this intricate scarf a fun update. World-famous landmarks, such as the Eiffel Tower, echo the enduring traveler spirit of the House. Hallmark Louis Vuitton symbols enhance this bright and lively accessory crafted in opulent silk.
Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format. The  daring twist between Navy Blue and Light Blue will highlight any silhouette.

This colorful silk square reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. This elegant accessory will add a sophisticated, feminine touch to any outfit.

A miniature version of Louis Vuitton's iconic Petite Malle, replicating key details of the historic trunks, the Essential Trunk is the most elegant way to carry a few precious essentials. Its removable chain offers different carry options, while it can also accessorize a larger bag.

Part of a special capsule inspired by the season's Hawaiian theme, this refined striped tie features fine stripes printed on a tone-on-tone Monogram jacquard. On the back, a floral pattern adds a poetic touch.

This Brazza, fashioned in Damier Graphite canvas, is energized by a playful touch of blue that emphasizes the checkered pattern. Its generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.

Adorned with the Maison's graphic Cities print motif, this generous scarf fhas a new enveloping format for a fashion-forward look. Crafted from a warm blend of wool and cashmere, it features a double-sided effect.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. Crafted of grained Taurillon leather, this city bag that takes care of business, with ample room for papers and files.

The Matchpoint collection mixes sporty details with luxury know-how on stylish designs adapted to the lifestyles of modern men. The compact Pocket Organizer in Damier Coastline canvas is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers.

This NéoNoé handbag is crafted of grained Epi leather with smooth leather trim and two eye-catching stripes which bring a fresh feel to the emblematic model. The two-tone stripe, a traversal theme seen on shoes at the Fall 2018 Collection, is a nod to the House’s trunk making and personalization Heritage. The Néonoé bucket bag can be carried over the shoulder with its adjustable strap or by hand, thanks to the removable top handle.

A genuine fashion accessory, this bandoulière strap will turn any bag into an object of desire. True to the codes of the House, the craftsmanship pays tribute to Louis Vuitton’s heritage of fine leatherwork.

The LV Jungle sunglasses are reimagined in new season colors. These frames combine horn effects and solid acetate to create a sophisticated contrast. Their round shape and keyhole nose detail add retro accents, complemented by iconic House hallmarks, such as Louis Vuitton signatures on the temples and LV Initials engraved on the lenses.

For Fall 2018, the exquisite Petite Malle handbag is crafted from black calf leather with exclusive exotic python-leather trim and a gold-color S-lock clasp. A sophisticated yet practical small bag perfect for evening use, it is Nicolas Ghesquière’s vision of the House’s original trunks and the spirit of travel they represented. The removable leather strap enables two carry options: clutch or cross-body.

In iconic Monogram canvas, the iPhone X & XS Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.

The Lymington in Damier Ebene canvas is the perfect city companion for everyday life. The discreet touches of burgundy combined with dark cowhide leather on the handles and tassels will bring elegance and feminity to any look.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.
Sophisticated and supple Epi leather is the perfect material for the Multiple Wallet. Very compact but still functional with numerous pockets and slots, it fits easily into any pocket.

The best-selling My Fair Lady model is now offered in two fashionable new color combinations. House signatures – note the Essential V metal inserts, iconic trunk studs at the front and LV Circle end tips – lend a special elegance to this ultra-feminine style.
This classic striped tie combines a gradient effect with a contrasting Monogram motif. An ideal choice for business and formal looks, it makes a perfect gift.

These Mascot Pilot sunglasses are a sophisticated mix of metal and acetate. The iconic V shape at the bridge is the central focus of these aviator sunglasses, with open metal work highlighting their strong silhouette. Distinctive House touches include the Louis Vuitton signature at the temples, LV Initials on the lenses and the Monogram design on the bar.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel heritage, this stylish silk bandeau is printed with a trompe-l'œil trunk in Monogram canvas, complete with colorful details such as a Louis Vuitton luggage label and brass hinges. A versatile, fashionable piece, it can be worn in many different ways: around the neck, in the hair, or knotted on the handles of a bag.

The emblematic Twist bag gets an edgy rock feel thanks to the alternating studs and eyelets that adorn this model’s flap. The ultimate chic little bag takes a bold look at what’s happening on the streets.

Complementing Louis Vuitton's Summer 2018 capsule collection, this casual reversible belt in Damier Cobalt canvas offers two stylish looks in one: a rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on one side and a playful jungle print on the other.
Adorned with a bold camouflage pattern, this fashionable scarf is ideal for a young and modern look. Available in two colour options, it coordinates perfectly with the Maison's shoe collection.

The Matchpoint collection mixes sporty details with luxury know-how on stylish designs adapted to the lifestyles of modern men. Supple and lightweight, this spacious washbag in Damier Cobalt canvas keeps grooming essentials perfectly organized thanks to its three inside compartments.
With numerous carry options, the Montaigne BB is a compact alternative for businesswomen who don’t wish to carry too much. And of course it looks beautiful in Monogram Empreinte leather.

These Mascot Pilot sunglasses are a sophisticated mix of metal and acetate. The iconic V shape at the bridge is the central focus of these aviator sunglasses, with open metal work highlighting their strong silhouette. Distinctive House touches include the Louis Vuitton signature at the temples, LV Initials on the lenses and the Monogram design on the bar.

This Damier Colors Necklace is adorned with charms whose graphic lines are inspired by the House’s iconic Damier pattern. Their blue enameled background is a perfect match for the new Epi leather color from the season’s Leather Goods. Three adjustment rings enable the necklace to be adjusted to the ideal length.

Elegance is personified in the petite shape of the Pochette Metis. Made of supple Monogram canvas adorned with screen prints of trunk corners and historic LV locks, this version is a post-modern trompe l'oeil masterpiece.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format.

Available in two colors, this new simple tour bracelet is embellished with a feminine mobile chain. Anchored in Louis Vuitton codes, it features delicate Monogram Flower and LV signature motifs on its metallic studs.

This Surene MM chain tote handbag in Monogram Empreinte leather with its gold-color chain is as functional as it is sophisticated. Very easy-to-wear thanks to the leather shoulder pads that adorn the chain, this tote’s generous dimensions mean it easily fits A4 files as well as all your daily essentials. The Monogram pattern embossed in the supple leather is deep enough to remain over time while still maintaining its supple feel.

Showcasing the fluorescent colors that are a key theme of the Fall/Winter 18 collection, the LV Fluo Necklace Charms is a fun piece for fashion-forward customers. Fluorescent leather on the pendant contrasts with the shiny silver-color finish for a sophisticated hand feel and masculine look. The yellow and orange colors are a perfect match for this season’s Leather Goods and Accessories.

As its name suggests, the LV Tribute Bracelet is an ode to Louis Vuitton's heritage. It comes complete with a charm shaped like a hat box from the House archives, which dangles from a Monogram canvas strap with a calf leather lining. This collectible piece features the LV signature etched on the clasp for a further elegant touch.

The LV Jungle sunglasses are reimagined in new season colors. These frames combine horn effects and solid acetate to create a sophisticated contrast. Their round shape and keyhole nose detail add retro accents, complemented by iconic House hallmarks, such as Louis Vuitton signatures on the temples and LV Initials engraved on the lenses.

The new must-have accessory, Louis Vuitton's Flower Strass Phone Ring is a glamorous and innovative way to hold a mobile phone. The Monogram Flower is paved with glittering strass, while the gold-color ring is engraved with the iconic Monogram pattern and Louis Vuitton signature.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day.

The Metis Wallet is crafted from supple Monogram Empreinte leather with the celebrated Monogram pattern embossed on the leather. It features Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock, inspired by the historic trunks. Its roomy interior boasts two large gusseted compartments and a zipped coin pocket.

Adorned with the iconic Monogram motif, these must-have bracelets coordinate perfectly with the palette of the season's ready-to-wear and leather goods. Easy to mix-and-match, they will add a touch of colour to any silhouette.

The Monogram Flower morphs into a playful floral print on this new Lockme Backpack. The colorful blooms cavort on natural black calf, a leather with a fine grain and sensual hand. Outlined in red, the signature LV turn lock adds a final fashionable twist.

The best-selling LV Confidential bracelet is now offered in a rainbow of new hues. In grained calf leather or Monogram canvas, they feature engraved metal fasteners with lacquer or gold-color finishes. Stacked, they make an eye-catching fashion statement.

The Telling Monogram stole pairs the hallmark Epi and Monogram prints with modern detailing for a versatile finish. This soft wool shawl is enhanced by a subtle gradient effect and contrasted fringes. Generous proportions allow a variety of styling options while making it a cozy cool weather essential.
The Amerigo wallet combines timeless style with ultra-functionality. Its compact design is made of convenient features, while remaining slim enough to fit into a jeans back pocket.

The Monogram ring features coated canvas, a subtle reminder of the black trimmings of Louis Vuitton's luxury leather goods. This piece comes in a distinctive overlap design and signature engraving, making it suitable for both formal and casual occasions. Black- and silver-color finishing give this ring a modern, masculine feel.

These La Boum sunglasses feature the classic cat-eye shape and an added line of studs evoking Louis Vuitton's iconic trunks. A new model in the collection, the accentuated frame gives a feminine effect while gold-color temples add a luxury feel. Rubber temple tips give a secure comfortable fit.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt offers two looks in one: casual on the Monogram canvas side, more sophisticated with a chic neutral on the grained calf leather side. It is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's Pallas handbag.

Named for its distinctive House detailing, the LV Iconic 35mm belt features a large gold-color LV logo at the buckle. The black calf leather strap is detailed with gold-tone studs, in either a Monogram Flower motif or a dotted line, both creating a striking look.

The Monogram Empreinte Blanche MM combines embossed and smooth cowhide in a perfectly proportioned shoulder bag. Supple leather and curvaceous lines make this roomy, comfortable model a casual-chic choice for everyday wear. The flap closure is embellished with a signature hook-and-leather detail. Equipped with a detachable and adjustable strap, the Blanche MM can be carried cross-body, for hands-free ease.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton’s iconic personalized luggage, this Petite Malle handbag is crafted of Monogram canvas decorated with a graphic bicolor stripe and gold-color hardware. The interior is lined in sheepskin printed with the Malletage motif, a pattern adapted from the linings of the House’s classic trunks.
What better method to carry keys than in this charming 4 Key Holder. Sleekly rendered in attractive Monogram Vernis, it is a guaranteed way of ensuring that one never forgets their keys.

A luxurious way to stay warm and look cool, this winter stole is woven of softest cashmere and silk. The strong graphic design highlights the Louis V. signature as an allover, with a single element colored in a rainbow gradient. Offered in bold black with white or in off-white with gentle blue.

The classic Monogram Chain bracelet is inspired by trimmings found on traditional Louis Vuitton leather goods. A versatile reworking of a key design from the House, it features the iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas and has a silver-color finish. The bracelet is part of a full collection of complementary jewelry.

To celebrate Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition featuring cute, nature-inspired scenes incorporating key House signatures. A perfect gift, the Victorine wallet is the ultimate compact companion: an ingeniously designed small wallet that can hold as much as a long one.

The Essential V chain necklace takes its inspiration from the graphic V motif which Nicolas Ghesquière introduced at his first runway show for Louis Vuitton. This now iconic signature is interpreted in colored lacquer and decorated with studs referencing the House's historic trunks. The delicate chain is finished with a clasp and LV Circle ornament.
Louis Vuitton's Zippy Vertical wallet contains many practical features in a compact zip-around format. It looks modern and elegant in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.

Composed of blooming Monogram Flowers, LV Eden is a romantic, feminine pattern, rendered in an arty “watercolor” style on pure silk fabric. The slim bandeau model can be worn as a head, waist, wrist or neck wrap, or rolled around the handles of a bag.

The emblematic Twist Chain Wallet is given a glamorous touch in golden metallic leather. Stylish and versatile, it can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Detailing from Louis Vuitton's historical trunks combines to form the cat figure of this Wild Puppet bag charm and key holder. Miniature gold-tone metal studs, eyelets and zip pulls all feature in this inventive design, which is crafted from calf leather and natural mink fur. Secured with a clasp and chain, this piece makes a playful adornment to a backpack or handbag.

For Fall 2018, the day-to-evening Twist MM takes on a poetic feel, thanks to printed Monogram Flowers in contrasting colors surrounded by metallic studs. The row of delicate blossoms highlights the Twist’s iconic lines and brings an inviting softness to the Epi leather’s appearance.

Crafted from Monogram Empreinte leather, the elegant Adèle Wallet has a slim design with two leather zippers and a magnetized button for easy opening. Spacious enough to hold a smartphone in addition to credit cards and coins, it can also be carried as a clutch.

This large version of Louis Vuitton's Pochette Jour is crafted from supple Cuir Taurillon leather, characterized by its soft grain. With its wide zipped opening, this spacious pouch can be used as a clutch, laptop holder or document portfolio.

The Yummy LV bracelet has been updated for the new season in fresh colors. Each version is embellished with a trio of metal studs etched with the Louis Vuitton signature. The clasp is finished with an intricate engraving of the iconic Monogram pattern.

With its iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas sheathed directly onto metal, this must-have cuff pays tribute to the Maison's Leather Goods savoir-faire. A masculine piece, it can be mix-and-matched with other pieces from the collection.

Adorned with the season’s emblematic Monogram Titanium canvas, the Monogram Fluo Tab Bag Charm And Key Holder offers a distinctive and fashionable way to dress up bags, keys and pants. The rope detail with metal end tips is a key feature of Men’s Fall/Winter 18 collection, while the key ring and snap hook feature discreet Louis Vuitton signatures.

A special blend of silk and other yarns gives the Monogram Shine shawl its subtle shimmer. For this Leogram model, a tone-on-tone animal pattern is screen-printed atop an allover Monogram jacquard background. A fashionable day-to-evening accessory, this generously proportioned piece will enhance virtually any silhouette.
Understated and easy-going, this must-have tie features a delicate tone-on-tone LV logo in a semi-plain effect. A refined piece, it comes in four classic colours to match any formal look.
Combining Louis Vuitton's iconic Taiga leather with bright palladium-finish brass, this black and cobalt leather necklace makes a bold, masculine statement.

With its neat proportions and softly rounded flap, the Rosalie coin purse in Damier Azur canvas is a feminine design. The fresh canvas is complemented by a lining in pale-pink grained cowhide leather, which also covers the purse's press-stud closure. Inside, it offers two credit card slots and a zipped pocket for coins.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton’s emblematic trunks, this exclusive Georges MM in Monogram canvas with a distinctive tufted two-tone stripe, calf-leather trim, and signature lock is a lightweight one-handled handbag. Body-friendly, it offers multiple carry options including hand, elbow with the top handle, and over the shoulder thanks to the leather strap.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière reinterprets the iconic Petite Malle with this Trunk Clutch in supple Epi leather. This soft-sided clutch continues Louis Vuitton’s reimagining of its heritage as trunk makers and boasts signature details such as the S-lock clasp and a sheepskin interior lining with a Malletage print

Inspired by Nicolas Ghesquière's invitations to Louis Vuitton fashion shows, the Pochette Kirigami in iconic Epi leather consists of three individual envelopes which fit inside each other. The large pouch is perfect for an iPad Mini or everyday essentials, the medium one for a passport and the small one for cards or coins.

The Morningram belt displays the Louis Vuitton signature on its elegant Monogram canvas strap. The versatile belt can be reversed, showcasing the stylish calf leather that gives the belt a new dimension. A bold brass buckle with gold-color finishing effortlessly completes the look.

Enamel hardware on the Monogram Confidential bracelet creates saturated shades. It is accented with a precision print of intersecting lines that reflect the House's textile designs. The gold-tone fastener, which clicks to close, creates the illusion of a metal buckle.

This LV City 35mm Reversible Belt combines plain calf leather with the House’s iconic Damier canvas to supply a choice of styles. The plain leather side is perfect for business occasions, while the reverse’s Damier canvas creates a more urban feel. The new LV buckle provides a tone-on-tone effect, while the 35mm width is ideal to wear with suits.

In muted Monogram Eclipse canvas, the Monogram pouch bag charm and key holder exhibits Louis Vuitton's typically refined style. Luxury craftsmanship is continued with the polished metal hardware. Perfect for tucking away small items and keys, this zip-around pouch combines fashion with function.

Suitable both for business and special occasions, this easy-going tie is available in a broad range of colour options. The Maison's iconic Monogram motif is reproduced as a printed pattern, giving the appearance of a woven tie.
This fashion-forward piece features small Vs contrasting with a plain background, in an understated and low-key design. Available in three colours, it is ideal for formal yet modern looks.

The iconic Monogram Shawl becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a new, soft and airy monogram jacquard material embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

Compact and versatile, with plenty of space for essentials, Louis Vuitton's Pochette Voyage can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. It looks modern and elegant in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.

Edgy and versatile, this fashionable bandeaux celebrates the Maison's iconic Alma bag. Like the other pieces in this exclusive capsule, it is a perfect gift that can be wrapped around the bag's handles or worn around the neck or wrist.

The ultimate accessory for iPhone aficionados, Louis Vuitton's cult Eye Trunk has been upgraded for the iPhone X & XS. First seen on Spring-Summer 2018 show by Nicolas Ghesquière, this new version comes with a functional lock and removable leather strap for shoulder or cross-body carry, it is a cutting-edge fashion statment.

This silk jacquard tie reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a modern, miniaturised version. Discreetly signed with the LV initials, it is a timelessly stylish accessory that makes an ideal gift.

Following on from the success of the Monogram Split motif, the LV Split hat is a truly bold design. Featuring a Louis Vuitton signature that appears split down the middle, with each half in contrasting tones, the pure wool composition makes it soft to the touch. For a coordinated look, it can be worn with the matching gloves and scarf.

The Damier Shuffle sunglasses stand out thanks to their lightweight structure and modern design in black and silver, featuring a distinctive double bridge and top bar engraved with Louis Vuitton's signature Damier pattern. The fashionable round shape, emphasized by the double rim, suits square and oval faces.

Big, bold polka dots team up with House signature straps, chains, locks and the LV Circle logo on this Monodots Monogram shawl. The four corners display variations in patterns and color, for a host of creative styling options. Jacquard-woven of silk and wool yarns, the shawl’s generous dimensions wrap the wearer in lightweight warmth.

Big, bold and upside down: the LV logo on this oversized square is printed in neon coral against a dark-blue Monogram background. The inverted initials are a key story this season, found on leather goods and a range of accessories. Made of a cotton-and-silk blend, the scarf is ideal for mid-season wear.

A sporty yet elegant accessory for city looks, this pure-wool scarf has a soft, silky hand. The Monogram pattern in classic navy is accented with colorful stripes and an embroidered LV signature. Generously sized, it's both stylish and warm.

Featured at the Cruise 18 show, this new model revisits the iconic Noé design with a modern twist. The mix of supple Monogram Reverse canvas and rigid cowhide leather highlights House craftsmanship, for a light, versatile city bag that’s timeless and fashionable, too.
The historic Popincourt bag is back, with a trendy new attitude. In Monogram canvas and natural leather trim, this contemporary tote offers easy-going style as well as flawless functionality.

The Daily Confidential bracelet is crafted from calf leather and Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas for a two-tone effect. The materials are embellished with a metallic flower in a gold-color finish. A closer look at this new-season item reveals a clasp engraved in the House's iconic Monogram pattern.

This belt features a Taurillon leather strap with delicate Monogram flower perforations, which is complemented by the LV Iconic buckle with feminine rounded edges. It is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's emblematic Capucines handbag.

Updating the classic pilot frame, these sunglasses feature flat lenses for a sporty, fashionable look, while the semi-rimless structure adds lightness and modernity. The pilot shape is ideal for square and oval faces.

The LV Explorer square celebrates the art of travel with a playful pattern. Inspired by the lining in one of Louis Vuitton's trunks, the design combines exotic accents with the Monogram Flower print for a romantic finish. This versatile piece can be worn around the neck or as a statement headband.

The best-selling LV Confidential bracelet is now offered in a rainbow of new hues. In grained calf leather or Monogram canvas, they feature engraved metal fasteners with lacquer or gold-color finishes. Stacked, they make an eye-catching fashion statement.

Inspired by the season's Hawaiian fashion theme, this pocket square offers a delicate and poetic way of playing a floral print with fine stripes. Available in a refined denimy-grey, it is a perfect accompaniment for fashion-forward looks.

The Millefeuille Tote proves that it is indeed possible for a bag to be both timeless and modern. Its bold mix of color and iconic Monogram canvas combined with luxurious details make this functional bag remarkably stylish.
This business buckle provides a perfect option for more understated looks. Coloured edge dying adds a twist to the Taiga leather strap, with an LV cutout contributing a subtle branded touch.
Fast Flower reinterprets the Maison's iconic Monogram Flower in pure and graphic lines, tinted with Art Deco. With its fine metalwork, this flower-shaped ring is a must-have piece for day wear.

The sequins, embroidery and patches stitched onto the Damier Ebene canvas of this compact Victorine Wallet reference the travel stickers that adorned the House’s trunks at the turn of the 20th century. This compact envelope wallet boasts a range of useful pockets and card slots.

Decorated with embroidered and printed patches depicting iconic House symbols, the Pochette Felicie  is a nod to the Louis Vuitton’s historic trunks with their exotic travel stickers. This versatile wallet can be transformed into a stylish shoulder bag thanks to its removable golden chain, or carried as a clutch.

A shower of colorful blossoms is strewn across this soft calfskin edition of the Lockme Backpack Mini. Inspired by the iconic Monogram Flower, the leather blooms in six different shades lend this piece a summery vibe that will complement the season’s silhouettes.

Inspired by the SS18 season's leather goods, this exclusive new version of the Maison's LV Initiales Double Monogram is perfect for edgy looks. The Split design associates contrasting Monogram canvases for a striking bi-color effect.

Louis Vuitton's colorful Pop Monogram hat is knitted from soft, cozy pure wool. A perfect way to brighten cold days, it revisits the iconic Monogram pattern in the playful spirit of Pop Art. Part of a set including a scarf and gloves, it makes an ideal gift.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.
The most stylish way to carry around money, cards and coins is the Zippy Wallet Vertical. In elegant smooth Taïga leather, it’s also supremely practical with numerous pockets and compartments.

The matte black Ardillon buckle of the Voyager belt epitomizes the masculine elegance of this belt. Urban and contemporary, the belt is a statement piece. It is finished with meticulously crafted details that pay homage to the rich heritage of the House.

The City Steamer MM handbag takes on a striking new color for Fall 2018: an intense and elegant Etain dark gray, adding a modern touch to the grained calf leather and bringing a casual yet chic feel to the timeless City Steamer. The perfect mix of Louis Vuitton tradition and the new signatures created by Nicolas Ghesquière give this New Classic a fresh allure.

The matte black Ardillon buckle of the Voyager belt epitomizes the masculine elegance of this belt. Urban and contemporary, the belt is a statement piece. It is finished with meticulously crafted details that pay homage to the rich heritage of the House.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

The Morningram belt displays the Louis Vuitton signature on its elegant Monogram canvas strap. The versatile belt can be reversed, showcasing the stylish calf leather that gives the belt a new dimension. A bold brass buckle with gold-color finishing effortlessly completes the look.

Slim and chic, the reversible Slender 35mm belt in Taiga leather comes in two timeless and versatile color combinations. The ideal accessory for business suits, it features a finely crafted ardillon buckle in silver-finished brass.

For Fall-Winter 2018, Nicolas Ghesquière reimagines the classic hat box as the coveted Boite Chapeau souple handbag. Inspired by the House's travel heritage, this supple Monogram canvas design has a long leather strap, making it easy to carry across the body or over the shoulder.

Available in timeless black or vivid Coquelicot, this reversible belt offers a choice between iconic Epi leather and Monogram canvas for a more casual look. The new LV Circle buckle adds an extra signature touch.

The Yummy LV bracelet has been updated for the new season in fresh colors. Each version is embellished with a trio of metal studs etched with the Louis Vuitton signature. The clasp is finished with an intricate engraving of the iconic Monogram pattern.

The Time Trunk Zippy wallet comes in transformed Damier canvas with trompe-l'œil detailing for a vintage look. It is part of a seasonal collection referencing the Fall-Winter 2018-19 fashion show, where Nicolas Ghesquière revisited Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. This iconic wallet packs a host of convenient features into a secure, zip-around format.

The Very bag charm and key holder spotlights the LV Circle signature, which is inlaid with colored enamel and embellished with a matching leather braid ending in two Monogram Flower charms. This intricate design references Louis Vuitton's heritage of craftsmanship and coordinates with the Very leather goods line.

The Monodots pure-silk bandeau is patterned with two versions of the season’s Pop-inspired print. On the front, dots and stripes play with Monogram. On the back, Monogram Flower joins the mix for a fun, graphic effect. A stylish gift, this slim scarf can be wrapped around neck, head, wrist or waist or knotted on a bag.

This iconic piece combines a universal striped motif with the Maison's Monogram signature for a fashion-forward piece. Matching the season's Denim theme, it features a fine line of contrasting Monograms after each stripe.

Inspired by Nicolas Ghesquière's Essential V logo, these mask-shaped sunglasses create a statement look with wow effect. An engraved Monogram pattern on the end pieces and temples adds an iconic touch.

For Valentine's Day, a cute bird incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Sarah wallet in Monogram Vernis leather. This envelope-style wallet features an ingeniously designed interior offering a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.

This pocket square belongs to a capsule collection that features animals of the Chinese zodiac, constructed of Monogram and Damier motifs. Fashioned of pure silk, this playful piece coordinates with a matching tie as well as with the season’s leather goods and fashion jewelry. Definitely collectible.
This stylish, masculine bracelet in emblematic Taiga leather features a graphic locking system engraved with the Damier pattern and Louis Vuitton signature.

These aviator-style Clockwise sunglasses have a modern look thanks to a rimless frame and a flat front. They feature a double bar at the brow, LV Initials engraved on the end pieces and the Louis Vuitton logo at the temples. The metal elements are contrasted with colored gradient mirror or signature Monogram lenses.

Crafted from Louis Vuitton's iconic Epi leather with its distinctive grain, the Zippy Organizer is the perfect wallet for modern lifestyles. Its space-efficient design fits numerous essential features, including credit card slots, a secure coin pocket and two large bill compartments, into an extremely compact, zip-around format.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel heritage, the Trunk Summer 2018 theme sees the Zippy coin purse in Monogram canvas printed with brightly colored trompe-l'œil details taken from the historic trunks. Containing numerous practical features within a compact, zip-around format, this special edition is part of a complete collection of accessories and leather goods.

Louis Vuitton's Vivienne mascot makes a playful appearance on the Pochette Apollo in Monogram Eclipse canvas, bringing a fashionable twist to this sleek document wallet. Featuring coordinating green and black hardware, the Pochette Apollo can be carried in the hand as a clutch, or slipped inside another bag.

Chic and understated, the Comete wallet is crafted from luxurious Taurillon leather with a subtle grain and soft feel. The design features an all-round zipper which opens to reveal a functional, well-organized interior with three separate compartments. In a final sophisticated detail, the zip pull is embellished with a tiny Monogram Flower.

Inspired by the iconic padlock from Louis Vuitton's trunks, these feminine earrings make a perfect Christmas or Valentine's Day gift. Featuring an innovative closing system, they offer a refined combination of finishes.

A contemporary take on the classic schoolbag, the updated Mylockme is a sleek, ultra-fashionable model crafted of soft, supple calf. Versatile and functional, with a well-organized interior, it can be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

The Vivienne cap from this season’s capsule features the image Louis Vuitton’s playful mascot/toy. Crafted of cotton with leather detailing, this billed cap features an adjustable closing system, to ensure a comfortable fit. Available exclusively in pop-up locations, it is sure to be a favorite with collectors.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton patches, this branded scarf has a sporty flavour reminiscent of American college sport teams. Available in two colours, it is an easy-to-wear piece ideal for city/casual looks.

The Surene BB handbag in Monogram canvas and grained calf leather with a gold-color sliding chain is Louis Vuitton’s new chain bag. Its sleek shape is enlivened with gold-color hardware and the generous use of leather trim. The perfect casual-chic bag, it is lightweight, versatile, body-friendly and easy to wear.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

The LV Stories Logomania scarf is peppered with signature House motifs, including Monogram Flowers, in the form of colorful patches. The designs are layered over an allover Monogram jacquard weave. Crafted from a blend of wool and silk, this piece is finished with a fringed border. Coordinating designs can be found across the Leather Goods, Shoes and Accessories lines.
This envelope-style wallet combines an elegant exterior in Monogram canvas with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

For Fall 2018, the day-to-evening Twist MM takes on a poetic feel, thanks to printed Monogram Flowers in contrasting colors surrounded by metallic studs. The row of delicate blossoms highlights the Twist’s iconic lines and brings an inviting softness to the Epi leather’s appearance.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's personalization stripes, the LV History tie strikes the perfect balance between sporty and refined. Two bold diagonals and the LV signature contrast against a plain background for a college-inspired feel. The tie blends with laid-back looks as well as more formal ensembles.

The Tuileries Besace mixes Monogram canvas with tricolor leather accents for a bold, fashion-forward look. Easy-chic every day bag, the Besace may be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body, thanks to a removable strap.

House traditions of trunk-making and fine leatherwork come together in this miniature “hatbox” crafted of beige natural cowhide and black calfskin. A standout on the SS 18 runway, this covetable piece can be carried or worn cross-body on its removable strap.

The Pont Neuf belt echoes the famous Parisian bridge both in name and spirit. It features Louis Vuitton's seminal Damier canvas and gracefully contrasting red highlights for an extra visual element. The polished silver-tone buckle completes this multifaceted accessory.

Delicate perforations on the top and handle of the Capucines Sweet Brogues bag, crafted of Taurillon leather, create a Monogram Flower pattern that is enhanced by a contrast backing of light-colored lambskin. This feminine PM model is ideal for daily wear, either carried by hand or worn over the shoulder on its detachable strap.

The Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Tote in soft calf leather is both on-point and practical: with its luxe quilted detailing and aged-metal hardware, it will dress up any ensemble, while accommodating a full day’s essentials. The sliding-chain handle of this light, body-friendly bag can be adjusted for short or long shoulder carry.

This Messenger PM bag is made from Monogram Glaze, a glossy version of the iconic canvas, introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 show. Designed for hands-free, cross-body wear, it features a wide leather shoulder pad embossed with a bold Louis Vuitton signature. Compact and easy to wear, it is an ideal model for everyday use.

Inspired by the fluorescent colors of this season’s Men’s Ready-To-Wear collection, this LV Fluo Bracelet is a fun and fashion-forward piece. Easily adjustable thanks to its sliding elements, the thin cord bracelet is adorned with an iconic LV and an engraved brass circle. Fluorescent leather contrasts with shiny silver for a trendy look.

Slim and sleek, with an inlaid LV clasp that lies flush to the strap, this new masculine bracelet is offered in black calfskin, Monogram or Monogram Eclipse coated canvas. All are calf-leather lined. Easy to wear, this signature piece makes a handsome little gift.

Nicolas Ghesquière embraces daring animal prints in the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, reimagining the City Steamer PM in a bold combination of leopard-skin print, supple leather, warm corduroy, and iconic Monogram canvas. Sophisticated details – note the silver-colored padlock and nametag with a metallic LV signature – enrich this heirloom-quality piece.

This small version of the Pochette Apollo in Monogram Eclipse canvas spotlights Louis Vuitton's cute Vivienne mascot. With its coordinating green and black hardware, this on-trend design can be hand-held as a clutch or slipped inside another bag. It is large enough to take a smartphone, cards and cash.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.

Function and fashion align with the Epi Mix bag charm and key holder in vibrant Lava orange with Oxford blue edge-dying. Iconic Damier or Monogram canvas and Epi leather coat either side of the tab for a resistant finish that will keep its shape. This versatile accessory can be used to keep keys together, or to decorate a bag.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The charming Alma BB handbag traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Epi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colors. The removable strap brings versality to the Alma BB, which can also be worn over the shoulder or across the body.
This cotton-jacquard summer stole displays an allover, contrasted Monogram print. Deep-dyed for saturated color, it's an easy-to-wear accessory for casual warm-weather looks.

This version of the LV Pyramide 40mm Belt combines natural calf leather with the House’s iconic Louis Vuitton graphic details for a signed and edgy look. The calf leather strap’s embossed Monogram pattern delivers a subtle Louis Vuitton signature. Meanwhile, the LV Pyramide buckle incorporates aged ruthenium finish for a distinctive visual touch.

The Tropical Flower collection reinterprets the Maison’s Monogram Flower signature with a Hawaiian inspiration, incorporating a strong surf culture feel. The three necklaces and the earring set are ideal to mix-and-match to create a personalized look.

In a nod to the House's heritage as trunk-maker to world travelers, the Fall-Winter 2018 collection accents the Alma BB handbag with luggage "stickers" inspired by classic Louis Vuitton signatures. Crafted from smooth Epi leather, this adorably sized bag features a removable strap that adjusts to waist or hip height.
This sophisticated shawl, woven with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern, is given a subtle shimmer by the use of a soft shine yarn.

Fast Flower reinterprets the Maison's iconic Monogram Flower in pure and graphic lines, tinted with Art Deco. Illuminated by the sparkle of strass, these feminine earrings are the perfect complement for evening looks.

Here’s a new twist for the elegant Capucines: a gleaming “necklace” of golden studs and eyelets, inspired by the fittings on classic Louis Vuitton trunks. Edgy and sophisticated, this BB model is crafted of full-grain Taurillon skin in glamorous red Rubis.    Please call 1.866.VUITTON for availability.

House signatures abound on this new bracelet: Monogram canvas, the Monogram Flower, a padlock with LV Initials and engraved studs all refer to Louis Vuitton’s heritage and craftsmanship. Lined in colored calf, this cuff is elegant yet easy to wear.
Worn crossed over a winter coat, this luxurious mink scarf printed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern is both timelessly elegant and fashionably modern.

Iconic symbols from Louis Vuitton collections mix and merge with the Monogram pattern in the Pop Confidential bandeau. The new lively print lends this piece a playful and feminine dimension. Crafted in pure silk, it adds a feeling of luxury to each wear. This versatile accessory makes a great gift for Monogram fans.

The Surene BB handbag in Monogram canvas and grained calf leather with a gold-color sliding chain is Louis Vuitton’s new chain bag. Its sleek shape is enlivened with gold-color hardware and the generous use of leather trim. The perfect casual-chic bag, it is lightweight, versatile, body-friendly and easy to wear.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

Crafted of supremely supple Monogram Empreinte leather, the Ponthieu shoulder tote makes a stylish daily companion. Effortlessly chic (note the hoop detail on the handles and signature zip pulls), it is versatile too, with a removable strap for cross-body wear.

These on-trend “mask” sunglasses are adorned with metal Monogram Flower inserts fitted into the lenses, for a luxe, “crafted” touch. Lightweight, protective and easy to wear, the Purple Rain model is offered in a range of fashionable colors.

These aviator-style Clockwise sunglasses have a modern look thanks to a rimless frame and a flat front. They feature a double bar at the brow, LV Initials engraved on the end pieces and the Louis Vuitton logo at the temples. The metal elements are contrasted with colored gradient mirror or signature Monogram lenses.

The Damier Black Chain Bracelet reinterprets the House’s emblematic Damier pattern as a modern graphic motif. Precise craftsmanship makes its black enameled lines stand out against a silver background, with a Louis Vuitton signature adding a sleek branded touch. A fluid piece, it will complement any masculine outfit.

Louis Vuitton's Pochette Jour is large enough to hold a laptop easily. This new version in Damier Graphite offers more capacity and a very large opening. This supple and versatile design can be carried as a clutch or a document portfolio, or slipped inside a larger bag.

As part of the LV Stories seasonal collection, the iPhone X & XS Folio in black Epi leather is decorated with carefully crafted, brightly colored patches, some of which playfully reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage. This protective case has a functional adhesive surface to hold the phone securely.

Showcasing the fluorescent colors that are a key theme of the Fall/Winter 18 collection, the LV Fluo Necklace Charms is a fun piece for fashion-forward customers. Fluorescent leather on the pendant contrasts with the shiny silver-color finish for a sophisticated hand feel and masculine look. The yellow and orange colors are a perfect match for this season’s Leather Goods and Accessories.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day.

Crafted in bold, contrasting colors of Epi leather this tote combines distinctive design and flawless functionality. The outside pocket features a double-zip closure with signature leather pulls; inside, three compartments keep belongings in order. The two Toron handles and detachable strap offer multiple carry options.   Reserve now by calling Client Services at +1.866.VUITTON

With its chunky knit in pure wool, Louis Vuitton's Morningram hat is a warm and stylish option on cold days. The design features a beige pompom and Monogram Flowers on a black background for a look that is both feminine and easy to coordinate. It can be teamed with the matching Morningram scarf and gloves.

The LV Circle bag charm and key holder brings together iconic Epi leather and LV Initials to create a signature piece. Bright orange-coloring contrasts with the blue edge-dying for a vibrant finish. The small size makes for a portable bag charm or easily pocketable key holder.

The Pochette Félicie looks elegant in glossy Monogram Vernis patent leather, which is embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern. This adaptable, envelope-style design, which features two removable inside pockets and a removable metal chain, can be worn on the shoulder or hand-carried as a clutch.

Feminine and functional, this card holder in Monogram Empreinte leather is the perfect daily companion. Its ultra-slim format with a secure press stud closure makes it ideal for holding the daily essentials.

The Astrid is an elegant one-handled city bag in delicate grained leather with a smooth leather stripe. Its structured shape and new signature metallic Monogram Flower lock make it a very practical yet ultra-desirable choice.

Crafted in supple leather and bearing the discreet LV Twist Lock signature, the Lockme Backpack completes the Lockme Family with a fresh new shape. Lightweight and feminine, it is a youthful daily companion for active women: carry it on a single shoulder as a handbag or go for more functionality by wearing it as a backpack.

The Pochette Félicie in Monogram Empreinte leather is embossed with Louis Vuitton's emblematic Monogram pattern. The envelope-style design features two removable inside pockets and a removable gold-color chain, and can be worn on the shoulder or hand-carried as a clutch.

Crafted in luxurious silk, the That's a Wrap square evocatively illustrates the rich trunk-making history of Louis Vuitton. Leather goods, jewelry and iconic House symbols are interwoven creating a colorful graphic print. The merging of modern accents and classic elements gives this travel-inspired scarf timeless appeal.

The compact Croisette handbag is reinterpreted in Damier Ebene canvas accented with playful luggage “stickers”, evoking the House's historic connection to luxury travel. Gold-color hardware and a removable tassel in smooth leather complete the elegant classism of this flawless top-handle bag. The removable strap adds an over-the-shoulder carry option.

The renowned padlock from Louis Vuitton’s trunks echoes the House’s travel heritage in the LV Stone necklace. It features smooth Tiger's Eye stone embedded into silver-color metal and the LV Initials signature engraved on the back. Natural variations in the stone make each piece unique.

The LV Explorer square celebrates the art of travel with a playful pattern. Inspired by the lining in one of Louis Vuitton's trunks, the design combines exotic accents with the Monogram Flower print for a romantic finish. This versatile piece can be worn around the neck or as a statement headband.
Stylish and sporty in Damier Infini leather, the Discovery Clutch is the perfect size for transporting documents and other belongings, it can be hand-carried or slipped inside a larger bag.

This version of the LV Pyramide 40mm Belt combines natural calf leather with the House’s iconic Louis Vuitton graphic details for a signed and edgy look. The calf leather strap’s embossed Monogram pattern delivers a subtle Louis Vuitton signature. Meanwhile, the LV Pyramide buckle incorporates aged ruthenium finish for a distinctive visual touch.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's fold-over Rivets Chain wallet boasts an array of practical features, including credit card slots, a coin compartment and a removable chain with a key holder.

Floral motifs inspired by 18th-century French tapestries were a strong story at the SS18 show. Transposed onto lightweight shawls, the colorful patterns make a romantic style statement. Offered in white, for a fresh signature, or black, for day-to-evening elegance.

Available in timeless black or vivid Coquelicot, this reversible belt offers a choice between iconic Epi leather and Monogram canvas for a more casual look. The new LV Circle buckle adds an extra signature touch.
Bold animal prints combine with the Monogram pattern and House signatures for this new stole. Fully 2 meters in length, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth.

The Coin Card Holder in Damier Graphite canvas is the ideal solution to keep payment essentials in one safe place. Its neat, slim-line design features credit card slots, a zipped coin pocket and a compartment for banknotes.The black leather lining coordinates stylishly with the black and gray canvas.

The Oliver briefcase, crafted from signature Epi leather, combines elegant details with contemporary lines for a refined business-to-city bag that accommodates office paperwork as well as a laptop in a separate padded compartment. The Oliver can be carried by hand, over the shoulder or cross-body on the detachable leather strap.

Following on from the success of the Monogram Split motif, the LV Split hat is a truly bold design. Featuring a Louis Vuitton signature that appears split down the middle, with each half in contrasting tones, the pure wool composition makes it soft to the touch. For a coordinated look, it can be worn with the matching gloves and scarf.

This new jacquard shawl in a silk-wool blend features an oversize, high-contrast Monogram motif. Worn looped around the neck, its soft folds and graphic pattern lend effortless style to any look. Offered in edgy Silver, feminine Light Pink or fashionable Neon Pink.

The Venice Key Pouch is part of a seasonal collection combining glossy Vernis Miroir patent leather with iconic Monogram canvas for a fresh, summery look. Both stylish and practical, this zip-up key holder can carry cash as well as keys, and may be attached to a bag thanks to its metal hook and chain.
Get ready to turn heads with this totally on-trend Twist Tote and its perfect combination of modern lines and luxurious details like the iconic LV Twist-lock and très chic side-body straps.

This compact Danube PM crafted of Monogram Eclipse canvas features a new version of Vivienne, the Louis Vuitton mascot, drawn by Kim Jones expressly for the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection. A sleek city bag accented with black and green hardware, the Danube is equipped with an adjustable textile strap for shoulder- or cross-body carry.

The Maverick bow tie is a member of an evening capsule collection featuring a reinterpretation of the Damier pattern. Catching the eye with an interplay of shiny and matte elements, the pure silk piece offers a flourish to tuxedo looks.
The Brazza wallet is highly functional with its numerous credit cards slots and bills compartements. In emblematic Taiga leather, it is given a playful twist with a bold Hawaiian-print lining.

The matte black Ardillon buckle of the Voyager belt epitomizes the masculine elegance of this belt. Urban and contemporary, the belt is a statement piece. It is finished with meticulously crafted details that pay homage to the rich heritage of the House.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.

For Fall 2018, Louis Vuitton surprises with this Sarah Wallet crafted from historic Damier Ebene canvas: the famous pattern is rotated and decorated with ingeniously placed studs, forming a V on the front. The lining in Cerise red brings a discreet touch of color to one of the House’s most classic envelope-style wallets.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The PM model has a detachable strap for cross-body carry.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. The Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format.

This Twist Chain wallet is part of the LV Stories seasonal collection, which is a playful tribute to Louis Vuitton's travel and trunk-making heritage. Crafted from black Epi leather, it is decorated with colorful patches in materials including iconic Monogram canvas. The Twist Chain can be used as a clutch or a small shoulder bag.

This reversible piece provides two belts in one, with its colored Monogram Illusion and timeless black calf leather. Featuring a graphic LV Pyramide buckle, it is a modern branded accessory to brighten up any outfit.

This Very Messenger handbag is fashioned from a combination of smooth leather and grained leather with a discreet Monogram pattern. Signed with a gold-color chain and Vuitton "V,"it is body friendly, lightweight, and easily holds all daily essentials. The adjustable strap allows for a hands-free cross-body carry or long shoulder wear.
This woven piece reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic V signature in a luxurious heavy jacquard. Available in a range of classic colours, it will brighten up both business looks and special occasions.

The iPhone X & XS Folio is crafted from gray Monogram Titanium canvas, one of the key materials of Louis Vuitton's Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. The functional adhesive surface, integrated into the slim design of the case, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of everyday life.
This envelope-style Sarah wallet combines an elegant exterior in Epi leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

Louis Vuitton brings the discreet charm of Monogram Empreinte leather to the 6-Key Holder. Embossed with the House’s iconic Monogram pattern and featuring gold-color hardware, it can hold six keys and includes a flat pocket.

The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour strap totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

Slender by name, slender by nature. Compact and slim, the Slender Wallet carries all the essentials and still fits into a front or back pocket with ease. This version in Damier Graphite canvas is energized by a playful touch of blue.

A genuine fashion statement, this new Reverso model associates two new Monogram canvas colors with more classic versions for a strong visual effect. Fully reversible, it will complement both daring looks and more casual styles.

The envelope-style Sarah Wallet in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather has an ingeniously designed interior, featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots. As with all drummed leathers, Monogram Empreinte becomes slightly more supple with use.

In a tribute to Louis Vuitton's metalwork savoir-faire, this graphic bracelet reinterprets the lozine details from the Maison's historic trunks. With its open cuff design, it is an iconic and rich fashion piece.
This must-have piece features the easy-going Monogram Eclipse motif as an all-over design, with a textured effect recalling the original canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for any look.
Inspired by the iconic studs from Louis Vuitton's trunks, this must-have ring is a twisted classic. It can be customized using replacement palladium and pink gold studs to make your piece unique.

Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers. It is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men.

The Studdy bracelet, studs and box nod to the iconic embellishments found on the House's historical trunks. Each piece is engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature and affixed to coated Monogram canvas. An additional silver-color and pink gold-color stud is included in the set for customization, along with a mirrored box.

This Oliver briefcase is made from Damier Cobalt, trimmed in leather and accented with silver metal hardware. A contemporary business bag, it holds A4 documents and a laptop in a separate padded compartment. It also works as a city bag, with multiple sections for personal belongings. The detachable shoulder strap provides convenient hands-free carry.

model: CARRE G.THAT S A WRAP BIJ.
en_US_description: Inspired by the House's heritage, the That's a Wrap! giant square features an array of iconic Louis Vuitton motifs, including trunks, keys and designs from the Essential V line. The large design is embellished with Monogram Flowers, metallic threads and sequins for a glittering finish. A fringed border and Louis Vuitton signature ensure this pure silk scarf remains elegant.

The Louis Vuitton Flower Studs story comes to the Capucines Wallet in Taurillon leather this season. Adorned with a row of printed Monogram Flowers surrounded by metallic studs and a gold-color LV Initials clasp, partially covered in leather, this classic wallet has never looked so fresh.

The Digit bracelet for men in Louis Vuitton's classic Taiga leather features an innovative industrial-inspired closure which interprets the Damier pattern in 3D. The easy-to-open clasp is engraved with the LV initials.

The ideal evening companion, the Soft clutch in sensual calf leather combines style and convenience. Its supple, body-friendly shape is enhanced by emblematic Louis Vuitton details: an LV turn-lock closure and removable nautical-inspired chain.

With its finely crafted details, the Dandy Briefcase PM in full-grain Taurillon leather is the very definition of business chic. Its keyholder in contrasting leather and double rivet signature add a dash of je ne sais quoi.

The LV Monkeys tie sports a pattern inspired by the Fall-Winter 2018-19 Pre-collection. Fused with the LV signature using an integrated print technique, this print has a playful aesthetic. It comes in classic navy, red, light pink or a summer-worthy coral.

Inspired by our historical Congo bag, this messenger bag in Epi leather is a trendy yet discreet everyday bag. It’s signed with the classic LV circle signature first used on our trunks and reimagined for the Fall/Winter 2017 show.

Coordinating with the Mylockme handbag, the Mylockme envelope wallet is embellished with multi-colored Monogram Flowers on a background of soft cream calf leather. A signature LV Initials accessory secures the flap. Inside, the wallet offers a variety of convenient features, including two roomy compartments and a zipped pocket for coins.

The LV Stories Box is an homage to the House’s travel and trunk-making heritage. Fashioned from Damier Ebene canvas and smooth leather trim, this adorable “miniature trunk” is covered in vintage-modern travel “stickers”. It can be carried as handbag or over the shoulder with the removable strap.
Real New Classic of the House, the Twist MM chain bag is the ideal size for a day-to-evening companion, worn either over the shoulder or cross-body on its long, sliding chain.

The Alexandre wallet in Damier Graphite canvas opens to reveal an electric-blue lining, which creates a striking contrast with the neutral black and gray of the outside. This long, slim-line wallet offers a variety of convenient features, including slots for credit cards and a zipped compartment for coins.

This must-have accessory offers a play on functionality that pays tribute to the innovative spirit of Louis Vuitton. Adorned with the Maison's iconic Monogram, the phone ring holder allows you to hold your phone easily and with style.

Inspired by the New Wave story, which plays with color and volume, the New Wave Dragonne Key Holder reimagines the iconic LV signature. A black tab in flexible calf leather is embossed with multi-colored lettering alongside the instantly recognizable Monogram Flowers. This playful keyring has a brass ring and engraved signature in a gold-color finish.

The Daily Monogram bracelet is a rigid open-back bracelet featuring Monogram Flowers in gold- or silver-tone metal on lacquer. It comes in an assortment of statement colors, making it ideal for collecting and gifting.

Now there’s wallet that fits perfectly into the House’s fashionable mini-handbags: the Twist XS Wallet in Epi leather with silver-color hardware. Nicolas Ghesquiere’s iconic Twist Lock has been resized, transformed into a small piece of jewelry, to give a precious touch to this extra small wallet.

This Twist MM handbag in Beige Tivoli Epi leather edged with black is a must-have.  Now established as the Louis Vuitton chain bag, the Twist is offered this season with a new leather strap, for more carry options. For day, it can be worn over the shoulder or cross-body. Held by the short chain handle (with the strap removed) the bag becomes an ideal accessory for evening looks.

The Marignan Messenger in Monogram canvas and grained leather is the quintessence of everything that makes Louis Vuitton bags the very definition of elegance. The on-trend colors will bring instantaneous modernity and freshness to any outfit.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

This Bond Street BB is fashioned in a harmonious combination of Damier Ebene canvas and Cuir Taurillon leather and is adorned with a leather nametag and an elegant central stripe signed Louis Vuitton. This one-handled bag offers multiple carry options: by hand, on the elbow with the top handle, or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap. Adorably compact, it’s large enough to carry essentials such as wallet, keys and phone.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Graceful MM looks fresh and feminine in supple Damier Azur canvas. This spacious hobo has a lightweight, body-friendly design that makes it perfect for every day. The flat handle sits easily on the shoulder, while emblematic details, such as the leather name tag, reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

It was on the Rue des Capucines in Paris that the first Louis Vuitton store opened its doors. As timeless as the House itself, the Capucines bag brings chic sophistication to any look. Full-grain Taurillon leather combines with precious python to create a luxurious handbag accented with heritage details: the LV initials, the distinctive side rings and the subtle Monogram flower on the closing flap. This Capucines PM comes with a removable shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

This LV City 35mm Reversible Belt combines plain calf leather with the House’s iconic Damier canvas to supply a choice of styles. The plain leather side is perfect for business occasions, while the reverse’s Damier canvas creates a more urban feel. The new LV buckle provides a tone-on-tone effect, while the 35mm width is ideal to wear with suits.

This pretty Monogram canvas box is decorated with a meticulously stitched Monogram flower motif in Epi leather, in colors inspired by Japanese cherry blossom. A perfect gift that can be used to store jewelry, trinkets, office supplies and many other items.

The Victorine Wallet, made from supple Monogram Empreinte leather, has been carefully designed to create a small wallet able to hold as much as a long one. Thanks to a protective coating, the leather resists scratches, rubbing and fading. This compact and practical wallet easily slips into any bag.
Complementing Louis Vuitton's Summer 2018 capsule collection, this surfboard key holder and bag charm in Damier Cobalt canvas features a playful jungle print and rainbow Louis Vuitton signature.

Crafted from Damier Graphite canvas, Louis Vuitton's Slender wallet opens to reveal a lining in electric-blue cowhide leather, which contrasts with its black and gray exterior. True to its name, this slim-line wallet holds payment essentials in a format that slips easily into a jacket or trouser pocket.

This playful edition of the Petite Malle is offered in Monogram canvas decorated with bold bright patches, featuring modern reinterpretations of historic Louis Vuitton symbols. Trimmed with leather, lined with calfskin, and accented with hardware, this elegant “little trunk” travels seamlessly from day to night.

This Surene MM handbag in Monogram canvas and grained calf leather, with colored-leather details on the sides and the name tag attached to the eyelet, is a functional and stylish chain bag. Big enough to fit A4 files and easy to wear thanks to the calf-leather shoulder pads on the two chains straps, the bag boasts a well-organized interior with three separate compartments.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.
A bright palladium finish gives the Essential V jewelry line a coolmodern look signed discretely. Featuring Louis Vuitton's graphic V motif, these ear studs are perfect for every day life.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel heritage, this stylish silk square is printed with a trompe-l'œil trunk in Monogram canvas, complete with colorful details such as a Louis Vuitton luggage label and brass hinges and corners.

A familiar pilot shape is reimagined with modern touches for Louis Vuitton's new aviator-style Grease sunglasses. The temples, keyhole nose and open-work top bar are crafted from polished gold-color metal for a luxury feel. Adjustable nose pads and flex hinges help ensure a comfortable fit.

A perfect match for the SS18 leather goods lines, this bag charm and key holder offers a graphic play on the iconic Monogram canvas. A perfect gift, it combines two variants of the season’s signature Monogram Eclipse with blue Monogram Pacific on the back.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's personalization stripes, the LV History tie strikes the perfect balance between sporty and refined. Two bold diagonals and the LV signature contrast against a plain background for a college-inspired feel. The tie blends with laid-back looks as well as more formal ensembles.

The ideal evening companion, the Soft clutch in sensual calf leather combines style and convenience. Its supple, body-friendly shape is enhanced by emblematic Louis Vuitton details: an LV turn-lock closure and removable nautical-inspired chain.

With its two removable interior pockets, the Pochette Felicie in Epi leather is the stylish solution to carry and organize your daily essentials. Much more than a wallet, it can be transformed into a glamorous shoulder bag or clutch thanks to its removable silver chain.

New for Spring 17, the Tuileries Besace mixes Monogram canvas with tricolor leather accents for a bold, fashion-forward look. Easy-chic every day bag, the Besace may be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body, thanks to a removable strap.

The Vivienne bag charm and key holder is inspired by its namesake, a friendly character who embodies the House's savoir faire. The adorable miniature Vivienne in natural wood and red resin, also has a dual function clasp. This charm is highly collectible and a keepsake to be treasured.
Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format. It looks modern and elegant in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.

This pocket square belongs to a capsule collection that features animals of the Chinese zodiac, constructed of Monogram and Damier motifs.
