The Damier Shuffle sunglasses stand out thanks to their lightweight structure and modern design in black and silver, featuring a distinctive double bridge and top bar engraved with Louis Vuitton's signature Damier pattern. The fashionable round shape, emphasized by the double rim, suits square and oval faces.

The blue-to-white gradient of the Capucines Cloudy evokes a calm and misty horizon. It is an elegant color story for a chic, versatile bag that will elevate every summer silhouette. Crafted of Taurillon leather, this PM model features an edge-dyed top handle and a removable strap for a crossbody carry.

Whether you’re looking for discreet fashion statement or just a versatile everyday bag, this sporty Outdoor Messenger is the great choice. Inspired by the Spring Summer 2018 Show, it’s fashioned in our suppler Taiga leather for a surprisingly body-friendly feel.

With its cool ”schoolbag” shape in a trendy small size, the Mylockme BB makes a big fashion statement. Crafted of soft calf leather, the bag’s long chain strap can be doubled for short-shoulder carry or worn cross-body. A sleek choice for every day, it has room for all the essentials.

Part of the family of bag charms celebrating the animals of the Chinese zodiac, the limited edition Pig Bag Charm and Key Holder features a cute padded pig crafted from Monogram canvas and calf leather. An homage to historic Louis Vuitton materials, the pig’s eye is formed by a classic stud reminiscent of those used on the House’s trunks.

Crafted with details that evoke our emblematic trunks, this Twist MM is right on trend for this summer. Iconic Epi leather mixes with Monogram canvas for a lightly signed option on this strong seasonal story.

This edition of the indispensable bumbag combines the House’s colorful signature Epi leather with Damier Graphite canvas in a playful patchwork pattern. A stylish addition to any casual look, this belt bag is practical, too, for keeping essential items close at hand and secure, with a zipped closure and silver-color metal buckle fastener.

Louis Vuitton invites you to travel with peace of mind, tracing your connected luggage in the main worldwide airports. Get notified on your smartphone or your Tambour Horizon after landing: to know whether your luggage has arrived in the right airport or not. The services are accessed exclusively by downloading and using the Louis Vuitton App application.

The quintessential evening accessory, this captivating Louise clutch is fashioned from satin-smooth calfskin and embellished with a sparkling, richly crafted signature lock. Faceted Swarovski® crystals in two brilliant hues are individually set around the gold-finished LV initials, for a precious effect as dazzling as a night in Paris.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy Organizer is revisited as part of the Epi Patchwork collection, combining blue and gray Epi leather with accents of Damier Graphite canvas. With its neat proportions and secure zip-around format, this organizer is the perfect solution to keep essential documents and payment methods in one place.

For a slightly more casual feel, this Armand Messenger PM with its crafted details is the modern choice for your new attaché. Very body-friendly thanks to the supple Taurillon leather, you can literally carry it all day every day.

Now there’s wallet that fits perfectly into the House’s fashionable mini-handbags: the Twist XS Wallet in Epi leather with silver-color hardware. Nicolas Ghesquiere’s iconic Twist Lock has been resized, transformed into a small piece of jewelry, to give a precious touch to this extra small wallet.
This ultra-feminine edition of the Twist bag is as fresh as it is stylish. The design blends vibrant colors and crafted details into a new and poetic take on the classic Monogram Flower motif.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this elegant wallet is crafted from supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature. The striking two-tone color scheme complements this sleek design, which is large enough to hold all the daily essentials.

Complementing Louis Vuitton's Summer 2018 capsule collection, this casual reversible belt in Damier Cobalt canvas offers two stylish looks in one: a rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on one side and a playful jungle print on the other.

The Pop Monogram Square in pure silk presents the season’s fresh twist on the iconic pattern. The central Monogram Flower is composed of a playful mix of straps, chains and locks – all historic House leatherwork signatures. Stripes and dots add a modern touch to this on-trend screen-printed scarf, an ideal gift for Monogram fans.

Crafted from Monogram Titanium canvas, which featured at the Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show, the Cosmos wallet is an elegant way to keep cash, cards, tickets and papers in one safe place. The gray canvas is complemented by a front pocket in Louis Vuitton's iconic natural cowhide leather, which is embossed with the House signature.
Perfect to twist a business look, this playful tie combines classic dots with a tone-on-tone trunks pattern symbolizing Louis Vuitton. Available in a range of classic colours, it is a perfect gift.

In a choice of two new colors, the LV Initiales belt is an update on a design from Louis Vuitton's permanent collection. It is crafted from Damier canvas with a calf leather border, in reference to the House's leather goods edit. LV Initials in silver-color brass, inlaid with lacquer, complete this refined piece.

The design of this LV List stole takes a cue from the season’s ready-to-wear collection. Woven of a luxe cashmere-and-silk blend, it is a soft, warm accessory, ideal for mid-season to winter wear. Its graphic good looks have a cool fashion edge, yet the stole is easy to wear and coordinate with virtually any look.

The Victorine Wallet, made from supple Monogram Empreinte leather, has been carefully designed to create a small wallet able to hold as much as a long one. Thanks to a protective coating, the leather resists scratches, rubbing and fading. This compact and practical wallet easily slips into any bag.

This reversible piece provides two belts in one, with its colored Monogram Illusion and timeless black calf leather. Featuring a graphic LV Pyramide buckle, it is a modern branded accessory to brighten up any outfit.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Slim and chic, the reversible Slender 35mm belt in Taiga leather comes in two timeless and versatile color combinations. The ideal accessory for business suits, it features a finely crafted ardillon buckle in silver-finished brass.

The new mix of Damier Ebene canvas and lightly grained calf leather produces an urban-chic model with a decidedly youthful, modern vibe. A casual style with a fashionable twist, the Clapton is compact yet it holds a long wallet, a phone and other essentials with ease.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Discovery Backpack in Monogram Eclipse canvas has a sporty vibe. Green and black hardware lends a stylish touch to this versatile bag equipped with multiple pockets and a secure hook-and-eye closure. Comfortable textile back straps and a top handle provide different carry options.

A soft, hexagonal shape gives the LV Chamade model an original twist. The faceted acetate frame is accented with iconic “trunk” studs and Essential V inserts on the temples. Offered in black or tortoise shell, this style can be fitted with corrective lenses.

With their round shape and mix-material structure, these Nue au Soleil sunglasses are highly in vogue. The tubular temples are detailed with the iconic Louis Vuitton Monogram, while the double bridge in gold-color metal creates a striking focal point. These sunglasses can be fitted with corrective lenses.

A luxurious way to stay warm and look cool, this winter stole is woven of softest cashmere and silk. The strong graphic design highlights the Louis V. signature as an allover, with a single element colored in a rainbow gradient. Offered in bold black with white or in off-white with gentle blue.

This Speedy 30 handbag spotlights the House’s travel legacy. Supple Damier Ebene canvas takes on a contemporary feel with printed and embroidered travel “stickers”. The top handles and a removable strap give this versatile bag multiple carry options.

Decorated with the iconic LV Circle signature first used on our historic trunks, this Bumbag is for the fashion conscious. Compact and crafted in supple Epi leather, it’s ideal for transporting your daily essentials.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this sporty piece features a pattern made up of colourful trunk stamps. Available in two colour options, it is a playful hat to wear alone or combined with its matching scarf.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle meticulously inlaid with a blue lacquered piece , this reversible belt offers two looks in one: graphic and iconic on the Damier canvas side, bold and stylish on the calf leather side.

The sweet Japanese treats known as “hanami” inspired the ultra-feminine details on this new Capucines model. The Monogram Flower is rendered in satin, lambskin and colorful beads, for a fresh, playful look that is totally in tune with spring silhouettes.

Crafted from Monogram Ink canvas, which was inspired by the Louis Vuitton archives, the Voyager belt coordinates with the accessories and leather goods collection. Complemented by a bold coral-color buckle, it is lined with calf leather and features a leather loop with an LV-engraved rivet.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.

The Filigram bracelet is defined by its delicate detailing. Crafted in a subtle mesh design evocative of lacework, the gold-color metal also features the classic LV Circle and Monogram Flower throughout. It is complemented with a golden clasp for the perfect fit and is part of a feminine range of coordinating accessories.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière introduces the Trunk Clutch in supple Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas, a soft-sided reinterpretation of the iconic Petite Malle. This soft-sided clutch continues Louis Vuitton’s reimagining of its heritage as trunk makers and boasts signature details like the S-lock clasp and a sheepskin interior lining with a Malletage print.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

The New Wave compact wallet is crafted from exceptionally smooth, supple calf leather, which is quilted with a wave pattern inspired by a historic Louis Vuitton trunk. Lightweight and space-efficient, this envelope-style wallet offers a variety of pockets and credit-card slots. The flap is signed with an iconic LV Initials accessory.

The Blooming Flowers BB bag charm and key holder is a nod to the distinctive Monogram Flowers print. The use of Epi leather, metal and Monogram coated canvas is a testament to the expertise of Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. This floral charm is the perfect size to hook onto the zipper of small leather goods.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.
This cotton-jacquard summer stole displays an allover, contrasted Monogram print. Deep-dyed for saturated color, it's an easy-to-wear accessory for casual warm-weather looks.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.

The Epi Patchwork edition of the Christopher backpack makes a strong style statement with a mix of richly colored leather and Damier Graphite canvas. Robust and functional, this PM model is equipped with adjustable shoulder straps, a top handle for another carry option, and multiple pockets, inside and out. The leather flap with a press-stud closure keeps belongings secure.

Big, bold polka dots team up with House signature straps, chains, locks and the LV Circle logo on this Monodots Monogram shawl. The four corners display variations in patterns and color, for a host of creative styling options. Jacquard-woven of silk and wool yarns, the shawl’s generous dimensions wrap the wearer in lightweight warmth.

This Voyager 35mm Belt gives pride of place to the new Monogram Titanium canvas, introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Lined with calf leather, it also features iconic natural leather details that will acquire a distinctive patina over time. The roller on the ardillon buckle is engraved with a discreet Louis Vuitton signature.

The LV Initiales reversible belt is a timeless and versatile piece. Honoring the history of Louis Vuitton, the Monogram canvas side captures the spirit of the House, whilst the burgundy calf leather on the reverse provides a contrasting look. A brass buckle with gold finishing crowns this chic belt.

Refined yet trendy, this necklace reinterprets the Maison's iconic Monogram motif. A flower-shaped pink quartz stone is mounted inside a metal frame engraved with the Monogram pattern, for a refined signature look.
Real New Classic of the House, the Twist MM chain bag is the ideal size for a day-to-evening companion, worn either over the shoulder or cross-body on its long, sliding chain.

A key story for SS 18, Monogram Blossom brings an arty new mood to the House’s iconic canvas. The flower appliqués in smooth black calfskin lend this Petite Malle an edgy allure. Inside, the luxe sheepskin lining features the signature Malletage pattern.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Mixing Iconic Epi leather with emblematic Monogram canvas and silver-color studs, this Twist MM handbag takes on a fashionable rock edge. Grained leather and coated canvas are stitched together to reproduce Vuitton's emblematic V signature in a perfectly symmetric pattern that stretches from the bag's flap to its body. This reimaging of one of the House's New Classics is a testament to the House’s inimitable leatherworking expertise.

This sophisticated shawl is a perfect day-to-evening piece that will match any outfit. Metallic gold studs complement glamorous black to make this collector's item a must-have for Monogram lovers everywhere.
Launched in Fall 2017, the St Sulpice is already a classic LV chain bag. The smart metallic lock, contrasting leather edging, and adorable size make this BB version your go-to everyday chic solution.

The Twist MM handbag debuts a fresh look for Winter 18. Fashioned from Epi leather and embellished with the signature Twist lock, it features a short chain handle braided with contrasting leather. A colorful LV charm adds a playful touch to this on-trend, crafted model. Both the charm and the leather shoulder strap are removable, for extra versatility.

Inspired by the Normandy bag, this soft and feminine wallet elegantly combines Louis Vuitton's historic Damier canvas with supple Taurillon calf leather. Its cleverly designed interior can hold everyday essentials.

The Daily Monogram bracelet is a rigid open-back bracelet featuring Monogram Flowers in gold- or silver-tone metal on lacquer. It comes in an assortment of statement colors, making it ideal for collecting and gifting.

The LV Circle reversible belt is a distinctive fashion accessory. Patent leather on one side, and the world-renowned Monogram canvas on the reverse, make this slim piece a versatile companion. A striking gold-color medallion buckle displays the iconic LV signature.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Keepall Bandouliere 50, the original soft travel bag, is revisited for this special edition in key materials from the Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. Here, it comes in high-gloss Monogram Glaze canvas and features natural cowhide-leather trim, textile handles and a removable shoulder strap embossed with the House signature.
The iconic Reykjavik scarf gets a luxurious revamp with this exceptional fur and cashmere piece. Embellished with generous fox fur, it will bring a daring touch of elegance to any wintry outfit.

From the pen of Kim Jones comes this iteration of Vivienne, the jaunty Louis Vuitton mascot. She lends her playful presence to a limited edition of the Clémence Notebook, available only in the season’s pop-up spaces. Crafted of Monogram Eclipse canvas, the notebook’s cover coordinates with leather goods and accessories presented at the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection show. An ideal gift for writers, doodlers and travelers.

A perfect (and perfectly feminine) bag for business, this functional tote is embellished with a distinctive Monogram Flower padlock in gleaming golden metal. The smooth leather handles and detachable strap provide a variety of carry options, and the well-organized interior easily holds files and a laptop.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Metis Wallet is crafted from supple Monogram Empreinte leather with the celebrated Monogram pattern embossed on the leather. It features Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock, inspired by the historic trunks. Its roomy interior boasts two large gusseted compartments and a zipped coin pocket.

The emblematic Twist Chain wallet in Epi leather is a stylish and versatile design which can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

A new take on Louis Vuitton’s Monogram ID theme, the LV Tab bag charm and key holder features iconic padlock details and a masculine design. Vibrant Lava orange Epi leather combines with laser-cut LV Initials to make a street-style statement. This versatile accessory functions as a bag charm or key holder.

A bold, contrasting LV Circle signature defines the two-tone Cardiff scarf. It is crafted from cozy wool and cashmere, which has been brushed and scratched for maximum softness, woven together using the jacquard technique. Fringed edges add contemporary flair to this versatile piece.

The Magic Monogram stole features the classic Monogram pattern combined with a romantic floral print for a feminine update. This reimagined style comes in three versatile hues to complement a variety of moods. Crafted with a hint of cashmere, the stole's generous dimensions make it a cozy accessory on cooler days.

A close look reveals that this Gambling stole is printed with new and archival House signatures, arranged in a playing-card pattern. Woven of a cotton-and-silk blend, this mid-season piece makes an on-trend addition to a casual masculine wardrobe. Generously sized, it can be styled in a number of different ways.

The Mylockme compact wallet in supple calf leather references the key signatures of the Lockme handbag: the envelope-style flap, the front pocket and the LV Initials accessory. Small enough to fit into any Lockme bag, this space-efficient design offers an array of pockets and credit card slots, including a zipped pocket for coins.

With their rich textures and distinctive Louis signature, these playful accessories will bring a trendy touch to any bag. Available in both leather and metal versions, they are a perfect match for the Maison’s ready-to-wear collections and shoes.

Introducing an exclusive capsule of silk-and-wool shawls: three different designs each feature an iconic animal and  signature motifs (LV initials, stripes  borrowed from historic trunks...) These collectible pieces add a cool, colorful flourish to casual or dressy looks.

The ultra-functional Zippy XL offers the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It is large enough to hold a smartphone (in a specific pocket), keys and passport, in addition to credit cards and cash. Elegant in Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, it can be carried by the handle for a sophisticated look.
The simple elegance of Epi leather. The peerless versatility of the Zippy wallet. The numerous card slots and compartments. The all-round zip. Quite the unbeatable combination.

The new mix of Damier Ebene canvas and lightly grained calf leather produces an urban-chic model with a decidedly youthful, modern vibe. A casual style with a fashionable twist, the Clapton is compact yet it holds a long wallet, a phone and other essentials with ease.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Beyond Monogram shawl offers a fun interpretation of a classic Louis Vuitton print. A graphic background featuring playful striped accents and contrasting large-scale Monogram motifs elevates the design. This soft silk-and-wool-blend accessory comes in a vibrant pink hue for a contemporary finish.

With its trendy, large pilot shape this lightweight, metal design is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes. The cutout V design on the bridge offers a distinctive branded signature with a contrasting matt/shiny effect. Mirror or more classic lenses available.

The Daily Confidential bracelet is crafted from calf leather and Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas for a two-tone effect. The materials are embellished with a metallic flower in a gold-color finish. A closer look at this new-season item reveals a clasp engraved in the House's iconic Monogram pattern.

Nicolas Ghesquière updated the Chantilly bag on its 40th anniversary. Made of Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas trimmed with calf leather, it features a redesigned, embellished padlock. An edgy piece with a boho-chic spirit, for day to after dark.

The soft white version of Romantic Blossom – a key motif for SS 18 – wraps this Petite Malle in delicate pink, blue and yellow flowers, printed on pristine Epi leather. This exclusive model can be carried as a clutch or worn hands-free, on a removable strap.

Coordinating with the Louis Vuitton leather goods collection, the Voyager belt in supple Monogram Eclipse canvas offers a smart-casual look. It is complemented by an LV-engraved metal buckle with a distinctive dark-green finish, and is fully lined with calf leather.

The Saint Michel bag combines two iconic materials - Monogram canvas and Epi leather - in a small, chic shape that is perfect for everyday essentials. The adjustable strap allows it to be carried on the shoulder or across the body, and its flap can be personalized with the owner's initials.

Edgy and versatile, this fashionable bandeaux celebrates the Maison's iconic Speedy bag. Like the other pieces in this exclusive capsule, it is a perfect gift that can be wrapped around the bag's handles or worn around the neck or wrist.

This Neverfull MM tote bag is fashioned of Monogram canvas and trimmed in natural leather. It pays tribute to the Louis Vuitton travel and trunk-making heritage with a mix of patches featuring House emblems, twisted in a playful and contemporary way. Spacious but not bulky, structured yet supple, the Neverfull is always exactly what you need it to be.

This edition of the Discovery Messenger PM is made from Dark Infinity calf leather, a material introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 show. Designed for cross-body carry, this compact model features a leather shoulder pad in Monogram Glaze coated canvas. Detailed with black-metal hardware, the bag is a stylish choice for every day.

For Fall-Winter 2018 Show Nicolas Ghesquière introduces a new nomade-shape: the Glasses Case handbag with the familiar Monogram print and a striking padlock closure. A mix of luxury materials, such as Epi leather and Monogram coated canvas, gives a luxurious feel. This bag is ideal for carrying essentials and can be worn across the body or on the shoulder thanks to the adjustable chain strap.

These Mascot Sunglasses combine trendy transparent mirror lenses with a design centered around the House’s iconic V signature. An intricate blend of acetate and metal, they are available in two stylish color combinations. Alongside the top bar’s metallic V and Monogram design, signatures include LV initials on the lenses and an engraved Louis Vuitton on the temples.

Influenced by the House's permanent Keep It collection, this stylish bracelet is a statement piece. The metal hardware is intricately engraved with the Louis Vuitton Paris signature. Crafted from Damier printed canvas, this bracelet is ideal as a statement accessory.

For summer, the graphic Monogram Confidential pattern is revamped in animal print to create the Leogram Confidential square. Tonal gray hues soften the eye-catching design, carefully screen printed on pure silk for an offbeat finish. Coordinating patterns can be found across the ready-to-wear and shoe lines.
Adorned with a bold camouflage pattern, this fashionable piece is ideal for a young and modern look. Available in two colour options, it coordinates perfectly with the Maison's shoe collection.
This fashion-forward piece is inspired by the season's Hawaiian theme. Available in five classic colours, the delicate floral will add a soft cool touch to any look.

Fashioned in classic Monogram canvas and signed with a “Louis Vuitton Paris” leather patch, this uber-functional Bumbag transforms sportwear into the very definition of casual chic. Wear it as a belt bag, cross-body or over the shoulder for a jauntier look.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

With details, such as silver studs, inspired by Louis Vuitton's trunk-making heritage, the Legacy Enchape bag charm and key holder evokes the spirit of travel. Smooth, calf leather tabs are expertly lined with the iconic Monogram canvas. Keys are secured on the ring, while the snap closure can be fixed to bags or clothing.

These square LV Player sunglasses present a sporty look with their laminated acetate frames, brow bar and two-tone color. Nods to the House's hallmarks include the Damier signature engraved on the temples and tips, a Louis Vuitton signature on the side and LV Initials on the lenses. Solid-colored sun lenses complete this elegant design.

Fashioned in Damier Azur coated canvas and leather patches adorned with trompe l'oeil screen prints of trunk corners and historic LV locks, this Speedy 30 is the very essence of LV style. For those who wish to flaunt their fashion credentials.

Floral prints take on a darker feel for Fall-Winter 2018 with the Twist MM handbag. Nicolas Ghesquière contrasts the vibrant blue Epi leather of this shoulder bag with intricate black and red flower motifs, resulting in an elegant design.

Bleached denim jeans inspired this new Monogram shawl. Silk and wool yarns are specially dyed to highlight the pattern’s contrast; the fabric is then screen-printed to create the “bleached” effect. It brings a touch of effortless cool to any casual look.

This casual-chic hobo style in the Maison’s iconic canvas features a Monogram Flower padlock in shiny golden metal – a distinctive new signature. Light, roomy and easy to open, the bag’s flat leather shoulder strap ensures comfortable all-day wear.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Pince wallet in stylish black and grey Damier Graphite canvas is an ultra-slim design that will slip easily into any pocket. In addition to four credit card slots and two flat pockets, it features an articulated silver-tone metal clip to securely hold banknotes or tickets.
The most stylish way to carry around money, cards and coins is the Zippy Wallet Vertical. In elegant smooth Taïga leather, it’s also supremely practical with numerous pockets and compartments.

The Pop Monogram Square in pure silk presents the season’s fresh twist on the iconic pattern. The central Monogram Flower is composed of a playful mix of straps, chains and locks – all historic House leatherwork signatures. Stripes and dots add a modern touch to this on-trend screen-printed scarf, an ideal gift for Monogram fans.

The elegant Mylockme wallet in soft calf leather echoes the sleek design of the Mylockme handbag collection. Its envelope-style flap is secured with an LV Initials accessory, while its practical interior includes two large compartments and several pockets. The flat front pocket offers easy access to items such as tickets.
This business buckle provides a perfect option for more understated looks. Coloured edge dying adds a twist to the Taiga leather strap, with an LV cutout contributing a subtle branded touch.

The Metropole belt in Monogram Ink canvas references a design found in the Louis Vuitton archives. Its distinctive buckle, in calf leather with a coral-colored metal frame, is printed with the LV Upside Down logo. This is one of the key themes of the season, interpreted across shoes, accessories and leather goods.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.
Adorned with a bold camouflage pattern, this fashionable scarf is ideal for a young and modern look. Available in two colour options, it coordinates perfectly with the Maison's shoe collection.

The Monodots pure-silk bandeau is patterned with two versions of the season’s Pop-inspired print. On the front, dots and stripes play with Monogram. On the back, Monogram Flower joins the mix for a fun, graphic effect. A stylish gift, this slim scarf can be wrapped around neck, head, wrist or waist or knotted on a bag.

With its finely crafted details, the Armand Briefcase in full-grain Taurillon leather is the very definition of business chic. As practical as it is elegant, it boasts multiple compartments, including a large zipped compartment in which to carry your laptop.
The iconic Stephen Sprouse leopard stole is reinterpreted with a blurry effect for an effortless elegance.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom on the front of this pure-silk screen-printed bandeau, with an allover Monogram pattern on the reverse. Available in a range of summery shades, this slim scarf can be styled in a variety of ways. Perfect for gifting.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.

Slim and sleek, with an inlaid LV clasp that lies flush to the strap, this new masculine bracelet is offered in black calfskin, Monogram or Monogram Eclipse coated canvas. All are calf-leather lined. Easy to wear, this signature piece makes a handsome little gift.

With its iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas sheathed directly onto metal, this must-have necklace has a sophisticated masculine feel. Like an amulet, its plate hinges open to provide its wearer with a secret hiding place.

Fashioned from smooth calf leather, quilted into a unique wave pattern, the Louis Vuitton New Wave Long Wallet is inspired by the disruptive music  genre from the 1980s. This long flap wallet has a large interior with multiple slots and pockets and a removable “Vuitton” embossed leather strap for clutch carry.

Featuring an embossed leaning LV Circle logo, this new interpretation of the Metropole belt is available in two colour options. Its iconic Epi leather is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's leather goods and shoe collections.

This belt showcases the Maison's LV Circle logo for a masculine piece that is ideal for fashionable street wear looks. It is available in a choice of Monogram canvases, complemented by different metal finishes.

Referencing Louis Vuitton's travel heritage, the Pochette Weekend clutch in iconic Monogram canvas is printed with bold trompe-l'œil details inspired by the historic trunks. It can also carried on the shoulder thanks to its removable chain. This collectible edition is part of the Trunk Summer 2018 theme encompassing shoes, accessories and leather goods.

Inspired by the traditional college backpack, this Discovery Backpack in supple Taiga leather is incredibly body-friendly. It’s perfect for any man looking for an understated yet sophisticated bag in which to carry his everyday essentials.

For Fall 2018, the Monogram canvas of the Sarah Wallet is livened up with bright patches that that bring a jolt of color to this classic envelope-style wallet. Each patch is a modern reimagining of a classic Louis Vuitton signature, such as the padlock and the LV initials. The cleverly designed interior features a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

Crafted from black Monogram Shadow calfskin, an exceptionally supple leather discreetly embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Discovery Pochette is an elegant way to carry documents and other essentials. This sleek pouch with its signature D-ring can be carried on its own or slipped inside another bag.

The LV Initiales reversible belt is a timeless and versatile piece. Honoring the history of Louis Vuitton, the Monogram canvas side captures the spirit of the House, whilst the burgundy calf leather on the reverse provides a contrasting look. A brass buckle with gold finishing crowns this chic belt.

Adorned with the iconic Monogram motif, these must-have bracelets coordinate perfectly with the palette of the season's ready-to-wear and leather goods. Easy to mix-and-match, they will add a touch of colour to any silhouette.

With its pure lines and sophisticated details, the Very Chain Bag in supple Cuir Plume and Cuir Ecume leathers is a must-have bag. The delicate chain and crafted V signature provide glamour while the flap and lock closure keep your essentials safe inside. Very body friendly, thanks to its soft feel and very light weight. The silky and very transparent leather played in contrasted with a small grained version lets discretly appear the Monogram pattern.

The LV Upside Down Brazza wallet in Monogram Ink canvas playfully inverts the iconic LV Initials, which are printed in a bright coral pink. The Brazza wallet is a sleek design whose well-organized interior features a range of different compartments and credit card slots, as well as a zipped coin pocket.

Adorned with the Maison's iconic LV Twist signature in a bi-galva finish, this is the ultimate accessory for a chic and easy look. Crafted from black calf leather, its metallic studs and eyelets are a perfect match for the season's leather goods and belts.

A statement piece from the SS 18 men's collection, this off-beat bucket hat is made of Japanese-inspired Kuroki cotton denim, accented with two LV metal studs. With its vintage vibe, it makes a stylish summer accessory -- in the city or at the beach.

This must-have bracelet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram with refined lines of strass, for a perfect day-to-evening piece. Easy to mix-and-match and accumulate, it will add a sophisticated touch to any outfit.

Featuring the season’s statement print, the Pop Monogram stole strikes a playful note, its colorful dots and stripes mixed with the Monogram pattern. Woven of pure silk, it is airy and light, ideal for every season. A fashionable gift for Monogram lovers, the stole is finished with fringe and a printed “Louis Vuitton” signature.

Featuring both calf leather and edge-dyed Damier or Monogram canvas, the LV Treble bracelet pays homage to the House's esteemed leather goods. It is constructed from a trio of straps, braided together for a striking look. The piece is completed with a metal hook clasp in shimmering brass, with a silver-color finish.

Effortlessly practical, the Neverfull MM is an ideal tote whose laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag. This version with its trompe l'oeil LV trunk details brings a post-modern twist to a boldly versatile bag.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's classic Brazza wallet is an elegant, streamlined design with multiple practical features.

The emblematic Twist wallet is given a romantic touch with a rich floral embellishment inspired by Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers. Elegant and practical, it features the playful Twist turn-lock that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Edgy and daring, these new Split bracelets offer contrasting combinations of the Maison's iconic Monogram canvases for a unique bi-color effect. With their thin cord, they are ideal to mix-and-match and accumulate for a strong visual impact.

A recognizable pattern in a range of colors gives the Monogram Split pocket square versatility. Printed with the House's hallmark split Monogram Flowers emblem, this piece nods to Louis Vuitton heritage yet showcases a modern, easy-to-style appearance. The tie from the same range offers a complementary logo effect when paired.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.

The Venice bag is an eye-catching piece, crafted of  Monogram Vernis embossed patent leather. This glossy little model features reinforced contrasting corners, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Small enough for a great cross-body look, the Venice easily holds a smart phone, long wallet, lipstick and keys.

Romantic 18th-century floral motifs mix with modern House signatures on this silk bandeau, an accessory that will bring fresh, delicate color to any silhouette. Long and slim, it can be looped around the neck, worn on the head or around bag handles.

Inspired by the Maison’s trunks, the Twin Locks collection reinterprets the distinctive lock signature in a must-have jewelry range. The pieces offer a refined play on symmetry, with contrasting metallic finishes and decorative details.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Showcasing the brand new Monogram White canvas, this new animation of the Reverso buckle makes a strong fashion statement. The reversible option makes it two belts in one, with a summery white side complemented by casual navy.

The sporty chic solution for your daily adventures, this Discovery Messenger PM is remarkably comfortable to carry. Fashioned in extra supple Damier Infini leather, it’s a distinctively lowkey bag for the sophisticated man.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this sporty piece features an eye-catching pattern made up of colourful trunk stamps. Available in two colour options, it is a playful piece to wear alone or combined with its matching hat.

The LV Stories bag charm and key holder combines the House's iconic Monogram canvas with a playful motif. A perfect complement to leather bags, it features a colorful heart-and-dagger patch. The gold-tone metal snap hook closure is finished with signature Louis Vuitton engraving.

This elegant edition of the Kasai clutch is fashioned from black-dyed, full-grain Taurillon leather. Trimmed with cowhide leather and fitted with silver-metal hardware, it can be carried under the arm or worn around the wrist on its leather strap. With multiple pockets and 10 credit-card slots, this compact, zipped bag is roomy enough to stow a man’s daily essentials.

This Backpack features Vivienne, the Louis Vuitton mascot, in a version drawn by Kim Jones. Constructed of Monogram Eclipse canvas, it sports leather and textile trim for a city bag both sturdy and stylish. This exclusive edition is available only in pop-up stores (New Bond Street in the UK).

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.

The Morningram belt displays the Louis Vuitton signature on its elegant Monogram canvas strap. The versatile belt can be reversed, showcasing the stylish calf leather that gives the belt a new dimension. A bold brass buckle with gold-color finishing effortlessly completes the look.

The handles of classic House trunks inspired the Archive Slide bracelet, a new masculine talisman in black calf leather. The aged-metal fastener and accent are engraved, respectively, with the Louis Vuitton signature and LV Initials.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.

Made of colorful Taurillon skin in a charming BB size, the Capucines Flower Smile for Summer ’18 is embellished with leather Monogram Flowers and metal-studded Taïga leather patches. The motifs form a “V” for Vuitton along the top of the bag. The long strap, for shoulder or cross-body carry, is also accented with shiny golden Monogram blossoms.

This NéoNoé handbag is crafted of grained Epi leather with smooth leather trim and two eye-catching stripes which bring a fresh feel to the emblematic model. The two-tone stripe, a traversal theme seen on shoes at the Fall 2018 Collection, is a nod to the House’s trunk making and personalization Heritage. The Néonoé bucket bag can be carried over the shoulder with its adjustable strap or by hand, thanks to the removable top handle.

Crafted from Monogram Ink canvas, the LV Upside Down Multiple wallet is a playful design which turns the iconic LV Initials on their head and prints them in vibrant coral pink. Both stylish and practical, the Multiple wallet offers the benefit of a compact format, which nevertheless includes many user-friendly features.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle meticulously inlaid with a blue lacquered piece , this reversible belt offers two looks in one: graphic and iconic on the Damier canvas side, bold and stylish on the calf leather side.

Adorned with the Maison's iconic LV Twist signature in a bi-galva finish, this is the ultimate accessory for a chic and easy look. Crafted from black calf leather, its metallic studs and eyelets are a perfect match for the season's leather goods and belts.

In iconic Monogram canvas, the iPhone X & XS Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.

Influenced by the Monogram Split motif seen in the Spring-Summer 2018 collection, the Monogram Divide scarf is characterized by a two-tone pattern. It is crafted from pure cashmere for a luxuriously warm feel, and is bordered by a contrasting edge. Combined with the complementary hat, the scarf will lend any outfit a refined spirit.

Created for the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection, the Discovery Backpack in Monogram Ink canvas has a sporty silhouette, inspired by trekking gear. Boldly accented with pink and navy hardware, this model is equipped with comfortable textile straps, a top handle and multiple pockets. A stylish choice for men on the go.   Very limited quantities available. Please contact Client Services at +1.866.VUITTON for more details.

Louis Vuitton's classic Brazza wallet is an elegant, streamlined design with multiple practical features. It looks modern and stylish in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.

Featuring the season’s statement print, the Pop Monogram stole strikes a playful note, its colorful dots and stripes mixed with the Monogram pattern. Woven of pure silk, it is airy and light, ideal for every season. A fashionable gift for Monogram lovers, the stole is finished with fringe and a printed “Louis Vuitton” signature.

Personalise your belt with a wide selection of 17 leather straps, from the reversible iconic Taurillon and calf leather straps in classic or playful color combinations, to the non-reversible exotics in ostrich or crocodile. In one simple twist, you can quickly and easily change your LV Initiales buckle with a choice of 15 new redesigned pieces. With 255 possible combinations, My LV Belt ensures a unique and personalised belt adapted to each man’s individual taste.

This masculine accessory makes a strong fashion statement with its design inspired by ID plates. The iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas combines with trendy ruthenium finishing, in a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's leather goods.

The Logomania scarf is woven from a soft, warm blend of silk and wool using a jacquard technique to reproduce Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern. The combination of dark and lighter denim blue shades makes this a stylish and versatile accessory for every day. The scarf is finished with long fringes.

Louis Vuitton’s Neverfull MM handbag explores the House’s travel legacy with its modern take on vintage luggage “stickers”. A combination of smooth leather and Damier Ebene canvas with printed and embroidered patches create a playful feel. The bag’s side-leather laces and snap-hook closing keep essentials secure inside.

Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet is crafted from black Dark Infinity leather. This supple calfskin, which is embossed with the Louis Vuitton signature, made its debut at the Fall/Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. The compact Multiple wallet is small enough to fit a trouser pocket, yet still contains a variety of compartments and credit card slots.

Timeless design and up-to-date details make the Kleber in Epi leather a wardrobe essential for the active woman. Functional features combine with fashionable touches (note the LV signatures and bold colour story) for a business bag with exceptional cachet.
Compact and ingeniously designed, the Ariane wallet has multiple credit card slots and a wide variety of pockets. In Monogram Empreinte leather, it is both feminine and functional.

This masculine accessory makes a strong fashion statement with its design inspired by ID plates. The iconic Monogram canvas combines with shiny palladium finishing, in a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's leather goods.

This reversible belt features a new plaque buckle designed in trompe l'oeil to evoke a real see-through Petite Malle. Timeless black Epi leather is complemented by Damier canvas for a strong fashion statement.

The matte black Ardillon buckle of the Voyager belt epitomizes the masculine elegance of this belt. Urban and contemporary, the belt is a statement piece. It is finished with meticulously crafted details that pay homage to the rich heritage of the House.

Silvery rivets outline the flap and front of the season’s Mylockme Studs handbag. The metal brings extra edge to this sleek model, crafted from soft calf leather. Signed with an LV turn lock, it is an on-trend piece with a top handle for elbow- or hand-carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder or cross-body wear.

House history and craftsmanship shine in this Taurillon Initials model: bag with uptown NYC style, made of full-grain leather, embellished with a finely printed and stitched LV Circle emblem. For a slightly more casual feel, this Armand Messenger PM with its crafted details is the modern choice for your new attaché. Very body-friendly thanks to the supple Taurillon leather, you can literally carry it all day every day.

The playful animal prints on these new Animalle bandeaus are part of a collectible capsule, new this season. Woven of pure silk, the skinny scarves can be worn looped around the neck or knotted on the handles of a favorite bag. A very cool gift idea.

Wild feline prints and a host of House signatures – chains, padlocks, straps – emblazon this new bandeau. The reverse side features an all-over Monogram motif. Styled as a neck scarf or knotted on a bag, this pure-silk piece is effortlessly chic.

Mixing Iconic Epi leather with emblematic Monogram canvas and silver-color studs, this Twist MM handbag takes on a fashionable rock edge. Grained leather and coated canvas are stitched together to reproduce Vuitton's emblematic V signature in a perfectly symmetric pattern that stretches from the bag's flap to its body. This reimaging of one of the House's New Classics is a testament to the House’s inimitable leatherworking expertise.

Fashioned from smooth calf leather, quilted into a unique wave pattern, the Louis Vuitton New Wave Long Wallet is inspired by the disruptive music  genre from the 1980s. This long flap wallet has a large interior with multiple slots and pockets and a removable “Vuitton” embossed leather strap for clutch carry.

This Fluo city scarf from the Fall-Winter 2018 collection is signed “Louis” in giant, all-cap letters. Jacquard-woven from an extra-soft blend of wool and cashmere, it is a fashion-forward twist on a classic. Generously sized, it is long enough to loop stylishly around the neck.

This easy-to-wear style is a pure classic, perfect for every occasion. The new horn colour option adds diversity to the collection, while the square shape offers a trendy look for round and oval faces.

The elegant Mylockme wallet in soft calf leather echoes the sleek design of the Mylockme handbag collection. Its envelope-style flap is secured with an LV Initials accessory, while its practical interior includes two large compartments and several pockets. The flat front pocket offers easy access to items such as tickets.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. Crafted of grained Taurillon leather, this city bag that takes care of business, with ample room for papers and files.

This Petite Malle in supple Epi leather was inspired by custom trunks created for wealthy banker Albert Kahn in the early 20th century, personalized with his signature 3 white crosses. Timelessly elegant, it’s an exceptional small bag for evenings out.

For the Pre-collection Fall-Winter 2018, Louis Vuitton's Vivienne mascot has fun with one of the House's most iconic designs: the Keepall Bandoulière 50 travel bag. This timelessly stylish model in Monogram Eclipse canvas is playfully printed with the unmistakable figure of Vivienne and the slogan 'Louis Vuitton Forever'.

Featuring the Louis Vuitton baton signature, which was a standout at the Fall-Winter 2018 show, the Horizon City scarf has a contemporary look. Expertly made from a blend of cashmere and wool, this is a chic addition to any cold weather wardrobe.

The Daily Confidential bracelet is crafted from calf leather and Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas for a two-tone effect. The materials are embellished with a metallic flower in a gold-color finish. A closer look at this new-season item reveals a clasp engraved in the House's iconic Monogram pattern.

This stylish accessory, crafted from emblematic Taiga leather, is a tribute to Louis Vuitton's leather goods know-how. With its finely engraved snap hook and key ring, it can be used both as a key holder and a bag charm.

This colorful silk square reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. This elegant accessory will add a sophisticated, feminine touch to any outfit.

This sporty-chic piece plays on a mix of materials to offer a charms necklace based around the Maison's LV Initials signature. Available in all-black and colourblock versions, it can be adjusted using special sliding pieces.

Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet is an extremely compact design which slips easily into a jacket or trouser pocket, yet still offers a variety of practical features. This special edition is crafted from supple black Cuir Taurillon leather, characterized by its soft grain, and printed in bold blue with the iconic LV Circle signature.

The Pont Neuf belt echoes the famous Parisian bridge both in name and spirit. It features Louis Vuitton's seminal Damier canvas and gracefully contrasting red highlights for an extra visual element. The polished silver-tone buckle completes this multifaceted accessory.

A variation on a classic Louis Vuitton design, the Reykjavik Gradient scarf features a refined gradation effect in two feminine colorways: pastel pink and blue or easy to match grey and black. Soft and warm in pure cashmere, this sophisticated scarf is woven using a jacquard technique to create a large-scale version of the iconic Monogram pattern.

The Tuileries Besace mixes Monogram canvas with tricolor leather accents for a bold, fashion-forward look. Easy-chic every day bag, the Besace may be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body, thanks to a removable strap.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

Monogram canvas and smooth calfskin combine in the Saintonge, a compact bag with a youthful vibe. The leather lends contrast and volume to the design, and the tassels are a playful touch. With its top handle and long strap, the bag can be styled in different ways.

Each screen-printed dot on the new Kamondot pure-silk square displays an emblematic motif: LV initials or Monogram blossom. A spot-on fashion accessory, the scarf can be styled in any number of creative ways to brighten summery silhouettes.
This Pochette Voyage MM is energized by a playful touch of blue. It can be used as a bag in bag or hand-carried for a more modern, trendier look.

Crafted, playful details give this Twist PM bag a fresh look for Winter 18. Fashioned from Epi leather and signed with the namesake transformable lock, this Twist features a short chain handle braided with contrasting leather. A bold LV charm adds an extra touch of fun to this on-trend model. Both the charm and the leather shoulder strap are removable.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton’s origins as a luxury trunk maker, this one-handled Cherrywood BB handbag is fashioned from Monogram canvas combined with modern Miroir Vernis patent leather and natural cowhide details. Discreet signatures such as the emblematic tuck lock and embossed LV bring understated elegance. This versatile bag boasts a top handle and a hands-free cross-body carry option thanks to the removable and adjustable strap. Easy-to-wear and trendy, it is perfectly suited for shopping afternoons or day-to-evening use.

A familiar pilot shape is reimagined with modern touches for Louis Vuitton's new aviator-style Grease sunglasses. The temples, keyhole nose and open-work top bar are crafted from polished gold-color metal for a luxury feel. Adjustable nose pads and flex hinges help ensure a comfortable fit.

The Zippy Lockme wallet in supple calf leather combines the iconic design of the Zippy wallet with the key signatures of the fashionable Lockme collection: the LV Initials accessory and the front pocket offering easy access to items such as tickets. The Zippy Lockme contains numerous pockets and compartments within a secure, zip-around format.

The elegant Anton backpack makes a polished impression in any professional setting. Fashioned of durable Taiga leather, it features impeccably crafted heritage details: note the top handle, subtle tone-on-tone signature tab, and metal zip pulls.
These sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and gradient Monogram lenses. They are available in a rainbow of colors, with studs adding an extra signature detail.

This Voyager 35mm Belt gives pride of place to the new Monogram Titanium canvas, introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Lined with calf leather, it also features iconic natural leather details that will acquire a distinctive patina over time. The roller on the ardillon buckle is engraved with a discreet Louis Vuitton signature.

This limited-edition Toiletry Pouch in Damier Azur canvas belongs to the Resort 2018 collection. Each version is screen-printed with trompe-l'oeil details inspired by Louis Vuitton trunks, as well as the name of a glamorous resort in pink or blue. A chic travel companion, this wash bag offers a roomy interior and a washable lining.
Luxurious Epi leather makes the Neverfull MM suitable for every occasion. Effortlessly practical, it is an ideal tote or the laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag.

For Summer ’18 the Mylockme BB is embellished with a shower of colorful blooms, inspired by the iconic Monogram Flower. The leather blossoms are fastened to the soft calfskin with metal rivets, echoing the bag’s silver-finish LV Twist lock.
This iconic wallet just got an upgrade! Now with four additional credit card slots and a playful new colored lining, the Zippy Wallet in Damier Ebene canvas is more versatile than ever.
The Brazza Wallet is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men. It is a practical companion with several different pockets, slots and compartments.

The LV Capucines bag charm and key holder is inspired by its namesake handbag. The combination of metal and leather in the LV Initials signature is an ode to the heritage and expertise of the House. This elegant piece also features a dual function clasp.

Crafted from a soft wool and silk blend, the 2 in 1 Monogram shawl combines innovative technology and classic styling. Featuring a timeless tone-on-tone Monogram print, this cozy accessory has two faces, making it highly versatile. The stole can be worn over the shoulders or wrapped around the neck.

The Essential V bracelet spotlights the iconic V signature created by Nicolas Ghesquière for his debut collection for Louis Vuitton. This graphic motif is embellished with colored lacquer and studs inspired by the House's historic trunks. The supple chain closes with a clasp decorated with an LV Circle accessory.

The LV Initials tie features an intricate overlapping belt pattern, in recognition of the House's history of leather craftsmanship. With such a reference to the House's heritage, the tie is perfect for Louis Vuitton aficionados. This pure silk edition of the best-selling design, is available in a range of colors including navy, red and gray.

Influenced by the Spring-Summer 2018 show, the Monogram Divide hat carries the split logo style through to fall. The iconic Monogram pattern can be seen in two tonal colors, and can be worn with a matching scarf. Crafted from pure cashmere, it is an ideal accessory for cool weather.
This branded tie offers a fashion-forward mix of an iconic tone-on-tone Monogram motif with a twisted check design. Its subtle Louis Vuitton signature will accompany any business look.

This playful bag charms mixes pop orange, feminine pink and the iconic Monogram in a distinctly summery spirit. Highly collectible, it is inspired by the Maison’s archives and its historic travel DNA.

Edgy and arty, this colourful design will delight fashion-forward women with its tribute to the Cruise 18 collection's Japanese inspiration. Crafted from super light silk, its hand drawing is inspired by Japanese manga.

The Knotty Pearls choker combines a sleek single resin pearl with signature Louis Vuitton details such as the brass Monogram Flower crowns and Twist chain links. It features a black calf leather strap with refined hand-made knots that can be adjusted using the gold-colored chain link closure. This elegant choker is part of a matching jewelry line.

The Pochette Jour GM in Damier Graphite canvas is the large version of Louis Vuitton's versatile document portfolio. Its distinctive L-shaped zip opens to reveal an electric-blue lining in cowhide leather, which contrasts boldly with the black and gray exterior. This spacious pouch can also hold a laptop and may be used as a clutch.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Épi inspires Nicolas Ghesquière. His fresh interpretation of the Cluny bag will thrill aficionados of the signature House leather. The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless, the lively color palette totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

Part of the seasonal Wild capsule, the Zippy wallet takes up the leopard-print theme of Nicolas Ghesquière's Prefall 2018 collection, combining it with corduroy-styled leather and iconic Monogram canvas. Notable for its secure, zip-around design, the Zippy wallet contains an array of convenient pockets and compartments.

Playful patches depicting Louis Vuitton emblems, from the iconic padlock to the Monogram Flower, enliven the LV Stories Monogram shawl. The punchy Pop Art-style iconography brings historical House hallmarks into the present day. A coordinating theme can be seen across Leather Goods, accessories and shoes this season.
The Lorette embodies Louis Vuitton’s tradition of “travelling with style”: it’s easy-to-carry, roomy, and iconic. The handbag comes with a two-colored strap.

This summery silk-and-wool jacquard shawl is woven of tri-colored threads for a pleasing heathered effect. The allover contrasting Monogram pattern lends the piece a timeless appeal; the square shape makes it an easy-to-wear choice for any day of the week.

Blooming reinterprets the Maison's iconic LV Circle and Monogram Flower signatures as dangling charms. A perfect gift, this very feminine necklace is ideal to mix-and-match with other pieces from the collection.

These square LV Player sunglasses present a sporty look with their laminated acetate frames, brow bar and two-tone color. Nods to the House's hallmarks include the Damier signature engraved on the temples and tips, a Louis Vuitton signature on the side and LV Initials on the lenses. Solid-colored sun lenses complete this elegant design.

This LV City 35mm Reversible Belt combines plain calf leather with the House’s iconic Damier canvas to supply a choice of styles. The plain leather side is perfect for business occasions, while the reverse’s Damier canvas creates a more urban feel. The new LV buckle provides a tone-on-tone effect, while the 35mm width is ideal to wear with suits.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. The classic Brazza wallet is an elegant, streamlined design with multiple practical features.

The trompe l'oeil screen prints of trunk corners and historic locks that adorn the supple Monogram canvas make this NéoNoé a playful twist on LV heritage. As always, this is an on-trend bucket bag with an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.

Knitted from a wool blend, the Miss LV scarf features a refined allover pattern and an LV Circle signature. Gold-tone metal studs and gold-color Monogram Flowers enhance the design, creating a jewel-like finish. This elegant piece has generous proportions and is ideal for elevating winter outfits. A matching hat and mittens are available.
This envelope-style wallet combines an elegant exterior in Monogram canvas with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

With its two tiny name tags intricately engraved with the iconic Monogram pattern and LV Initials, the Nanogram bracelet is a distinctive piece for every day. Other key elements of the design include the contrasting gold and silver-color finishes, the supple ball chain and the clasp with its LV Circle accessory.

This playful bag charm is inspired by Vivienne, the friendly mascot who encapsulates Louis Vuitton's savoir-faire. Highly collectible, it features an adorable miniature Vivienne in bright pink resin and wood.

The Monogram Empreinte Blanche MM combines embossed and smooth cowhide in a perfectly proportioned shoulder bag. Supple leather and curvaceous lines make this roomy, comfortable model a casual-chic choice for everyday wear. The flap closure is embellished with a signature hook-and-leather detail. Equipped with a detachable and adjustable strap, the Blanche MM can be carried cross-body, for hands-free ease.

First created in Fall-Winter 2018, the Daily Confidential bracelet has been reworked in Rose Ballerine pink. It is crafted from patent leather and the House's classic Monogram canvas. A metallic folded flower in a gold-color finish fuses these materials together. The bracelet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Vernis Milkshake line of leather goods.

Function and fashion align with the Epi Mix bag charm and key holder in vibrant Lava orange with Oxford blue edge-dying. Iconic Damier or Monogram canvas and Epi leather coat either side of the tab for a resistant finish that will keep its shape. This versatile accessory can be used to keep keys together, or to decorate a bag.

Evocative of the personal touches historically added to Louis Vuitton luggage, the Paul LV Stories MM notebook cover features playful patches sewn onto traditional Monogram canvas. A luxury addition to a stationary collection, the inside of this notebook cover is lined with red leather. The gold-color metal S-lock fastens securely to keep the contents in place.

This Alma PM handbag in Monogram canvas and natural leather trim is decorated with prints and stamps stitched one by one onto the canvas base to form a vibrant mix of textures and contrasts. As on the season's shoes and accessories, the symbols on the patches are a contemporary reimagining of such classic House signatures as the padlock and LV Initials.

With its subtle tone-on-tone Monogram pattern in classic navy blue, the Nightfall stole is an elegant choice for evening or any special occasion. Woven of pure, luxurious cashmere yarns, the fabric is brushed for an extremely soft finish.

Inspired by the SS18 season's leather goods, this exclusive new version of the Maison's LV Initiales Double Monogram is perfect for edgy looks. The Split design associates contrasting Monogram canvases for a striking bi-color effect.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.

Bold, yet effortlessly elegant, the Louis Vuitton Monogram Split City scarf is inspired by the Spring-Summer 2018 show. Crafted from pure cashmere, it features a seamless blend of the Monogram print and the House's signature Split logo. This scarf is slightly oversized for a contemporary look.

With its generous dimensions and long fringes, the Morningram scarf is perfect for wrapping up in cold weather. In pure wool with a chunky knit, its romantic flowery  design in black and beige features Louis Vuitton's Monogram Flowers and LV Circle signature. The scarf is part of a complete set including a hat and gloves.

This Alma BB handbag is crafted of grained Epi leather with smooth leather trim and two eye-catching stripes. The two-tone stripe, a theme seen on shoes at the Fall 2018 Collection, is a nod to the House’s trunk making and personalization Heritage. Playful but practical, it easily holds keys, wallet, smartphone and lipstick. The removable strap brings versality to the Alma BB, which can also be worn over the shoulder or across the body.

The LV Initiales belt features elegant Louis Vuitton Epi leather and a matching tone-on-tone LV buckle. The monochrome effect of the belt create a contemporary look. Expertly crafted, the belt encapsulates the enduring values of style and quality that lie at the heart of Louis Vuitton.

The Monogram Vivienne Illustré bag charm and key holder in Monogram Eclipse canvas is printed with an image of Louis Vuitton's Vivienne mascot, recognizable for her Monogram Flower-shaped head and eye. This versatile accessory, which can serve as a key ring or bag ornament, coordinates with the Vivienne theme of the leather goods collection.
This envelope-style wallet combines an elegant exterior in Monogram canvas with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

This wallet in smooth Taiga leather is surprisingly compact and slim. It can carry all your essentials and still fit into a front or back pocket with ease. This model features a transparent window for your ID.

Featuring the Louis Vuitton baton signature, which was a standout at the Fall-Winter 2018 show, the Horizon City scarf has a contemporary look. Expertly made from a blend of cashmere and wool, this is a chic addition to any cold weather wardrobe.

This version of the LV Pyramide 40mm Belt combines natural calf leather with the House’s iconic Louis Vuitton graphic details for a signed and edgy look. The calf leather strap’s embossed Monogram pattern delivers a subtle Louis Vuitton signature. Meanwhile, the LV Pyramide buckle incorporates aged ruthenium finish for a distinctive visual touch.

The Monogram Classic tie in gray combines delicate craftsmanship with timeless House style. A dotted jacquard background sets off the Monogram print in a subtle combination. The fine silk creates a luxurious finish sure to complement any business outfit.

As part of the Epi Patchwork collection, the Pochette Voyage MM comes in blue and gray Epi leather accented with Damier Graphite canvas. This medium-sized document wallet with a secure zip closure can be carried on its own or slipped inside a larger bag when traveling. It contains a pocket and credit card slots.

Featuring a games board motif from the archives, the pure silk Jeu de Louis square vividly illustrates the history of Louis Vuitton. Hallmark prints including Damier and Monogram are mixed with playful symbols such as pawns and dice. The fun design retains all the qualities of an iconic accessory, making it a truly timeless piece.

A sartorial staple is reimagined in the Snowfall tie, using refined colors and a textured design. Contrasting dots and the Louis Vuitton signature top off the contemporary aesthetic. The piece comes in three winter-appropriate shades: khaki, burgundy and navy.

Effortlessly practical, the Neverfull MM is an ideal tote whose laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag. This version with its trompe l'oeil LV trunk details brings a post-modern twist to a boldly versatile bag.

Delicate perforations on the top and handle of the Capucines Sweet Brogues bag, crafted of Taurillon leather, create a Monogram Flower pattern that is enhanced by a contrast backing of light-colored lambskin. This feminine PM model is ideal for daily wear, either carried by hand or worn over the shoulder on its detachable strap.

In calf-lined Monogram canvas or punchy red Epi leather, the new Crazy In Lock bracelet wears a charming heart-shaped padlock, finely engraved with the LV Circle signature.  This feminine, collectible piece makes a most romantic little gift.

The iconic Zippy Wallet in Monogram Empreinte leather with a gold-color zipper is a study in understated style. Generous space and an all-round zip bring versatility. Compartments and pockets for credit cards, coins, and bills and notes make it extremely practical.

The Capucines Sweet Brogues compact wallet in soft Taurillon leather reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram Flowers in the spirit of the decorative perforations of brogue-style shoes. This wallet, which offers an array of pockets and credit card slots within a very space-efficient format, coordinates with the Capucines handbag.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy Organizer is a carry-all item. It easily holds a chequebook, plane tickets, papers, bills, coin, credits cards and a pen. The elegant twist between Black and Grey will bring a touch of brightness to the line.

Louis Vuitton crafted this Zippy Coin Purse in Monogram Empreinte leather with a subtle tone-on-tone Monogram pattern embossed on the leather. Compact and extremely practical, this multifunction coin purse houses change, credit cards, and folded banknotes.

This special edition of the compact Victorine wallet is part of the seasonal LV Stories collection, which was inspired by Louis Vuitton's tradition of travel and trunk-making. Crafted from Epi leather in pale-pink Rose Ballerine, it is embellished with silver-tone studs and colorful patches in materials including iconic Monogram canvas.

Part of the Epi Patchwork collection, Louis Vuitton's Pocket Organizer combines two iconic materials, grained Epi leather and Damier Graphite canvas, in an elegant harmony of gray tones. This neatly proportioned wallet offers a variety of pockets and credit card slots in an extremely compact format.

The Time Trunk Micro Boîte Chapeau purse is part of a collection referencing Louis Vuitton's Fall-Winter 2018-19 fashion show, at which Nicolas Ghesquière revisited the historic trunks. It is crafted from transformed Monogram canvas with trompe-l'œil detailing for a vintage look. This miniature hatbox can be hooked onto a bag or belt.

These Light Infinity Sunglasses combine a grey titanium frame - inspired by the Fall/Winter collection’s Landscape Crater print - with a cord whose fluorescent touches coordinate with the season’s accessories. Calf leather end tips provide a rich finish, while mat mirror lenses create a modern masculine feel. Fully adjustable, the cord can be detached to suit any occasion.

The glamorous Pallas BB combines iconic Monogram canvas with colourful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colourful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

Simple, yes, but very stylish, this new bracelet is crafted of braided calf leather in Navy or Chocolat. The barrel-shaped metal fastener bears the “Louis Vuitton” signature in finely engraved characters. Worn in multiples, it makes on-trend fashion statement.

The Fall-Winter 2018 Wild West theme lends inspiration to this LV Wild Reykjavik scarf, which is an update of a classic design. Made from refined cashmere wool, it features House motifs in the form of metallic embroidered patches. Detailing includes the discreet Monogram pattern and a contrasting Louis Vuitton signature.

The LV Stories Monogram shawl combines Pop Art iconography with motifs that represent the House's heritage. These colorful patches include Monogram Flowers, the iconic padlock and key, and travel-inspired words such as 'Volez', 'Voguez' and 'Voyagez'. Crafted from silk and wool, the scarf is woven in an allover Monogram jacquard with the Louis Vuitton signature placed near the fringed border.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The PM model has a detachable strap for cross-body carry.
The delicate studs and rivets around the flap and lively edge dyeing make this sleek Mylockme bag a study in rebel glamour. Rock and roll never looked so chic.

Inspired by the Art of Travel, the double-sided Time Trunk Monogram shawl features images of vintage trunk fittings on a background of Monogram jacquard. Actual metal studs heighten the print’s astonishing trompe-l’oeil effect. Woven of silk and wool, with a plain back, this enveloping shawl coordinates perfectly with the season’s leather goods.

The LV World bandeau highlights the House history of trunk-making and travel. Wild animal prints, a compass and the LV signature decorate this on-trend skinny scarf woven of pure silk in rich brown with golden details. A stylish gift idea, it can be worn in a number of fashionable ways.

This casual-chic hobo style in the Maison’s iconic canvas features a Monogram Flower padlock in shiny golden metal – a distinctive new signature. Light, roomy and easy to open, the bag’s flat leather shoulder strap ensures comfortable all-day wear.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

A tribute to the House's iconic creations, the Jeu de Louis BB Bandeau scarf features a motif of instantly recognizable accessories spanning Louis Vuitton history. Vivid colorways and a board-game-style print make for a playful piece crafted from pure silk. Art nouveau and Monogram Flowers inspired by the Asnières house add a romantic touch to the slim scarf.

The Karakoram pattern, created by Louis Vuitton in 1920 to celebrate the House's heritage of exploration and adventure, comes to Damier Ebene canvas for Fall-Winter 2018 with the Alma BB handbag. The vivid red grained leather and bright white border with engraved gold-color studs make this a strikingly bold top-handled bag.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Monogram canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom in lush profusion on this pure-silk screen-printed square. Mixed with signature House motifs, the florals compose a modern pattern, offered in fresh colors that are the perfect foil for neutral summer looks.
