These aviator-style Clockwise sunglasses have a modern look thanks to a rimless frame and a flat front. They feature a double bar at the brow, LV Initials engraved on the end pieces and the Louis Vuitton logo at the temples. The metal elements are contrasted with colored gradient mirror or signature Monogram lenses.

The LV City 35mm Reversible Belt offers a stylish choice between two different leather finishes. Plain calf leather on one side creates a sophisticated look, while the embossed Damier motif on the other provides a more branded option. The brand new LV buckle is the ideal width for suits and comes with shiny black ruthenium finish for a tone-on-tone effect.

The Cherrywood wallet is an elegant envelope style which combines iconic Monogram canvas with smooth patent calf leather. Its standout detail is a gold-color clasp inspired by the locks of historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Inside, this spacious and practical design offers multiple credit card slots, compartments for banknotes and a zipped pocket for coins.

The Louis Vuitton Wilderness scarf is a truly luxurious piece. Crafted from 100% rabbit fur using an intricate intarsia technique, this exceptionally soft scarf features the LV Initials signature. Inspired by the Fall-Winter 2013 show, it is a statement design.

The elegant, envelope-style Pallas wallet in Monogram canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by brightly colored leather trim. Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock guarantees security, while inside there is ample space for all everyday essentials.

Crafted from a soft wool and silk blend, the 2 in 1 Monogram shawl combines innovative technology and classic styling. Featuring a timeless tone-on-tone Monogram print, this cozy accessory has two faces, making it highly versatile. The stole can be worn over the shoulders or wrapped around the neck.

Stylish in Taiga leather, the Pochette Voyage can be carried in the hand or slipped inside a larger bag for travel. Spacious and structured, with a zip closure, inside pocket and credit card slots, this pouch can hold a variety of essentials, including a laptop and documents.

A graphic braided detail outlines the flap of this richly crafted Twist bag. New for Summer ’18, it is made of emblematic Epi leather, with a detachable strap that adjusts to several lengths. Carried by the short chain handle, it is perfect for evening wear.

Statement of Spring/Summer 2018, the Monogram Blossom story contrasts iconic Monogram canvas with an intriguing floral print, bringing a fashionable touch to the Pochette Félicie. The stylish solution to carry and organize daily essentials, it features two removable interior pockets and can be transformed into a shoulder bag thanks to its removable golden chain.
Inspired by the Spring-Summer 2018 show, this fun and colorful shoulder strap is the ideal way to refresh the look of your favorite Louis Vuitton bag.

The ladylike Cherrywood PM in glossy patent leather features a top handle and removable strap trimmed with Monogram canvas. A fashionable daily companion, it opens wide for easy access to the roomy interior. An embossed LV logo and heritage tuck lock are discreet yet distinctive signatures.
This business buckle provides a perfect option for more understated looks. Coloured edge dying adds a twist to the Taiga leather strap, with an LV cutout contributing a subtle branded touch.

Available in a rainbow of different lens colors, these stylish sunglasses are decorated with iconic studs that evoke the Maison's trunks: lining the edges of each sunlens, they highlight the design's perfect pilot shape.

Thin and feminine, this elegant belt pays tribute to the architecture of Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. Combining an engraved LV Malletier buckle with Epi leather or a choice of the Maison's most iconic canvases, it will add a touch of sophistication to any outfit.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.

Two iconic Louis Vuitton materials are combined in this Epi Patchwork version of the Pocket Organizer, as blue Epi calf leather contrasts with Monogram canvas. Notable for its extremely compact format, this neatly proportioned wallet, which is embossed with the LV initials, offers several pockets and credit card slots.

Influenced by the House's permanent Keep It collection, this stylish bracelet is a statement piece. The metal hardware is intricately engraved with the Louis Vuitton Paris signature. Crafted from Damier printed canvas, this bracelet is ideal as a statement accessory.

Signed with an LV Initials buckle in a coral finish, this 14mm Reversible Bracelet for men is crafted in Monogram Ink canvas and calf leather on one side and simple calf leather on the other. The pairing of a darker Monogram motif with supple calf leather is a theme found in many of the accessories of the Men's Fall 2018 Pre-collection.

The LV Initials tie features an intricate overlapping belt pattern, in recognition of the House's history of leather craftsmanship. With such a reference to the House's heritage, the tie is perfect for Louis Vuitton aficionados. This pure silk edition of the best-selling design, is available in a range of colors including navy, red and gray.

Introducing the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag MM, crafted from smooth quilted calfskin. On-trend details – a detachable handle signed “Louis Vuitton,” edgy hardware with an aged-metal finish – make this a statement piece that is also perfect for every day. The sliding chain adjusts the drop for long-, short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

Featuring the iconic Monogram motif, the Denim Monogram shawl is given a seasonal update with two fresh and feminine hues. Crafted from a soft blend of cotton and silk, both yarns are dyed to highlight the contrasting print. Effortlessly elegant, it can be showcased as a head scarf or worn around the neck.

Created for the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection, this model of the Danube city bag is fashioned of Monogram Shadow cowhide. Remarkably supple, the leather is embossed with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern. Black hardware and an adjustable strap complete the sleek and masculine look of this piece, designed for shoulder- or cross-body carry.

This slim-line version of the Danube city bag adds an on-trend touch to any casual outfit. Crafted from colorful Epi leather paired with Monogram canvas and set off by silver metal hardware, it is a compact yet functional model with an adjustable strap, wide zipped opening and convenient front pocket. An ideal companion for everyday wear.

A perfect match for this season's Monogram Constellation Denim ties, this pocket square offers an iconic motif in an easy-going and recognizable pattern. The red version coordinates with the season's other red pieces.

The LV Circle bag charm and key holder brings together iconic Epi leather and LV Initials to create a signature piece. Bright orange-coloring contrasts with the blue edge-dying for a vibrant finish. The small size makes for a portable bag charm or easily pocketable key holder.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. The compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

A seasonal capsule of pure-silk squares, featuring screen-printed animal figures in three exclusive designs. Each is framed with a signature "trunk" motif and finished with oversized LV initials. These collectible pieces add a playful touch to work, weekend or dressy looks.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom on the front of this pure-silk screen-printed bandeau, with an allover Monogram pattern on the reverse. Available in a range of summery shades, this slim scarf can be styled in a variety of ways. Perfect for gifting.
The Amerigo wallet combines timeless style with ultra-functionality. Its compact design is made of convenient features, while remaining slim enough to fit into a jeans back pocket.

This reversible piece provides two belts in one, with its colored Monogram Illusion and timeless black calf leather. Featuring a graphic LV Pyramide buckle, it is a modern branded accessory to brighten up any outfit.

Cute and compact, the Rosalie coin purse in Monogram canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by its colorful press stud and leather lining. Thanks to its tiny dimensions, it fits perfectly in a bag or even a coat pocket.

In Epi leather, the iPhone X & XS Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.

A genuine fashion statement, this new Reverso model associates two new Monogram canvas colors with more classic versions for a strong visual effect. Fully reversible, it will complement both daring looks and more casual styles.

Inspired by the Maison’s trunks, the Twin Locks collection reinterprets the distinctive lock signature in a must-have jewelry range. The pieces offer a refined play on symmetry, with contrasting metallic finishes and decorative details.

The Blanche BB handbag combines smooth and embossed Monogram Empreinte leather for a casual-chic signature piece that is perfect for daily wear. The secure closure is embellished with a finely crafted metal loop and leather detail. The bag’s leather strap adjusts to different lengths for a modern, hands-free shoulder or cross-body carry.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The MM model accommodates daily essentials as well as documents and files.
This bracelet in calf leather with colorful contrasting edges features a locking system inspired by the handles of historic Louis Vuitton trunks.

This Camera Bag is made from Monogram Titanium canvas, a material revealed at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 show. The strap features a shoulder pad embossed with a bold Louis Vuitton signature. A fashion-forward piece for men on the go, it can be worn cross-body or carried by the side handle, as seen on the runway.

For Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition of cute animals featuring iconic House signatures. This rabbit key holder and bag charm is crafted from Epi leather and Monogram canvas.

This pure-silk tie is part of a limited capsule, celebrating animals of the Chinese zodiac. Perfect for injecting a bit of fun into serious suiting, these pieces make thoughtful gifts. The same creatures also appear on the season’s leather goods and fashion jewelry – collectors should take note.

The Essential V bi-color ring plays with the graphic V signature created by Nicolas Ghesquière in his first fashion collection for Louis Vuitton. The bold design and bi-color finish of the metal make this a striking piece which can be worn alone or with other items from the collection.

The Logomania Shine scarf is a perfect way to brighten cold days. Its blend of wool, silk and lurex yarns creates a lustrous gold effect on a petrol blue base, while a jacquard technique is used to reproduce Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern for a bold signature look.

Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers. It is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men.
With its delicate blend of Taurillon leather and Damier Ebène canvas, the one-handled Bond Street is this season’s ultra-feminine must-have handbag. It is the very definition of understated luxury.

A perfect gift, these delicate Miss LV Hoop earrings feature the signature Louis Vuitton Monogram Flowers on the front. Crafted from enamel and metal, these timeless pieces are part of a range of matching accessories.

For Winter 18 this version of the Capucines PM handbag offers a playful message, executed with exacting workmanship. The top handle features an XOXO motif, created with delicately braided colored leather threads alternating with round metal studs. The embellishment lends a unique and on-trend crafted touch to this collectible piece, made from full-grain Taurillon leather lined with smooth calfskin.

Iconic House signatures combine to form a romantic floral pattern on this extra-soft summer-weight stole. Offered in fuchsia or light pink, this generously sized piece brings an air of effortless elegance to the season’s casual or dressed-up silhouettes.

Inspired by the SS18 season's leather goods, this exclusive new version of the Maison's LV Initiales Double Monogram is perfect for edgy looks. The Split design associates contrasting Monogram canvases for a striking bi-color effect.

The new Black Gravity Petite Malle in Epi leather, with its stunning mix of glossy and matte surfaces, was unveiled by Nicolas Ghesquière at the Fall 2018 Pre-collection. Using an innovative silkscreen printing technique, the House brings a striking 3D aspect to the black leather of the iconic Petite Malle. Its shiny black surface adds a touch of glamorous rock-and-roll attitude.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. Crafted of grained Taurillon leather, this city bag that takes care of business, with ample room for papers and files.

Monogram canvas and smooth calfskin combine in the Saintonge, a compact bag with a youthful vibe. The leather lends contrast and volume to the design, and the tassels are a playful touch. With its top handle and long strap, the bag can be styled in different ways.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.
Slender by name, slender by nature. This wallet in smooth Taiga leather is suitably compact and slim, will carry all the essentials and still fit into a front or back pocket with ease.

The Toiletry Pouch in Louis Vuitton's iconic Epi leather is a chic and practical travel companion. This wash bag offers a wide zippered opening and a roomy interior with enough space for a variety of beauty essentials, while its washable synthetic textile lining makes it easy to clean up any spills.

With different designs on the front and flip sides, the pure-silk Pop Monogram bandeau offers lots of styling options. The Pop-inspired patterns – a key statement this season – feature Monogram Flowers mixed with dots and stripes. This skinny scarf wraps around neck, wrist, head or bag handle. It makes a fashionable gift.

For Fall 2018 the House presents an evening version of the New Classic Twist MM handbag. Crafted from signature Epi leather in Bleu Boréal, a gleaming   metallic blue shade, this model features a jewel-like LV Twist lock and chain strap, both finished with a hypnotic “scarabeo” effect that changes color with the light, like a beetle’s wing.
This woven piece reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic V signature in a luxurious heavy jacquard. Available in a range of classic colours, it will brighten up both business looks and special occasions.

This versatile accessory offers a modern twist on the Maison’s classic motif. An ideal gift, it reinterprets the iconic Monogram canvas in silver to provide a perfect match for the Men’s SS18 leather goods lines.

Presenting the Carry All, inspired by the House travel heritage. Crafted of Monogram canvas with signature Toron leather handles and a removable leather strap, it is roomy and modern, ideal for day-to-business use. The golden chain adds a sophisticated touch.

The best-selling My Fair Lady model is now offered in two fashionable new color combinations. House signatures – note the Essential V metal inserts, iconic trunk studs at the front and LV Circle end tips – lend a special elegance to this ultra-feminine style.

For Valentine's Day, an adorable dog incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Zippy coin purse in Monogram canvas. This compact design, with its wide opening for easy access, will fit in any bag or pocket.

The House continues to reveal new facets of Vernis leather with an unexpected reinterpretation of one of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic shapes: the Alma BB. The audacious color and Monogram canvas trim gives it a stunningly disruptive feel.

The Fetish Flower bag charm and key holder is a playful take on the House's most iconic signature designs. It mixes sumptuous materials including Monogram canvas, Epi leather and metal hardware. This charm is expertly crafted and combines luxury leather techniques with perforation and double-facing.

The best-selling LV Confidential bracelet is now offered in a rainbow of new hues. In grained calf leather or Monogram canvas, they feature engraved metal fasteners with lacquer or gold-color finishes. Stacked, they make an eye-catching fashion statement.

The Monogram canvas disc of this finely crafted bag charm/key ring is embellished with a black-lacquer flower motif, a signature of the SS18 show. The reverse side, in black calf leather, can be hot-stamped with initials, for a thoughtful, personalized gift.

Functional and fashionable, the Light Infinity Dragonne Bag Charm And Key Holder evokes the colors and the spirit of the Men’s Fall/Winter 18 collection. Its nylon dragonne is embellished with a strip of calf leather, delicately embossed with Louis and Vuitton for a signed look. The titanium finish is a perfect match for the season’s Leather Goods.

Introducing the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag MM, crafted from smooth quilted calfskin. On-trend details – a detachable handle signed “Louis Vuitton,” edgy hardware with an aged-metal finish – make this a statement piece that is also perfect for every day. The sliding chain adjusts the drop for long-, short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

This new jacquard shawl in a silk-wool blend features an oversize, high-contrast Monogram motif. Worn looped around the neck, its soft folds and graphic pattern lend effortless style to any look. Offered in edgy Silver, feminine Light Pink or fashionable Neon Pink.

An openwork metal frame gives these cat-eye sunglasses a striking, on-trend allure. The Midnight in Paris model is embellished with a host of subtle yet unmistakable House signatures, including engraved studs, Monogram Flower details and LV Circle emblems.
These sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and gradient Monogram lenses. They are available in a rainbow of colors, with studs adding an extra signature detail.

Slim and sleek, with an inlaid LV clasp that lies flush to the strap, this new masculine bracelet is offered in black calfskin, Monogram or Monogram Eclipse coated canvas. All are calf-leather lined. Easy to wear, this signature piece makes a handsome little gift.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.

With a round shape and soft facet work on the frame, the La Piscine Studs sunglasses exude femininity. A floral pattern in gold detailing along the temples chimes with Louis Vuitton's Flower Studs story. Flexible hinges and a sculpted nose support help ensure a comfortable fit.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.

In a direct reference to the House’s trunkmaking heritage, the Victorine Wallet in Damier Ebene canvas is decorated with studs like those found on Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. Compact and ingenious, the Victorine’s interior holds almost as much as a long wallet.

This pretty Monogram canvas box is decorated with a meticulously stitched Monogram flower motif in Epi leather, in colors inspired by Japanese cherry blossom. A perfect gift that can be used to store jewelry, trinkets, office supplies and many other items.
This ultra-feminine edition of the Twist bag is as fresh as it is stylish. The design blends vibrant colors and crafted details into a new and poetic take on the classic Monogram Flower motif.

The House employs a special leatherwork technique to achieve the matte/glossy effect that makes this new golden Twist model so striking. Accented with a jewel-like LV lock, it brings full-on glamour to evening looks, carried by hand or in the crook of an elbow.

With their round shape and mix-material structure, these Nue au Soleil sunglasses are highly in vogue. The tubular temples are detailed with the iconic Louis Vuitton Monogram, while the double bridge in gold-color metal creates a striking focal point. These sunglasses can be fitted with corrective lenses.

Inspired by Nicolas Ghesquière's Essential V logo, these mask-shaped sunglasses create a statement look with wow effect. An engraved Monogram pattern on the end pieces and temples adds an iconic touch.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

Easy and accessible, this functional key holder offers a graphic play on colours with a contrasting lining adding a modern feel. Its two complementary version make a strong statement around the Maison's iconic Monogram canvas.

Presenting the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag PM, a statement piece destined to become a fashionable wardrobe staple. Made from smooth quilted calfskin, it features a removable handle with a colorful “Louis Vuitton” signature. An aged-metal finish adds richness to the bag’s hardware and sliding chain, which adapts to long- and short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

The Very bag charm and key holder spotlights the LV Circle signature, which is inlaid with colored enamel and embellished with a matching leather braid ending in two Monogram Flower charms. This intricate design references Louis Vuitton's heritage of craftsmanship and coordinates with the Very leather goods line.

For Fall 2018, the day-to-evening Twist MM takes on a poetic feel, thanks to printed Monogram Flowers in contrasting colors surrounded by metallic studs. The row of delicate blossoms highlights the Twist’s iconic lines and brings an inviting softness to the Epi leather’s appearance.

In fine-grained Taurillon leather, the Capucines Sweet Brogues wallet was inspired by the decorative perforations found on traditional brogue-style shoes. Here, they are given a feminine twist in the shape of Louis Vuitton's Monogram Flowers. Matching the iconic Capucines handbag, this wallet boasts a spacious interior with multiple practical features.

The Matchpoint collection mixes sporty details with luxury know-how on stylish designs adapted to the lifestyles of modern men. The Zippy Vertical wallet in Damier Coastline canvas contains many practical features in a compact zip-around format.

Showcasing the brand new Monogram White canvas, this new animation of the Reverso buckle makes a strong fashion statement. The reversible option makes it two belts in one, with a summery white side complemented by casual navy.
The Long Wallet is stylish, spacious and practical. Its durable yet supple Taïga leather and layered leather detailing inside give this generous wallet a sumptuous appeal.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colourful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Keeping pace with the demands of modern life, the Zippy Organizer wallet in contemporary Damier Graphite canvas combines style and practicality. Multiple credit card slots, a zipped coin pocket and two spacious compartments for bills and travel documents are just some of the user-friendly features contained within its compact dimensions.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The PM model has a detachable strap for cross-body carry.

The Zoé wallet is the perfect mini companion: small enough to fit into even a tiny bag or clutch, yet spacious enough to hold coins, notes and credit cards. Its appeal is enhanced by its stylish combination of Monogram canvas and colored leather, finished off with a gold-tone Louis Vuitton press-stud.

This season, the iconic Keepall 55, Louis Vuitton’s original soft travel bag, is fashioned from iconic Monogram canvas embellished with colorful patches. Sewn, printed and embroidered onto the canvas, each patch design is a nod to the House’s  emblematic signatures, twisted in a playful and contemporary way.

The Blanche BB handbag combines smooth and embossed Monogram Empreinte leather for a casual-chic signature piece that is perfect for daily wear. The secure closure is embellished with a finely crafted metal loop and leather detail. The bag’s leather strap adjusts to different lengths for a modern, hands-free shoulder or cross-body carry.

An openwork metal frame gives these cat-eye sunglasses a striking, on-trend allure. The Midnight in Paris model is embellished with a host of subtle yet unmistakable House signatures, including engraved studs, Monogram Flower details and LV Circle emblems.

For the Epi Blooming Corners limited edition, the Clémence wallet comes in Epi leather with contrasting Monogram flower-shaped corners. This detail, which was inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks, brings a fresh, playful note to this elegant long wallet, whose secure zip-around format conceals a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The Millefeuille Tote proves that it is indeed possible for a bag to be both timeless and modern. Its bold mix of color and iconic Monogram canvas combined with luxurious details make this functional bag remarkably stylish.

Named for its distinctive House detailing, the LV Iconic 35mm belt features a large gold-color LV logo at the buckle. The black calf leather strap is detailed with gold-tone studs, in either a Monogram Flower motif or a dotted line, both creating a striking look.

To celebrate Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition featuring cute, nature-inspired scenes incorporating key House signatures. A perfect gift, the Pochette Felicie is the stylish solution to carry daily essentials, and can be transformed into a shoulder bag thanks to its removable chain.

The Capucines shows a stylish new twist this season: the now-classic bag is embellished with a stud-and-eyelet “necklace” wrought of gleaming golden metal. This elegant and practical PM model is crafted of Taurillon skin in timeless, go-everywhere Noir.
Worn crossed over a winter coat, this luxurious mink scarf printed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern is both timelessly elegant and fashionably modern.

For Summer ‘18 the House presents Flower Smile, an exquisitely made edition of the Capucines. Monogram Flowers crafted from Taurillon skin alternate with metal-studded Taïga leather patches, forming the iconic “V” for Vuitton. The detachable shoulder strap of the PM model is accented with shiny golden Monogram blossoms.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière reinterprets the iconic Petite Malle with this Trunk Clutch in supple Epi leather. This soft-sided clutch continues Louis Vuitton’s reimagining of its heritage as trunk makers and boasts signature details such as the S-lock clasp and a sheepskin interior lining with a Malletage print

These LV Showdown Sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and light rimless structure. Thin all-metal temples create a hyper-modern feel, while specific Monogram lenses inject a unique touch of branding. Engraved LV initials and Louis Vuitton signatures supply the finishing touches for this fashion-forward piece.

Refined and sophisticated, this timeless stole is a must-have for any wardrobe. Woven from precious cashmere, it is a perfect day-to-evening companion that will match both casual and more elegant looks.

The small LV Upside Down Discovery Pochette in Monogram Ink canvas is a versatile accessory which can be carried as a clutch to hold a smartphone, cards and cash, or used as a bag in a bag. This colorful design is printed with the upside-down LV Initials in coral pink and features coordinating hardware.

This adorable version of the ladylike Alma in grained Epi leather is a versatile day-to-evening piece. Trendy yet timeless, it features a long strap – perfect for cross-body wear – adorned with a golden-chain detail. Signatures include an embossed LV logo and a “Louis Vuitton Paris” patch.

A host of glossy resin “bubbles” adorns this new version of the Twist. Each jewel-like cabochon is inlaid with a Monogram Flower against a holographic background, for a mesmerizing effect. In pure white Epi leather, it will elevate any summer silhouette.

Enamel hardware on the Monogram Confidential bracelet creates saturated shades. It is accented with a precision print of intersecting lines that reflect the House's textile designs. The gold-tone fastener, which clicks to close, creates the illusion of a metal buckle.

Fast Flower reinterprets the Maison's iconic Monogram Flower in pure and graphic lines, tinted with Art Deco. With their three-dimensional flower shape, these delicate earrings will contribute a subtle signature to any outfit.

This belt showcases the Maison's LV Circle logo for a masculine piece that is ideal for fashionable street wear looks. It is available in a choice of Monogram canvases, complemented by different metal finishes.

The Blooming Flowers bag charm and key holder is inspired by the classic Monogram Flowers print. Its complementary mix of materials is a nod to the expertise of Louis Vuitton's trunk-making heritage. The three individual charms are crafted from Monogram coated canvas, Epi leather and metal. It can be secured to a bag or keys thanks to its dual-function clasp.

The Epi Patchwork collection combines two iconic Louis Vuitton materials, grained Epi leather and Damier Graphite canvas, as here on the Brazza wallet. On the exterior, blue and gray Epi harmonize with the black and gray of the canvas, while the interior features bright orange. This classic wallet contains a comprehensive array of pockets and compartments.

The LV Initiales belt features elegant Louis Vuitton Epi leather and a matching tone-on-tone LV buckle. The monochrome effect of the belt create a contemporary look. Expertly crafted, the belt encapsulates the enduring values of style and quality that lie at the heart of Louis Vuitton.

Showcasing the brand new Monogram White canvas, this new animation of the Reverso buckle makes a strong fashion statement. The reversible option makes it two belts in one, with a summery white side complemented by casual navy.

Louis Vuitton's colorful Pop Monogram hat is knitted from soft, cozy pure wool. A perfect way to brighten cold days, it revisits the iconic Monogram pattern in the playful spirit of Pop Art. Part of a set including a scarf and gloves, it makes an ideal gift.

Versatile and right on trend, the Double V is made from noble fine-grained leather and iconic Monogram canvas. The round and voluptuous shape of the bag is perfectly contrasted by the bold V-shape flap, making the Double V a unique bag. It can be carried by hand or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap.

The textured background of this pure-silk jacquard tie creates a tone-on-tone check, overlaid with a subtle pattern of Monogram Flowers and LV initials. Cut with a classic 8cm blade, in Navy, Grey or Medium Blue, it enhances business or formal attire.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom in lush profusion on this pure-silk screen-printed square. Mixed with signature House motifs, the florals compose a modern pattern, offered in fresh colors that are the perfect foil for neutral summer looks.

A structured day bag with generous capacity, the City Steamer MM Time Trunk handbag is inspired by luggage from the House's archives. Contrasting bands of transformed canvas and calfskin leather create a trompe l’oeil effect, with mock clasps and gold-color studs for subtle embellishment. A removable shoulder strap and Toron top handles allow for different carrying options.

With its cool ”schoolbag” shape in a trendy small size, the Mylockme BB makes a big fashion statement. Crafted of soft calf leather, the bag’s long chain strap can be doubled for short-shoulder carry or worn cross-body. A sleek choice for every day, it has room for all the essentials.

The Pochette Cosmos clutch was inspired by the space theme of Louis Vuitton's Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. Large enough to hold everyday essentials, it also features an outside zipped pocket. This version comes in high-gloss Monogram Glaze canvas, one of the show's key materials, and is embossed with the Louis Vuitton signature.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this elegant wallet is given a sophisticated twist by a row of golden studs and eyelets, which create a jewel effect along the flap. Its compact design is large enough to hold all the daily essentials.

The Monogram necklace is a versatile reinterpretation of the iconic Monogram design. Its calf leather strap is inspired by the black trims on Louis Vuitton's traditional leather goods. The piece is finished with a coin pendant in a silver-color finish.

In a choice of two new colors, the LV Initiales belt is an update on a design from Louis Vuitton's permanent collection. It is crafted from Damier canvas with a calf leather border, in reference to the House's leather goods edit. LV Initials in silver-color brass, inlaid with lacquer, complete this refined piece.

In a choice of two new colors, the LV Initiales belt is an update on a design from Louis Vuitton's permanent collection. It is crafted from Damier canvas with a calf leather border, in reference to the House's leather goods edit. LV Initials in silver-color brass, inlaid with lacquer, complete this refined piece.

For Valentine's Day, an adorable dog incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Zippy wallet in Monogram Vernis leather. Combining well-organized functionalities with a pure design, it is the perfect choice for an modern lifestyle.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

With Fluorescent Pink and black color-blocking, the LV In The City beaver muff is an irreverent piece. It has a secret pocket to elegantly carry essentials, and an adjustable strap made from Monogram canvas. A contrasting LV Initials design adds the finishing touch.

Daring and modern, the Tote Miroir in smooth patent calf leather is distinguished by its embossed LV initials signature, sleek shape and unexpected combinations, combined with handles and shoulder strap in a contrasting color or iconic Monogram canvas. True to its name, it features a bag charm with a pocket mirror.
This fashion-forward piece features small Vs contrasting with a plain background, in an understated and low-key design. Available in three colours, it is ideal for formal yet modern looks.

This accessible piece reinterprets the Maison's iconic Damier signature into a versatile accessory with a graphic, modern twist. This tab key holder is a functional classic, revisited with Louis Vuitton style.

These on-trend metal frames feature a thin openwork design that makes them light and comfortable to wear. Black lacquer adds a note of contrast, while the V signature at the bridge provides a subtle touch of branding.

A tribute to the House's iconic creations, the Jeu de Louis BB Bandeau scarf features a motif of instantly recognizable accessories spanning Louis Vuitton history. Vivid colorways and a board-game-style print make for a playful piece crafted from pure silk. Art nouveau and Monogram Flowers inspired by the Asnières house add a romantic touch to the slim scarf.

The Venice bag is an eye-catching piece, crafted of smooth Miroir patent leather, accented with Monogram canvas trim. This glossy little model features reinforced contrasting corners, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Small enough for a great cross-body look, the Venice easily holds a smart phone, long wallet, lipstick and keys.

Crafted from luxurious cashmere, the Jelham Stripes scarf is a timeless addition to any wardrobe. With a narrow profile and a dark denim blue color, it is a versatile piece. Contrasting stripes, which are new this season, have been added to the left edge of the scarf, along with a discreet embroidered LV signature.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day.
A sophisticated accessory for formal looks, this elegant scarf in a soft, luxurious blend of cashmere and wool is woven with a graduated Monogram pattern.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

This casual-chic hobo style in the Maison’s iconic canvas features a Monogram Flower padlock in shiny golden metal – a distinctive new signature. Light, roomy and easy to open, the bag’s flat leather shoulder strap ensures comfortable all-day wear.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Personalise your belt with a wide selection of 17 leather straps, from the reversible iconic Taurillon and calf leather straps in classic or playful color combinations, to the non-reversible exotics in ostrich or crocodile. In one simple twist, you can quickly and easily change your LV Initiales buckle with a choice of 15 new redesigned pieces. With 255 possible combinations, My LV Belt ensures a unique and personalised belt adapted to each man’s individual taste.
Launched in Fall 2017, the St Sulpice is already a classic LV chain bag. The smart metallic lock, contrasting leather edging, and adorable size make this BB version your go-to everyday chic solution.

These Damier Shuffle Sunglasses showcase a fluorescent yellow color inspired by the Men’s Fall/Winter 18 collection. Their trendy lightweight construction gets a strong dose of character from the double rim structure. The lenses are engraved with LV initials and the temples have Louis Vuitton signatures, while a Damier design graces the double bridge’s top bar and the end piece.

The classic Monogram Chain bracelet is inspired by trimmings found on traditional Louis Vuitton leather goods. A versatile reworking of a key design from the House, it features the iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas and has a silver-color finish. The bracelet is part of a full collection of complementary jewelry.

Louis Vuitton signature detailing takes center stage on the LV Iconic 35mm belt. It is crafted from luxurious calf leather featuring gold-tone studs and a Monogram Flower motif. With an oversized gold-color LV logo on the buckle, this statement piece is a new animation of the LV Iconic design, first launched in Fall-Winter 2017.

Featuring both calf leather and edge-dyed Damier or Monogram canvas, the LV Treble bracelet pays homage to the House's esteemed leather goods. It is constructed from a trio of straps, braided together for a striking look. The piece is completed with a metal hook clasp in shimmering brass, with a silver-color finish.

The Digit bracelet for men in Louis Vuitton's classic Taiga leather features an innovative industrial-inspired closure which interprets the Damier pattern in 3D. The easy-to-open clasp is engraved with the LV initials.

The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour strap totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.
This warm wintry piece revisits the classic cable knit hat in luxurious cashmere. A sophisticated high end piece, it is signed with an embossed LV Circle patch featuring contrasted edge dying.

A chic travel companion, the Toiletry Pouch in iconic Monogram canvas offers a roomy interior, wide opening and washable lining. This collectible edition is printed with brightly colored trompe-l'œil details inspired by Louis Vuitton's historic trunks as part of the Trunk Summer 2018 theme encompassing shoes, accessories and leather goods.

For Valentine's Day, an adorable dog incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Pochette Felicie in Monogram Vernis leather. The stylish solution to carry and organize daily essentials, it features two removable interior pockets and can be transformed into a shoulder bag thanks to its removable golden chain.

Updating the classic pilot frame, these sunglasses feature flat lenses for a sporty, fashionable look, while the semi-rimless structure adds lightness and modernity. The pilot shape is ideal for square and oval faces.
Inspired by the Spring-Summer 2018 show, this fun and colorful version of the easy-to-wear District PM transforms the everyday work bag into a full-on fashion statement.

The Daily Monogram collection reinterprets the Maison’s Monogram Flower signature in rigid pieces with a graphic, feminine feel. Ideal for day to evening wear, it showcases must-have necklaces, bracelets and a ring in a variety of colors and finishes.

Featuring the season’s statement print, the Pop Monogram stole strikes a playful note, its colorful dots and stripes mixed with the Monogram pattern. Woven of pure silk, it is airy and light, ideal for every season. A fashionable gift for Monogram lovers, the stole is finished with fringe and a printed “Louis Vuitton” signature.

A genuine fashion statement, this new Reverso model associates two new Monogram canvas colors with more classic versions for a strong visual effect. Fully reversible, it will complement both daring looks and more casual styles.

This reversible belt features a new plaque buckle designed in trompe l'oeil to evoke a real see-through Petite Malle. Rose Ballerine Epi leather is complemented by iconic Monogram canvas for a strong fashion statement.

The Venice Key Pouch is part of a seasonal collection combining glossy Vernis Miroir patent leather with iconic Monogram canvas for a fresh, summery look. Both stylish and practical, this zip-up key holder can carry cash as well as keys, and may be attached to a bag thanks to its metal hook and chain.

This finely crafted Zippy Wallet in Epi leather now boasts a coloured lining and four extra credit card slots for even more functionality and style. Its iconic combination of versatility, generous space and an all-round zip make it perfect for carrying and organizing your daily essentials.

To celebrate its travel and trunk-making heritage, Louis Vuitton has created a limited edition Zippy Wallet with travel sticker-inspired patches featuring key House signatures. The wallet’s well-organized interior and pure design make it ideal for everyday use.

The Oscar doudou is a cute toy incorporating Louis Vuitton’s flower, VVN leather and Monogram signatures, and will delight children and adults alike. With its design as a nod to the Chinese year of the Dog, this iconic branded piece will last a lifetime.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt offers two looks in one: casual on the Monogram canvas side, more sophisticated with a pop of color on the grained calf leather side. It is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's Pallas handbag.

The LV Circle reversible belt is detailed with a striking LV Circle logo buckle. The strap is available in black Epi leather and in signature Monogram canvas, each with a contrasting effect on the reverse and different buckle colors. This is a reinterpretation of an iconic style, updated in new combinations and with sleek finishes.

These Las Vegas Parano aviator sunglasses are an eye-catching evolution of a Spring-Summer 2018 showpiece. A shell detail around the outer frame adds a contemporary edge. The temples feature Monogram Flowers and gold-color studs, with studs also on the shells, which is a nod to the House’s iconic trunks. The gradient lenses are available with or without a signature Monogram motif.

Woven from a delicate blend of silk and wool, this new shawl is both light and warm. The tone-on-tone Monogram jacquard background is overlaid with decorative black flowers – inspired by 18th-century motifs – for a graphic and very feminine effect.
These stylish sunglasses feature on-trend round lenses and transparent frames integrating a flash of color. The round shape particularly suits square and oval faces.

The eye-catching Logomania Rainbow scarf in wool and silk offers two looks in one: one side is woven with a multi-colored Monogram pattern on a navy background and has a warm wool feel, while the other features the Monogram pattern on rainbow stripes and feels soft and silky.

Introducing the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag MM, crafted from smooth quilted calfskin. On-trend details – a detachable handle signed “Louis Vuitton,” edgy hardware with an aged-metal finish – make this a statement piece that is also perfect for every day. The sliding chain adjusts the drop for long-, short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

The Monogram Empreinte Blanche MM combines embossed and smooth cowhide in a perfectly proportioned shoulder bag. Supple leather and curvaceous lines make this roomy, comfortable model a casual-chic choice for everyday wear. The flap closure is embellished with a signature hook-and-leather detail. Equipped with a detachable and adjustable strap, the Blanche MM can be carried cross-body, for hands-free ease.

In celebration of Qixi, Chinese Valentine’s Day, Louis Vuitton has created the romantic Capucines BB handbag in pink Taurillon leather. With a crown of red enamel Monogram Flowers along the top of the bag, evocative of red lips ready to offer a kiss, the Capucines BB is a statement piece that can be carried by hand, worn over the shoulder or cross-body on its detachable, long leather strap.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The MM model accommodates daily essentials as well as documents and files.

Featuring an irreverent tone-on-tone print, the Hook tie is an offbeat accessory. Crafted from jacquard weave silk, it comes in two rich colors: burgundy and navy. With a Monogram print background and a scattering of colorful snap hooks, it is ideal for House aficionados with a playful sense of humor.

The natural Tiger's Eye stone cufflinks are a prime example of Louis Vuitton's expertise and a unique addition to a connoisseur's wardrobe. The signature LV Initials are incorporated into the sleek design. Timeless and tonal, these cufflinks will complement an array of looks.

The textured background of this pure-silk jacquard tie creates a tone-on-tone check, overlaid with a subtle pattern of Monogram Flowers and LV initials. Cut with a classic 8cm blade, in Navy, Grey or Medium Blue, it enhances business or formal attire.

The ultimate accessory for iPhone aficionados, Louis Vuitton's cult Eye Trunk has been upgraded for the iPhone X & XS. First seen on Spring-Summer 2018 show by Nicolas Ghesquière, this new version comes with a functional lock and removable leather strap for shoulder or cross-body carry, it is a cutting-edge fashion statment.

The LV Tab Chain comes in indigo blue and vibrant Lava orange. The long chain features an iconic padlock reminiscent of those from Louis Vuitton’s trunks, and LV Initials embellished in metallic detailing. This versatile accessory can be used as a key holder or bag charm.

This shimmering version of the Capucines BB handbag is crafted of smooth calf leather adorned with delicate crystal flowers around the bag’s top edge – inside and out – creating a floral crown. The studded rings, Monogram flowers and LV signature are all adorned with sparkling crystals, a nod to the crystal detailing on some of the belts and scarves this season.

A background of Monogram jacquard is overlaid with a classic pattern of small circles, for an elegantly subdued pure-silk tie that will complement business or formal suiting. An ideal gift for a man of traditional tastes.

To celebrate Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition featuring cute, nature-inspired scenes incorporating key House signatures. A perfect gift, the envelope-style Sarah wallet combines an elegant exterior with an ingeniously designed interior offering a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The classic striped tie is reinterpreted with the subtle addition of the iconic Monogram jacquard motif. Woven of pure silk yarn, this model is offered in classic yet modern colors,  the ideal accessory for a stylish business look.

The Neverfull MM handbag explores the House’s travel and trunk-making roots.   Crafted from grained Epi Leather, it is accessorized with playful reinterpretations of the travel “stickers” found on turn-of-the-century luggage. The side laces can be tightened to transform this practical tote into a more compact city bag.

The matte black Ardillon buckle of the Voyager belt epitomizes the masculine elegance of this belt. Urban and contemporary, the belt is a statement piece. It is finished with meticulously crafted details that pay homage to the rich heritage of the House.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.
This classic striped tie combines a gradient effect with a contrasting Monogram motif. An ideal choice for business and formal looks, it makes a perfect gift.

For Valentine's Day, a cute bird incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Victorine wallet in Monogram canvas. Ingeniously designed, this compact wallet allies perfectly a cute look and a wide capacity.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt offers two looks in one: casual on the Monogram canvas side, more sophisticated with a chic neutral on the grained calf leather side. It is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's Pallas handbag.

This edition of the Capucines handbag presents a playful message delivered through exacting workmanship. The top handle features an XOXO motif, created with delicately braided colored leather threads alternating with round metal studs. The embellishment lends a unique and on-trend crafted touch to this charming BB model, made from full-grain Taurillon leather lined with smooth calfskin.

Influenced by the House's permanent Keep It collection, this stylish bracelet is a statement piece. The metal hardware is intricately engraved with the Louis Vuitton Paris signature. Crafted from Damier printed canvas, this bracelet is ideal as a statement accessory.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.

Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet is revisited for the Epi Patchwork collection with a combination of grained Epi leather and Monogram canvas. On the outside, two shades of blue complement the iconic canvas, while the inside features tan leather. This compact wallet is notable for its well-designed interior with a variety of slots and compartments.

Featuring an all-over Monogram pattern twisted with a flowery background, this feminine piece references the Maison's heritage with its Louis Vuitton trunk frame. It is available in two summery colours.
This woven tie combines the Maison's iconic Monogram motif with a coloured gradient. Ideal for business looks, it offers a subtly twisted way of playing stripes.

Flower prints abound in the SS 18 collection. For this new iteration of the daytime-to-dark Twist bag, colorful blossoms adorn a backdrop of signature Epi leather. It’s a fresh and summery piece, finished with a long sliding chain and a jewel-like LV Twist lock.

Black Monogram Shadow calfskin, a very supple leather embossed with the iconic Monogram pattern, complements the neat design of Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet. Offering the advantage of an extremely compact format, this practical wallet contains a variety of credit card slots and compartments for tickets and banknotes.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton’s origins as a luxury trunk maker, this one-handled Cherrywood BB handbag is fashioned from Monogram canvas combined with modern Miroir Vernis patent leather and natural cowhide details. Discreet signatures such as the emblematic tuck lock and embossed LV bring understated elegance. This versatile bag boasts a top handle and a hands-free cross-body carry option thanks to the removable and adjustable strap. Easy-to-wear and trendy, it is perfectly suited for shopping afternoons or day-to-evening use.

These square LV Player sunglasses present a sporty look with their laminated acetate frames, brow bar and two-tone color. Nods to the House's hallmarks include the Damier signature engraved on the temples and tips, a Louis Vuitton signature on the side and LV Initials on the lenses. Solid-colored sun lenses complete this elegant design.

The iconic Zippy Wallet combines versatility, generous space and an all-round zip, making it perfect for carrying and organizing your daily essentials. Epi leather delivers an elegant version of this icon and a range of attractive colors to match every style.

At the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 show, the Backpack GM stood out as a key shape for the season. This model is crafted from Monogram Titanium canvas, a breakthrough material inspired by space travel. Technical hardware in Titanium-color metal imparts a sporty look to this capacious bag, equipped with padded straps for a comfortable carry.

With its eye-catching Monogram Flowers allover pattern, this version of the Capucines BB handbag, fashioned of supple Taurillon leather, is in tune with spring fashions. Shaped from cream-colored blossoms surrounded by studs, the Monogram Flowers perfectly complement the khaki-colored leather.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. Compact and versatile, with plenty of space for essentials, the Pochette Voyage can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look.

Soft, warm and light, the new Daily Monogram stole displays a large-scale, contrasted version of the iconic House motif. Woven of a balanced blend of wool, cotton and silk, it is a timeless, all-season, must-have piece for every wardrobe.

model: PTE CLES SUMMER FEEL ICE CREAM
en_US_description: These playful items evoke the spirit of summer, with their blend of seaside artifacts with iconic Louis Vuitton codes. Perfect and accessible gifts, they are ideal to mix and match, with the versatile bag charm doubling as a key holder.

With its finely crafted details, the Armand Briefcase in full-grain Taurillon leather is the very definition of business chic. As practical as it is elegant, it boasts multiple compartments, including a large zipped compartment in which to carry your laptop.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom in lush profusion on this pure-silk screen-printed square. Mixed with signature House motifs, the florals compose a modern pattern, offered in fresh colors that are the perfect foil for neutral summer looks.

Featuring an embossed leaning LV Circle logo, this new interpretation of the Metropole belt is available in two colour options. Its iconic Epi leather is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton's leather goods and shoe collections.

Introducing an exclusive capsule of silk-and-wool shawls: three different designs each feature an iconic animal and  signature motifs (LV initials, stripes  borrowed from historic trunks...) These collectible pieces add a cool, colorful flourish to casual or dressy looks.

Part of the Trunk Summer 2018 collection of shoes, accessories and leather goods, the Clémence wallet in signature Damier Azur canvas is given a fresh look with colorful trompe-l'œil details inspired by Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. This stylish zip-around wallet offers a well-organized interior with a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The elegant Anton backpack makes a polished impression in any professional setting. Fashioned of durable Taiga leather, it features impeccably crafted heritage details: note the top handle, subtle tone-on-tone signature tab, and metal zip pulls.

Updating the classic pilot frame, these sunglasses feature flat lenses for a sporty, fashionable look, while the semi-rimless structure adds lightness and modernity. The pilot shape is ideal for square and oval faces.
For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne MM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.

Suitable both for business and special occasions, this easy-going tie is available in a broad range of colour options. The Maison's iconic Monogram motif is reproduced as a printed pattern, giving the appearance of a woven tie.

Feminine and functional, this card holder in Monogram Empreinte leather is the perfect daily companion. Its ultra-slim format with a secure press stud closure makes it ideal for holding the daily essentials.

Fashioned in discreet Monogram Eclipse canvas, this Odyssey Messenger PM is perfect when you’re working a more relaxed business look. The wide strap and supple form mean it’s very comfortable to carry.

Taking inspiration from the House’s iconic trunks, this Neverfull MM boldly reinterprets Monogram canvas by overlaying screen prints of trunk corners and historic LV locks for a trompe l'oeil effect that freshens up this effortlessly practical tote.

These fashionable sunglasses have a fashionable rounded shape that is perfect for oval and square faces. The layered acetate gives a touch of colour and flare. They are conformable to wear thanks to their integrated flex hinges.

Evoking the sport universe from the SS18 Men’s show, these trendy accessories reinterpret the Louis Vuitton signature in graphic and reflective lettering. Usable as both bag charms and key holders, they coordinate perfectly with the Maison’s other lines.

This Voyager 35mm Belt gives pride of place to the new Monogram Titanium canvas, introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Lined with calf leather, it also features iconic natural leather details that will acquire a distinctive patina over time. The roller on the ardillon buckle is engraved with a discreet Louis Vuitton signature.
With its front pocket and discreet Monogram Eclipse canvas, the Odyssey Messenger MM means that you’ll arrive at your business meeting looking stylish.

A contemporary take on the classic schoolbag, the updated Mylockme is a sleek, ultra-fashionable model crafted of soft, supple calf. Versatile and functional, with a well-organized interior, it can be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body.

model: PTE CLES LV UPSIDE DOWN ILL.
en_US_description: The LV Upside Down Illustré bag charm and key holder in Monogram Ink canvas mischievously inverts the LV Initials as part of a transversal theme taking in leather goods and ready-to-wear. The initials are screen-printed in a bold coral shade coordinating with the leather goods collection.

The Pop Monogram gloves reinterpret Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern in a fun, colorful spirit inspired by Pop Art. In soft and warm wool, these long gloves are particularly pleasant to wear. A perfect gift, they form part of a set with the Pop Monogram beannie and scarf.

The Pochette Félicie in pink Epi leather features a bold red and white stripe as part of the Epi Stripes special edition, which was inspired by Louis Vuitton's heritage of personalizing its clients' luggage. This versatile pouch has a removable metal chain, enabling it to be worn on the shoulder or hand-carried as a clutch.

The trimmings on traditional Louis Vuitton leather goods were the inspiration for this classic Monogram ring. This new silver-colored piece is a versatile reinterpretation of the well-known Monogram pattern, preserving the iconic design by engraving it into the metal. This elegant ring is part of a matching collection.

Inspired by the playful spirit of Pop Art, Louis Vuitton's Pop Monogram scarf is a colorful way to wrap up on cold days. This double-sided scarf is knitted from a soft, warm blend of wool and cashmere. A perfect gift, it can be teamed with the matching Pop Monogram hat and gloves.

The Pop Monogram Square in pure silk presents the season’s fresh twist on the iconic pattern. The central Monogram Flower is composed of a playful mix of straps, chains and locks – all historic House leatherwork signatures. Stripes and dots add a modern touch to this on-trend screen-printed scarf, an ideal gift for Monogram fans.

The mascot of Louis Vuitton's gifting collection, the charming Vivienne figurine embodies both playfulness and the know-how of the Maison. Carefully crafted from iconic materials, this latest 500-pieces limited edition, Vivienne World Tour pays tribute to the art of travel.

With its ladylike shape, reminiscent of the original Vernis bags from 1999 and 2000, the Neo Triangle glams up any scene. Its shiny shiny Monogram Embossed patent leather in stylish tones and perfect proportions prove that indeed, small is beautiful.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

Specifically designed for the iPhone 8+, this modern wallet in Damier Graphite canvas with a touch of Neon combines a purse, a card holder and a phone case in one playful and versatile package. The different elements can be detached, while the removable strap enables the wallet to be carried stylishly around the wrist.

The most structured of the iconic Louis Vuitton handbags. The original was the creation of Gaston Vuitton, who named it for the Alma Bridge, a span that connects two fashionable Paris neighbourhoods. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Épi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colours.

An edgy look inspired by piercings, these mismatched multi-ring earrings have an original design that envelopes the ear lobe. Their rich details feature iconic Louis Vuitton elements, including trunk studs and the LV Circle signature.

As a go-to bag for every day, the Clapton Backpack checks all the boxes. Damier canvas looks fresh, paired with supple small-grained leather. The shiny golden tuck lock adds a heritage touch. Casual yet trendy, it can be carried several ways thanks to a top handle and adjustable straps.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Each screen-printed dot on the new Kamondot pure-silk square displays an emblematic motif: LV initials or Monogram blossom. A spot-on fashion accessory, the scarf can be styled in any number of creative ways to brighten summery silhouettes.
Slender by name, slender by nature. This wallet in masculine Monogram Eclipse canvas is suitably compact and slim, will carry all the essentials and still fit into a front or back pocket with ease.

Feminine and functional, this card holder in Monogram Empreinte leather is the perfect daily companion. Its ultra-slim format with a secure press stud closure makes it ideal for holding the daily essentials.

The LV in the City compact scarf is crafted from soft beaver fur with a silk Monogram-pattern lining. The perfect size to wrap around the neck, it spotlights the LV initials and a Monogram Flower. It comes in two colorways: eye-catching black with bright pink and feminine pearl gray with pastel pink.

The Essential V bracelet spotlights the iconic V signature created by Nicolas Ghesquière for his debut collection for Louis Vuitton. This graphic motif is embellished with colored lacquer and studs inspired by the House's historic trunks. The supple chain closes with a clasp decorated with an LV Circle accessory.

Crafted from black Cuir Taurillon leather, this Capucines compact wallet is part of the seasonal LV Soleil collection. It is decorated with a sun-ray pattern in silver and gold-tone studs, which was inspired by the sun sculpture on the Louis Vuitton Place Vendôme store in Paris. Its space-efficient interior offers multiple practical features.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Keepall Bandouliere 50, the original soft travel bag, is revisited for this special edition in key materials from the Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. Here, it is crafted from Dark Infinity leather, a supple black calfskin, and features high-gloss Monogram trim, textile handles and a removable shoulder strap.

These fashionable sunglasses have a fashionable rounded shape that is perfect for oval and square faces. The layered acetate gives a touch of colour and flare. They are conformable to wear thanks to their integrated flex hinges.

The iconic Zippy Wallet in Monogram Empreinte leather with a gold-color zipper is a study in understated style. Generous space and an all-round zip bring versatility. Compartments and pockets for credit cards, coins, and bills and notes make it extremely practical.

The eye-catching Logomania Rainbow scarf in wool and silk offers two looks in one: one side is woven with a multi-colored Monogram pattern and has a warm wool feel, while the other features the Monogram pattern on rainbow stripes and feels soft and silky.

The Monogram Flower morphs into a kaleidoscope pattern on this bright, light, silk-and-wool jacquard shawl. The colorblock print gives this piece a modern allure that will enhance any outfit. Generously sized, for many styling options.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day.

Featuring the season’s statement print, the Pop Monogram stole strikes a playful note, its colorful dots and stripes mixed with the Monogram pattern. Woven of pure silk, it is airy and light, ideal for every season. A fashionable gift for Monogram lovers, the stole is finished with fringe and a printed “Louis Vuitton” signature.

This edition of the Porte-Documents Business is made of signature Damier Graphite coated canvas, set off by silver-color hardware. In addition to papers and files, it also accommodates a laptop in a separate padded compartment. The bag can be neatly and securely attached to Horizon luggage, thanks to a removable, adjustable strap.

Miniature animals introduced in the Fall-Winter 2018-19 Pre-collection make for a playful print on the Safari tie. Available in bold colors, it lends an offbeat accent to a formal outfit. This piece is part of a capsule collection featuring a coordinating pocket square.

Woven of cashmere and silk, this luxurious stole mixes two bi-color Monogram patterns with a graphic "Louis Vuitton" "split" logotype. A must-have for Monogram fans, it is an ideal mid-season piece, easy to style and coordinate with virtually any outfit.

For those looking for a casual business bag, the Odyssey Briefcase in masculine Monogram Eclipse canvas is the very definition of contemporary urban chic. Its relaxed shape is perfect for carrying a laptop and documents in style.

The Monogram Flower morphs into a fun floral print for the season’s new edition of the Lockme BB. The blossoms play against soft black calf, a leather with a fine grain and sensual hand. Outlined in red, the LV turn lock adds a final fashionable twist.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Monogram canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

Lightweight and fashionably versatile, this sporty Matchpoint Backpackdelivers both style and comfort. It elegantly combines nylon and mesh details with Damier Coastline coated canvas for a summer-ready look.

The Tribute to BB Bandeau scarf pays homage to classic Louis Vuitton bags using an inkjet printing technique for modern polish. A photographic treatment lends realism to the purse motif, printed across slim-cut silk. Allover Monogram Flowers on the reverse make for a timeless contrast, appealing to classic and experimental sensibilities.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers. It looks modern and elegant in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.
Even more stylish with a touch of color to freshen things up, the classic Dayton Reporter PM in emblematic Damier Graphite canvas is the perfect size for a city trip.
This woven tie combines the Maison's iconic Monogram motif with a coloured gradient. Ideal for business looks, it offers a subtly twisted way of playing stripes.

Inspired by the oh-so-feminine vanity case, this new Square Bag is made of Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas with calf trim and shiny hardware. Fitted with a leather Toron handle for day and a golden chain for evening wear, it’s the season’s must-have model.

The classic striped tie is reinterpreted with the subtle addition of the iconic Monogram jacquard motif. Woven of pure silk yarn, this model is offered in classic yet modern colors,  the ideal accessory for a stylish business look.

Épi inspires Nicolas Ghesquière. His fresh interpretation of the Cluny bag will thrill aficionados of the signature House leather. The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless, the lively color palette totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

Thin and feminine, this elegant belt pays tribute to the architecture of Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. Combining an engraved LV Malletier buckle with Epi leather or a choice of the Maison's most iconic canvases, it will add a touch of sophistication to any outfit.

Louis Vuitton's classic Brazza wallet is embellished by an elegant twist between Black and Grey which will bring a touch of brightness to the line. The Brazza’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials.

These La Boum sunglasses feature the classic cat-eye shape and an added line of studs evoking Louis Vuitton's iconic trunks. A new model in the collection, the accentuated frame gives a feminine effect while gold-color temples add a luxury feel. Rubber temple tips give a secure comfortable fit.

The Monogram Split tie has a statement appeal thanks to its inspired jacquard weave. The intricate detailing of its signature Monogram Split motif provides a subtle contrast with the block-color background. Silk fabric elevates this piece and creates a soft finish.

Inspired by a print featured at the Fall-Winter 2018 show, the Graphic Paisley square mixes florals and paisley to compose an oversized Monogram Flower motif, signed with the LV initials. Made of pure silk and finished with hand-rolled edges, it adds an of-the-moment touch to any silhouette.

This Cluny BB handbag is inspired by Louis Vuitton's roots as luxury trunkmaker. Grained Epi leather is decorated with playful “stickers” that evoke those found on vintage trunks but with a contemporary twist. A top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear make it practical.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city, from day to day.

Compact and versatile, with plenty of space for essentials, Louis Vuitton's Pochette Voyage can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. The elegant twist between Black and Grey will bring a touch of brightness to the line.

With its iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas sheathed directly onto metal, these must-have cuff links pay tribute to the Maison's Leather Goods savoir-faire. Masculine and sophisticated, they will enhance every business look.

This charming and sophisticated accessory reinterprets the Maison's iconic Monogram Flowers with a refreshing springtime feel. Its must-have chain is embellished with tiny studs, small gold Vs and flower charms.

With its distinctively modern shape, this Cabas Light in masculine Monogram Eclipse canvas adds a fashionable twist to any look. Extra-light and hyper-comfortable, it can be carried by hand or over the shoulder for a stylish touch.

These aviator-style Clockwise sunglasses have a modern look thanks to a rimless frame and a flat front. They feature a double bar at the brow, LV Initials engraved on the end pieces and the Louis Vuitton logo at the temples. The metal elements are contrasted with colored gradient mirror or signature Monogram lenses.

With a corail barrel-shaped metal fastener elegantly inscribed with the “Louis Vuitton” signature, this Keep It Bracelet in black calf leather was designed for the Men's Fall 2018 Pre-collection. It can be stacked with other thin cord bracelets for a fashionably casual look. Simple yet elegant, it makes a great gift.

Launched in Fall-Winter 2017, the Blurrygram Monogram shawl fuses the classic Monogram motif with an elegant gradient design. Crafted from a soft silk and cotton blend, this subtle piece is finished with a fringed hem for a modern feel. It comes in three complementary colors to accentuate an array of styles.

The Pochette Cosmos clutch references the space theme of Louis Vuitton's Fall-Winter 2018-19 fashion show. It offers room inside for everyday essentials and a secure zipped pocket on the outside. This version comes in gray Monogram Titanium canvas, one of the key materials of the show, and is embossed with the Louis Vuitton signature.

Louis Vuitton's classic Clémence wallet is an elegant and compact design offering multiple practical features. In iconic Monogram canvas, it is given a playful, feminine feel by its brightly colored leather zipper and lining.

The LV City 35mm Reversible Belt offers a stylish choice between two different leather finishes. Plain calf leather on one side creates a sophisticated look, while the embossed Damier motif on the other provides a more branded option. The brand new LV buckle is the ideal width for suits and comes with shiny black ruthenium finish for a tone-on-tone effect.

This new version of the Maison's must-have LV Twist belt makes a strong visual impact with its metallic studs and eyelets. Combining timeless black calf leather with bi-galva finishing, it will upgrade both fashion silhouettes and more edgy looks.

A familiar pilot shape is reimagined with modern touches for Louis Vuitton's new aviator-style Grease sunglasses. The temples, keyhole nose and open-work top bar are crafted from polished gold-color metal for a luxury feel. Adjustable nose pads and flex hinges help ensure a comfortable fit.
