The handles of classic House trunks inspired the Archive Slide bracelet, a new masculine talisman in black calf leather. The aged-metal fastener and accent are engraved, respectively, with the Louis Vuitton signature and LV Initials.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's classic Brazza wallet is an elegant, streamlined design with multiple practical features.

For the Epi Patchwork collection, the classic Brazza wallet combines grained Epi leather with Monogram canvas. On the exterior, two shades of blue contrast with the iconic canvas, while the interior features tan leather. Distinguished by its long, elegant shape, the Brazza wallet contains an extensive array of credit card slots, pockets and compartments.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. The Zippy Vertical wallet contains many practical features in a compact zip-around format.

This Cluny MM handbag is fashioned of grained Epi leather and features two bold stripes, separately stitched, and shiny silver hardware. The unexpected combination of colors on the LV signature and trim makes a bold fashion statement. The two-tone stripe is a detail seen on shoes in the Fall 2018 Collection and evokes the House’s orgins as trunkmakers.

The Essential V chain necklace takes its inspiration from the graphic V motif which Nicolas Ghesquière introduced at his first runway show for Louis Vuitton. This now iconic signature is interpreted in colored lacquer and decorated with studs referencing the House's historic trunks. The delicate chain is finished with a clasp and LV Circle ornament.

Simple, yes, but very stylish, this new bracelet is crafted of braided calf leather in Navy or Chocolat. The barrel-shaped metal fastener bears the “Louis Vuitton” signature in finely engraved characters. Worn in multiples, it makes on-trend fashion statement.

A cold weather must-have, the Petit Damier hat features a fresh treatment of an instantly recognizable House pattern. Dyed and knitted into the iconic Damier motif and punctuated with an LV Initials signature patch, its soft blue hues reflect the palette of the season. The warm, pure wool is finished with concealed stitching for a sleek look.

With its red and white stripes inspired by Louis Vuitton’s iconic personalized trunks, this eye-catching Petite Malle handbag in black Epi leather is an example of the House’s codes and leatherworking expertise. Small yet practical, this New Classic has the emblematic S-lock clasp closure and a removable leather strap for two carry options: clutch or cross-body.

Kim Jones turned the LV signature on its head for this bold edition of the Discovery Backpack. Created for the Men’s 2018 Fall Pre-collection, it is crafted of Monogram Ink canvas, with rugged cowhide leather trim. The Coral Pink zipper echo the bag’s colorful, oversize logo.

This must-have notebook combines the feel of historic trunk stickers with the patches "My LV World Tour" from the Maison’s leather goods personalization. A playful piece, its Monogram signature is a perfect match for Louis Vuitton’s leather goods, fashion accessories and shoes.

Created exclusively for the 2018 Summer accessory collection, this Illustrée bag charm and key holder displays a trompe l’oeil Trunk motif. A tribute to Louis Vuitton’s Art of Travel, the detailed design is silk-screened onto Monogram canvas. The reverse side features the signature Malletage pattern, and may be personalized with hot-stamped initials. Polished golden-brass fittings, finely engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature are finished with a miniature leather travel sticker. A stylish gift idea.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this versatile accessory reinterprets classic American motel key rings. The timeless Tabac version combines the Maison's leather know-how with an elegant palladium finish.

Flower prints abound in the SS 18 collection. For this new iteration of the daytime-to-dark Twist bag, colorful blossoms adorn a backdrop of signature Epi leather. It’s a fresh and summery piece, finished with a long sliding chain and a jewel-like LV Twist lock.

Crafted from braided calf leather, this exclusive belt's V motif is a tribute to the Maison's trunk-making craftsmanship. Available in two timeless colors, it is adorned with a graphic LV Pyramide buckle.

The Venice bag is an eye-catching piece, crafted of smooth Miroir patent leather, accented with Monogram canvas trim. This glossy little model features reinforced contrasting corners, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Small enough for a great cross-body look, the Venice easily holds a smart phone, long wallet, lipstick and keys.

As part of the seasonal Venice collection, Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy coin purse is reinterpreted in luminous Vernis Miroir patent leather with Monogram-canvas trim. This fresh, summery look complements the neat design of this purse, which holds cash and credit cards in a secure, zip-around format.

Available in a rainbow of different lens colors, these stylish sunglasses are decorated with iconic studs that evoke the Maison's trunks: lining the edges of each sunlens, they highlight the design's perfect pilot shape.
Stylish and sporty in Damier Infini leather, the Discovery clutch is the perfect size for transporting documents and other belongings, it can be hand-carried or slipped inside a larger bag.

This new metal model offers an innovative blend of Monogram canvas and rubber on the temples, making it extremely comfortable to wear. Available in a choice of Monogram Ebene or Monogram Eclipse, it is ideal for round and oval face shapes.

The inventive Wild Puppet bag charm and key holder takes details from Louis Vuitton's historical trunks to form a playful panda figure. A calf leather and natural mink fur base is adorned with gold-color metal studs, eyelets and zip pulls to highlight the animal's features. This whimsical piece can be attached to a bag with the secure chain and clasp.

To celebrate Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition featuring cute, nature-inspired scenes incorporating key House signatures. A perfect gift, the ultra-secure Zippy wallet combines well-organized functionalities with a pure design, making it ideal for an urban lifestyle.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Keepall Bandoulière 50, the original soft travel bag, is stylishly revisited as part of the Epi Patchwork collection. Crafted from navy grained Epi leather, it is accented with details in bright blue Epi, while its removable luggage label and shoulder strap come in black and gray Damier Graphite canvas.

This lovable Monkey bag charm and key holder belongs to a collection of Chinese zodiac animals. Its soft body is crafted from luxurious mink fur, while its eyes are Louis Vuitton trunk studs. A Monogram canvas medal completes this richly detailed design, which functions both as a bag ornament and a key ring.

For Valentine's Day, an adorable dog incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Pochette Felicie in Monogram canvas. The stylish solution to carry and organize daily essentials, it features two removable interior pockets and can be transformed into a shoulder bag thanks to its removable golden chain.

An updated design gives the iconic Messager scarf a sporty, modern look. Refined woolen yarns are precision-knitted to create the allover Damier pattern, which gets a trendy twist from stripes inspired by the markings on vintage House trunks.

The Flower wallet is an elegant, feminine design playing on two iconic Louis Vuitton signatures: the Monogram flower and the padlock. In Monogram canvas with a leather front pocket and lining, it has ample space for all everyday essentials.

This new metal model offers an innovative blend of Monogram canvas and rubber on the temples, making it extremely comfortable to wear. Available in a choice of Monogram Ebene or Monogram Eclipse, it is ideal for round and oval face shapes.

Introducing the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag MM, crafted from smooth quilted calfskin. On-trend details – a detachable handle signed “Louis Vuitton,” edgy hardware with an aged-metal finish – make this a statement piece that is also perfect for every day. The sliding chain adjusts the drop for long-, short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

These delicate LV Windsor Fleur Pendant Earrings were presented for the first time at Nicolas Ghesquière’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Their flower design is fashioned from black enamel with pearl and strass details, with finely engraved wing motifs adding a majestic touch. A thin gold-color chain is suspended from the closure behind the ear.

Complementing Louis Vuitton's Summer 2018 capsule collection, this casual reversible belt in Damier Cobalt canvas offers two stylish looks in one: a rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on one side and a playful jungle print on the other.

The Essential V bracelet spotlights the iconic V signature created by Nicolas Ghesquière for his debut collection for Louis Vuitton. This graphic motif is embellished with colored lacquer and studs inspired by the House's historic trunks. The supple chain closes with a clasp decorated with an LV Circle accessory.

A background of Monogram jacquard is overlaid with a classic pattern of small circles, for an elegantly subdued pure-silk tie that will complement business or formal suiting. An ideal gift for a man of traditional tastes.
Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers. The daring twist between Navy Blue and Light Blue will highlit any silhouette.

A combination of some of the House's most recognizable signatures, the Fetish Tassel bag charm and key holder is a keepsake to cherish. A collectible ornament crafted from a mix of materials, including Monogram canvas, Epi leather and metal, this playful charm makes a thoughtful gift.

Featuring the iconic Monogram motif, the Denim Monogram shawl is given a seasonal update with two fresh and feminine hues. Crafted from a soft blend of cotton and silk, both yarns are dyed to highlight the contrasting print. Effortlessly elegant, it can be showcased as a head scarf or worn around the neck.

The Pop V tie sees the House's V signature print reimagined as an allover cartoon motif for a touch of irreverence. Channeling the Pop Art movement, the pure silk tie comes in a range of vivid hues whose patterned 3-D effect immediately catches the eye.

The Lockingram bracelet combines three iconic Louis Vuitton motifs in reference to the House's rich history. The padlock charm, a detail often found on Louis Vuitton's leather goods, takes center stage. A Monogram canvas strap with a calf leather lining, and hardware shaped in the Monogram Flower, complete the bracelet.

The Knotty Pearls earrings each showcase a resin pearl for a feminine look. Hardware in the shape of the Monogram Flower, a signature Louis Vuitton detail, is applied to the pair. These earrings are part of a coordinating line of jewelry.

For Winter 2018, Louis Vuitton offers a new take on the iconic Alma handbag, with its precious chain, reinterpreting it in a  compact Mini size. Fashioned of glossy Vernis Miroir patent leather with an understated Louis Vuitton embossed front patch and crafted Monogram-canvas zip pullers, this adorable handbag is a very feminine accessory.

The Helsinki hat and scarf have a new look. Knitted from pure, precious cashmere yarns in an allover Damier pattern, these sporty, generous pieces will keep winter’s chill at bay. A leather patch embossed with the LV initials adds an elegant signature.
Ideal for everyday use, this luxuriously soft Monogram Neo Denim shawl is subtle and very feminine. Entirely weaven in jacquard, it features the Louis Vuitton signature and the Monogram pattern.

Crafted from softly grained black Cuir Taurillon leather, Louis Vuitton's Pocket Organizer is printed with the iconic LV Circle signature in bright blue. The design gives a bold new twist to this all-in-one wallet, which contains several pockets and credit card slots in an extremely space-efficient format.

The NéoNoé is an on-trend bucket bag with an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry. The trompe l'oeil screen prints of trunk corners and historic locks that adorn the supple Damier Azur canvas make this version a playful twist on LV heritage.

Introducing an exclusive capsule of silk-and-wool shawls: three different designs each feature an iconic animal and  signature motifs (LV initials, stripes  borrowed from historic trunks...) These collectible pieces add a cool, colorful flourish to casual or dressy looks.

The iconic appliqué of the House is reimagined as Monogram Eclipse canvas over metal on these sleek cufflinks. Modern and masculine, they embody Louis Vuitton's savoir faire and heritage. Cylindrical in shape, these cufflinks will elevate any ensemble.

The Monogram Layers tie is a timeless piece that makes an ideal partner for business ensembles. It blends a subtle allover pattern, incorporating the Louis Vuitton Monogram print, with a gradient stripe for contrast. Available in a selection of deep hues, this tie is a classic piece.

Featuring a bold and graphic design in tune with Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this stole is available in a generous format for fashion-forward looks. Available in a choice of colours, it is perfect for mid-season wear.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

This Brazza, fashioned in Damier Graphite canvas, is brightened by a  touch of yellow  that emphasizes the checkered pattern. Its generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket

A graphic braided detail outlines the flap of this richly crafted Twist bag. New for Summer ’18, it is made of emblematic Epi leather, with a detachable strap that adjusts to several lengths. Carried by the short chain handle, it is perfect for evening wear.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. Stylish and functional with its double zip, inside pocket and washable lining, this spacious Toilet Pouch is ideal for frequent travelers.

This playful piece combines Damier canvas with plain calf leather for two distinct looks. The Damier canvas is enhanced with edge-dying, while lacquered finishing adds a subtle graphic effect to the LV Initiales buckle.

The Digit bracelet for men in Louis Vuitton's classic Taiga leather features an innovative industrial-inspired closure which interprets the Damier pattern in 3D. The easy-to-open clasp is engraved with the LV initials.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this versatile accessory reinterprets classic American motel key rings. It combines the Maison's leather know-how with the iconic Monogram Eclipse and a trendy ruthenium finish.

Spacious, sophisticated and chic, the Artsy MM is a timeless tote bag. In sumptuous embossed Monogram Empreinte leather, a luxuriously ornate handle and rich golden color metallic pieces create a refined look.

This edition of the Lockme Bucket sports an embellishment of silver-color rivets. The metal studs lend an edgy attitude to the soft calf leather and complement the signature LV turn lock. A leather drawstring pulls the bag tight; an adjustable leather strap ensures comfortable shoulder- or cross-body wear.

The Morningram belt displays the Louis Vuitton signature on its elegant Monogram canvas strap. The versatile belt can be reversed, showcasing the stylish calf leather that gives the belt a new dimension. A bold brass buckle with gold-color finishing effortlessly completes the look.

Louis Vuitton's Zippy Wallet is fashioned from Monogram Vernis, a high-gloss patent leather embossed with the iconic Monogram pattern. This elegant leather enhances the clean lines of this zip-around wallet, whose ingeniously designed interior features a variety of pockets, compartments and credit card slots.

Featuring a striking fluorescent color inspired by the Men’s Fall/Winter 18 collection, these Clockwise Sunglasses offer a blend of sport and street style. Their trendy double bar combines with a flat front to create very modern look. Engraved LV initials and Louis Vuitton logos add a subtle touch of branding.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.

This must-have scarf features the easy-going Monogram Eclipse motif as an all-over design, with a textured effect that recalls the original canvas. Subtly branded, it can be worn as a set with the matching gloves and hat.

For the Epi Blooming Corners limited edition, the Clémence wallet comes in Epi leather with contrasting Monogram flower-shaped corners. This detail, which was inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks, brings a fresh, playful note to this elegant long wallet, whose secure zip-around format conceals a variety of pockets and credit card slots.
This simple cover with resistant textile protects your Horizon 55 while checking it in.

Belonging to Louis Vuitton's Trunk Summer 2018 collection of accessories and leather goods, the Sarah wallet in fresh Damier Azur canvas is printed with trompe-l'œil trunk straps and corners. This envelope wallet, which features numerous pockets and compartments, closes with an S-lock inspired by the historic trunks.

Part of the Resort 2018 limited edition, the Mini Pochette Accessoires in summery Damier Azur canvas is screen-printed with trompe-l'oeil details inspired by Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. Each version features the name of a glamorous destination in pink or blue. This chic pouch can be attached to a bag or carried on its own.

Suitable both for business and special occasions, this easy-going tie is available in a broad range of colour options. The Maison's iconic Monogram motif is reproduced as a printed pattern, giving the appearance of a woven tie.

As a go-to bag for every day, the Clapton Backpack checks all the boxes. Damier canvas looks fresh, paired with supple small-grained leather. The shiny golden tuck lock adds a heritage touch. Casual yet trendy, it can be carried several ways thanks to a top handle and adjustable straps.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Card Holder in Damier Graphite canvas is distinguished by its electric-blue trim and lining, which contrast boldly with the black and gray of one of Louis Vuitton's signature materials. This neatly proportioned accessory holds payment essentials in a slim, pocket-friendly format.

Modern and stylish in Damier Graphite canvas, Louis Vuitton's Pochette Jour features a wide zipped opening and a discreet gusset to further increase its capacity. It can carried in the hand or slipped inside a larger bag.

This elegant wallet combines iconic Damier canvas with soft, fine-grained calf leather and a statement clasp inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Its well-designed interior offers an array of functional pockets and slots.

Here is the Fluo hat, a brilliant neon number knitted of pure, warm 100% wool. Extra-soft but very sharp, this fisherman-style beanie can be worn at different angles. Offered in statement shades inspired by the season’s ready-to-wear collection.

The LV City 35mm Reversible Belt offers a stylish choice between two different leather finishes. Plain calf leather on one side creates a sophisticated look, while the embossed Damier motif on the other provides a more branded option. The brand new LV buckle is the ideal width for suits and comes with shiny black ruthenium finish for a tone-on-tone effect.

This Fluo city scarf from the Fall-Winter 2018 collection is signed “Louis” in giant, all-cap letters. Jacquard-woven from an extra-soft blend of wool and cashmere, it is a fashion-forward twist on a classic. Generously sized, it is long enough to loop stylishly around the neck.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Keepall Bandouliere 50, the original soft travel bag, is revisited for this special edition in key materials from the Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show. Here, it comes in gray Monogram Titanium canvas and features natural cowhide-leather trim, textile handles and a removable shoulder strap embossed with the House signature.

This City Steamer handbag is fashioned from black grained calf leather embellished for the first time with exclusive gold python-leather handles and nametag. Inspired by iconic steamer luggage designs from the House archives, it blends Louis Vuitton heritage with the new codes introduced by Nicolas Ghesquière. Perfectly adapted for day-to-office use (ideal for A4 files), its clever design offers good capacity and a removable shoulder strap as well as round Toron handles for two carrying options: hand and shoulder.

In a tribute to Louis Vuitton's travel inspiration, these trendy pearl bracelets are like souvenirs brought back from the beaches of Hawaii. Their precious mix of materials is a tribute to the Maison's savoir-faire.

The best-selling LV Confidential bracelet is now offered in a rainbow of new hues. In grained calf leather or Monogram canvas, they feature engraved metal fasteners with lacquer or gold-color finishes. Stacked, they make an eye-catching fashion statement.

Simple, yes, but very stylish, this new bracelet is crafted of braided calf leather in Navy or Chocolat. The barrel-shaped metal fastener bears the “Louis Vuitton” signature in finely engraved characters. Worn in multiples, it makes on-trend fashion statement.

The Capucines Sweet Brogues compact wallet in soft Taurillon leather reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram Flowers in the spirit of the decorative perforations of brogue-style shoes. This wallet, which offers an array of pockets and credit card slots within a very space-efficient format, coordinates with the Capucines handbag.

This casual-chic hobo style in the Maison’s iconic canvas features a Monogram Flower padlock in shiny golden metal – a distinctive new signature. Light, roomy and easy to open, the bag’s flat leather shoulder strap ensures comfortable all-day wear.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

The Very Zipped Tote is the zipped handbag you’ve always wanted: feminine, sophisticated, and fashionable. The subtle mix of grained and smooth leather and the delicately braided edges are the epitome of Vuitton craftsmanship and style.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

The Venice bag is an eye-catching piece, crafted of smooth Miroir patent leather, accented with Monogram canvas trim. This glossy little model features reinforced contrasting corners, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Small enough for a great cross-body look, the Venice easily holds a smart phone, long wallet, lipstick and keys.

Discreetly woven with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Monogramissime tie is a timelessly elegant choice in an array of classic or seasonal colors. A matching pocket square is also available.

Part of the Men's Pre-collection Fall-Winter 2018, the Gambling dice necklace evokes Louis Vuitton's travel heritage and the renowned casinos of Macau. Flawlessly crafted from silver-color brass and enamel, and signed with the LV Initials, this stylish necklace can be adjusted to three different lengths.

The iconic Zippy Wallet in Monogram Empreinte leather with a gold-color zipper is a study in understated style. Generous space and an all-round zip bring versatility. Compartments and pockets for credit cards, coins, and bills and notes make it extremely practical.
In Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, the Enveloppe Carte de Visite offers space for business cards as well as a credit card or parking ticket.

Slim and elegant, the Anton Briefcase in Damier Graphite canvas combines business-like functionality with modern, masculine style. The interior accommodates a laptop and documents, while the front compartment and pockets provide easy access to travel tickets, passports and the like. With a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

This masculine accessory makes a strong fashion statement with its design inspired by ID plates. Featuring Monogram Eclipse canvas and shiny palladium finishing, it will add a street-style touch to any silhouette.
The simple elegance of Epi leather. The peerless versatility of the Zippy wallet. The numerous card slots and compartments. The all-round zip. Quite the unbeatable combination.

This chic little bag has a secret: it's roomier than it looks. The cleverly designed "wave" base provides extra space for storing necessities. With lines inherited from the Trapèze clutch, the new Twist features an updated version of the signature turn-lock. Rendered with a 3D bombé effect, the metal closure has a modern, architectural feel. To open the bag, a single smooth twist fits the letter "L" into the "V," with a satisfying click. The convertible chain handle can be worn cross-body or hung gracefully from the shoulder.

In a tribute to Louis Vuitton's travel inspiration, this trendy necklace evokes the season's Hawaiian theme with its gradient of colours and Aloha wave motif. Its precious mix of materials is a tribute to the Maison's savoir-faire.

Nicolas Ghesquière’s fascination with Japanese culture is on display in this season’s Twist MM Kawai Blossom handbag. Crafted from signature Epi leather, the bag is printed and embroidered with Monogram Flowers, reimagined with a fresh Pop attitude. The colorful textile patches change with the light, for a cool and captivating holographic effect.

This limited-edition Toiletry Pouch in Damier Azur canvas belongs to the Resort 2018 collection. Each version is screen-printed with trompe-l'oeil details inspired by Louis Vuitton trunks, as well as the name of a glamorous resort in pink or blue. A chic travel companion, this wash bag offers a roomy interior and a washable lining.

An update on an iconic piece, the LV Chain bracelet has been refreshed for the new season. The hardware features the Louis Vuitton signature, meticulously etched on both sides. The metal chain has an aged silver-color finish, and the bracelet is available in two classic hues for a timeless look.

Just like the Palm Springs backpack it has been inspired by, the Wild Bag Palm Springs charm and key holder showcases historic Louis Vuitton style. Studs and Monogram canvas combine with fur fringing and the iconic LV signature to create a playful owl motif. A versatile chain, for bag and key attachment, completes this collectible piece.

Combining fine-grained calf leather with iconic Monogram canvas, this stylish, trendy wallet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Double V bag. The original double flap conceals a secret pocket, which is ideal for tickets or coins.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel heritage, this cool cotton stole is printed with a trompe-l'œil trunk in Damier Azur canvas, complete with details such as a Louis Vuitton luggage label and brass hinges and corners. A versatile piece that is perfect for summer, it can also be worn as a pareo.

The Marignan Messenger in Monogram canvas and grained leather is the quintessence of everything that makes Louis Vuitton bags the very definition of elegance. The on-trend colors will bring instantaneous modernity and freshness to any outfit.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Mylockme compact wallet in supple calf leather references the key signatures of the Lockme handbag: the envelope-style flap, the front pocket and the LV Initials accessory. Small enough to fit into any Lockme bag, this space-efficient design offers an array of pockets and credit card slots, including a zipped pocket for coins.

On-point style and timeless design make the Boccador handbag a covetable complement to any wardrobe. Crafted from Epi leather, it is embellished with details inspired by classic House trunks, including a contoured top handle and a magnetic metal lock. A new signature, the lock provides easy access to belongings, while keeping them secure. The detachable strap offers the option of effortless shoulder or cross-body carry.

Thin and feminine, this elegant belt pays tribute to the architecture of Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. Combining an engraved LV Malletier buckle with Epi leather or a choice of the Maison's most iconic canvases, it will add a touch of sophistication to any outfit.

The Karakoram pattern, launched by Louis Vuitton in 1920, brings a band of color to the Neverfull MM handbag. The serrated stripe in Rubis red grained leather with a white border and engraved gold-color studs livens up the Damier Ebene canvas. The snap-hook closing and large interior zipped pocket keep belongings safe.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format.

The Emilie wallet in Monogram canvas comes with a poppy-red lining as part of the seasonal Monogram Blooming Flowers Coquelicot theme, while its distinctive press stud is transformed into a Monogram Flower. This envelope-style wallet opens to reveal a variety of user-friendly features, including a zipped coin pocket with a Monogram Flower charm.

A perfect (and perfectly feminine) bag for business, this functional tote is embellished with a distinctive Monogram Flower padlock in gleaming golden metal. The smooth leather handles and detachable strap provide a variety of carry options, and the well-organized interior easily holds files and a laptop.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.
Featuring a trendy round shape, this model exudes modern retro cool. Its mix of materials offers a play of contrasts, while Damier details on the rim add a subtle Louis Vuitton signature.

The pairing of Monogram canvas with hand-woven, leather-lined wicker results in a fresh and very French version of the Twist bag. Offered for Summer ’18 in a limited edition, this covetable piece will add a fashion-forward vibe to the season’s silhouettes.

The Filigram bracelet is defined by its delicate detailing. Crafted in a subtle mesh design evocative of lacework, the gold-color metal also features the classic LV Circle and Monogram Flower throughout. It is complemented with a golden clasp for the perfect fit and is part of a feminine range of coordinating accessories.

The glamorous Pallas BB combines iconic Monogram canvas with colourful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colourful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour strap totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

Hawaiian and Japanese flowers bloom on the front of this pure-silk screen-printed bandeau, with an allover Monogram pattern on the reverse. Available in a range of summery shades, this slim scarf can be styled in a variety of ways. Perfect for gifting.

Timelessly elegant in Taiga leather, Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy Organizer wallet combines pure design with true practicality. It unzips to reveal a variety of convenient features, including multiple credit card slots, a zipped coin compartment and a large pocket for plane tickets, all in an exceptionally space-efficient format.

The Summer ’18 edition of the Lockme Bucket wears an embellishment of colorful leather blossoms. Inspired by the iconic Monogram Flower, they are fastened to the soft calfskin body with metal rivets, for a cool, feminine piece that partners perfectly with the season’s silhouettes.

In a choice of two new colors, the LV Initiales belt is an update on a design from Louis Vuitton's permanent collection. It is crafted from Damier canvas with a calf leather border, in reference to the House's leather goods edit. LV Initials in silver-color brass, inlaid with lacquer, complete this refined piece.

The Monogram Split tie has a statement appeal thanks to its inspired jacquard weave. The intricate detailing of its signature Monogram Split motif provides a subtle contrast with the block-color background. Silk fabric elevates this piece and creates a soft finish.

Fashioned in historic Monogram Eclipse Canvas, the iPhone X & XS Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, hold the phone perfectly to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
The Zippy Coin Purse Vertical is an extremely practical choice for the urban man. Fitting effortlessly into small city bags and pockets, its smooth Taïga leather adds to its sense of refinement.

The Cosmetic Pouch in Monogram canvas is printed with bold trompe-l'œil details - a brass lock, corners and leather straps - inspired by Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. This special edition, part of the Trunk Summer 2018 accessories collection, references the House's travel heritage. Both practical and stylish, this makeup bag features a wide opening and washable lining.

The stylish and ultra-secure Zippy wallet in Damier Azur canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by its colorful zipper and leather lining. Combining well-organized functionalities with a pure design, it is the perfect choice for an urban lifestyle.
This handsome box in Monogram Eclipse canvas is complemented by a meticulously stitched leather lid embossed with the LV iconic Circle logo. A perfect gift, it is ideal for both home and office use.

Chiseled perforation work turns calf leather to lace: the finely crafted Love Note bag features a subtle Monogram Flower design, enriched with metal studs that shimmer like stars. A feminine piece for evening, it is finished with a signature LV closure.

The Pinball LV square features a games-inspired print, giving this intricate scarf a fun update. World-famous landmarks, such as the Eiffel Tower, echo the enduring traveler spirit of the House. Hallmark Louis Vuitton symbols enhance this bright and lively accessory crafted in opulent silk.

The Best Friend Chain bag charm and key holder is a light-hearted reimagining of the padlock and key associated with Louis Vuitton's historical trunks. The gold-color hardware is traditional, while the pink-and-black enamel work provides a refined finish. The lock and key can be shared between friends or connected into one piece by the Monogram Flowers magnet.

Statement of Spring/Summer 2018, the Monogram Blossom story contrasts iconic Monogram canvas with an intriguing floral print, bringing a fashionable touch to the Zippy Coin Purse. This compact design, with its wide opening for easy access, will sit snugly in any bag or pocket.
In luxurious fine-grained soft leather adorned with delicate rivets, this darling little bag takes on a rock and roll sneer. The metallic LV turn lock adds a discreet touch of Louis Vuitton chic.

Colorful Louis Vuitton patches are layered over the pure silk jacquard weave of the LV Stories square. Showcasing motifs inspired by Pop iconography alongside the House's iconic symbols, it is a contemporary piece. The designs include the iconic padlock and key, Monogram Flowers and travel-inspired words, including 'Volez', ' Voguez' and 'Voyagez'.
As an elegant, modern bag for city living, the Roman PM in cross grained Taïga leather has no parallel. With its specially designed iPad pocket, it also makes an excellent choice for short trips.

Its slim design and pure lines make the Anton Briefcase’s elegant silhouette as appropriate for work as the weekend. Whether you carry it by hand or wear it over the shoulder with the removable strap, you’ll be right on-trend.

This colorful silk square reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. This elegant accessory will add a sophisticated, feminine touch to any outfit.

A stylish essential to take everywhere with you, these four mini notebooks are covered in Monogram canvas printed with trompe-l'œil stickers inspired by the world's great cities. The spine of each notebook is color-matched the corresponding Louis Vuitton City Guide, while the pages are crafted from high-quality paper with the LV watermark.

Louis Vuitton's Pocket Organizer in black Monogram Shadow calf leather is an elegant way to carry everyday essentials. Discreetly embossed with the iconic Monogram pattern, Monogram Shadow is an exceptionally supple leather which complements the sleek design of this ultra-compact wallet containing several pockets and credit card slots.

Featuring a games board motif from the archives, the pure silk Jeu de Louis square vividly illustrates the history of Louis Vuitton. Hallmark prints including Damier and Monogram are mixed with playful symbols such as pawns and dice. The fun design retains all the qualities of an iconic accessory, making it a truly timeless piece.

The Nanogram necklace features a distinctive ball chain with two miniature name tags engraved with the LV Initials and iconic Monogram pattern. The design is striking for its combination of gold and silver-color finishes. The supple chain closes with a clasp accessorized with an LV Circle ornament.

A genuine fashion statement, this new Reverso model associates two new Monogram canvas colors with more classic versions for a strong visual effect. Fully reversible, it will complement both daring looks and more casual styles.
This Pochette Voyage MM is brightened by a playful touch of yellow. It can be used as a bag in bag or hand-carried for a more modern, trendier look.

This silk jacquard tie reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a modern, miniaturised version. Discreetly signed with the LV initials, it is a timelessly stylish accessory that makes an ideal gift.

This sporty Matchpoint Messenger bag brings together high performance sportswear details like mesh and nylon with Damier Coastline coated canvas for an on-trend summer look. Great for work or more casual occasions.

Logomania – a key seasonal theme – surfaces once again in the bold, graphic design of the LV List city scarf. Made of a soft, wool-and-cashmere jacquard knit, this warm accessory adds a stylish accent to a man’s winter wardrobe. Note the cheeky “Merci” signature woven into the scarf’s bottom edge.

These playful items evoke the spirit of summer, with their blend of seaside artifacts with iconic Louis Vuitton codes. Perfect and accessible gifts, they are ideal to mix and match, with the versatile bag charm doubling as a key holder.

Fashioned in historic Damier Graphite Canvas, the iPhone X & XS Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, hold the phone perfectly to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.

This sporty-chic piece plays on a mix of materials to offer a supple bracelet based around the Maison's LV Initials signature. Available in all-black and colourblock versions, it can be adjusted using special sliding pieces.

A perfect (and perfectly feminine) bag for business, this functional tote is embellished with a distinctive Monogram Flower padlock in gleaming golden metal. The smooth leather handles and detachable strap provide a variety of carry options, and the well-organized interior easily holds files and a laptop.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.

This Bond Street BB is fashioned in a harmonious combination of Damier Ebene canvas and Cuir Taurillon leather and is adorned with a leather nametag and an elegant central stripe signed Louis Vuitton. This one-handled bag offers multiple carry options: by hand, on the elbow with the top handle, or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap. Adorably compact, it’s large enough to carry essentials such as wallet, keys and phone.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Versatile and right on trend, the Double V is made from noble fine-grained leather and iconic Monogram canvas. The round and voluptuous shape of the bag is perfectly contrasted by the bold V-shape flap, making the Double V a unique bag. It can be carried by hand or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.

In Louis Vuitton's supple Mahina leather with distinctive Monogram perforations, this compact wallet will slip into any bag with ease. Its softly rounded flap opens to reveal a practical interior, including slots for credit cards and a zipped pocket for coins.

These La Boum sunglasses feature the classic cat-eye shape and an added line of studs evoking Louis Vuitton's iconic trunks. A new model in the collection, the accentuated frame gives a feminine effect while gold-color temples add a luxury feel. Rubber temple tips give a secure comfortable fit.

This adorable version of the ladylike Alma in grained Epi leather is a versatile day-to-evening piece. Trendy yet timeless, it features a long strap – perfect for cross-body wear – adorned with a golden-chain detail. Signatures include an embossed LV logo and a “Louis Vuitton Paris” patch.

This reinterpretation of the Croisette handbag in Damier canvas features a colorful leather lining and an emblematic metallic clasp inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Fresh and feminine, it can be used as a large wallet or a small, chic evening pouch, either with or without its removable chain.

This Speedy 30 travel bag gets a twist thanks to the mix of printed and embroidered patches adorned with modern redesigns of iconic Louis Vuitton signatures. Originally designed for travelers in the 1930s, with a convenient strap for cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 30 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and eternally stylish.

In Louis Vuitton's supple Mahina leather with distinctive Monogram perforations, this compact wallet will slip into any bag with ease. Its softly rounded flap opens to reveal a practical interior, including slots for credit cards and a zipped pocket for coins.

The matte black Ardillon buckle of the Voyager belt epitomizes the masculine elegance of this belt. Urban and contemporary, the belt is a statement piece. It is finished with meticulously crafted details that pay homage to the rich heritage of the House.

The silk-and-wool Anachronism Monogram shawl features a Monogram jacquard allover, framed by a screen-printed border of stylized flowers. Its Art Deco spirit reflects a key story from Nicolas Ghesquière’s Fall-Winter 2018 ready-to-wear collection. This generous wrap coordinates perfectly with the season’s leather goods and accessories.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

An openwork metal frame gives these cat-eye sunglasses a striking, on-trend allure. The Midnight in Paris model is embellished with a host of subtle yet unmistakable House signatures, including engraved studs, Monogram Flower details and LV Circle emblems.

An update of the classic black model, this Leogram Monogram shawl features a boldly patterned border with a mix of animal motifs and House signatures, including straps, locks and chains. It is one of the season’s hallmark prints, shared with leather goods and fashion jewelry. Woven of silk and wool.

This new double-wrap bracelet in black calf is embellished with meticulously crafted Monogram Flower cut-outs in shiny golden brass. The fastener features an LV Circle, for an unmistakable signature piece – an ideal gift for House aficionados.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

Pleasingly classic lines and supple Taiga leather make the Anton Pochette an ideal option for every day. Compact and comfortable to carry, this new model features refined detailing: witness the discreet metal signature on the bag’s front pocket.

These on-trend “mask” sunglasses are adorned with metal Monogram Flower inserts fitted into the lenses, for a luxe, “crafted” touch. Lightweight, protective and easy to wear, the Purple Rain model is offered in a range of fashionable colors.

With its ladylike shape, reminiscent of the original Vernis bags from 1999 and 2000, the Neo Triangle glams up any scene. Its shiny shiny Monogram Embossed patent leather in stylish tones and perfect proportions prove that indeed, small is beautiful.
Blooming reinterprets the Maison's iconic LV Circle and Monogram Flower signatures as dangling charms. A perfect gift, this feminine bracelet is an effortlessly chic adornment for the wrist.
This business buckle provides a perfect option for more understated looks. Coloured edge dying adds a twist to the Taiga leather strap, with an LV cutout contributing a subtle branded touch.
This trendy tie combines the Monogram Constellation pattern with a washed denim print for a subtle vintage look.

The Flower compact wallet is an elegant, feminine design playing on two iconic Louis Vuitton signatures: the Monogram flower and the padlock. In Monogram canvas with a leather front pocket and lining, it has space for all everyday essentials. In compact version, the Flower wallet can be carried in the smallest bags.

The Flower wallet is an elegant, feminine design playing on two iconic Louis Vuitton signatures: the Monogram flower and the padlock. In Monogram canvas with a leather front pocket and lining, it has ample space for all everyday essentials.

This Very Messenger handbag is fashioned from a combination of smooth leather and grained leather with a discreet Monogram pattern. Signed with a gold-color chain and Vuitton "V,"it is body friendly, lightweight, and easily holds all daily essentials. The adjustable strap allows for a hands-free cross-body carry or long shoulder wear.

Crafted from Louis Vuitton's signature black Taiga leather, the Coin Card Holder is a neat, slim design which keeps all payment essentials in one secure place. It includes several credit card slots and a compartment for banknotes, in addition to a zipped pocket for coins with a silver-tone zip pull.

The Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Tote in soft calf leather is both on-point and practical: with its luxe quilted detailing and aged-metal hardware, it will dress up any ensemble, while accommodating a full day’s essentials. The sliding-chain handle of this light, body-friendly bag can be adjusted for short or long shoulder carry.

This large version of Louis Vuitton's Pochette Jour is crafted from supple Cuir Taurillon leather, characterized by its soft grain. The iconic LV Circle signature, printed in bright blue, stands out boldly against the black leather. With its wide zipped opening, this spacious pouch can be used as a clutch, laptop holder or document portfolio.

The perfect stole for summer, in a lightweight blend of cotton and silk. Monogram Flower “dots” create a playful 3D effect, for a modern take on a classic pattern. Offered in easy-going blue or feminine pink, it adds a sunny touch to warm-weather looks.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in emblematic Epi leather with a colorful bonded lining, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.

In calf-lined Monogram canvas or punchy red Epi leather, the new Crazy In Lock bracelet wears a charming heart-shaped padlock, finely engraved with the LV Circle signature.  This feminine, collectible piece makes a most romantic little gift.

The best-selling My Fair Lady model is now offered in two fashionable new color combinations. House signatures – note the Essential V metal inserts, iconic trunk studs at the front and LV Circle end tips – lend a special elegance to this ultra-feminine style.

A blend of dyed and lurex yarns produces the unique shimmer of this Shine Monogram shawl.  Its jacquard weave elegantly highlights the contrasts of the allover Monogram pattern. Offered in soft-pink Rose Velours, this enveloping, feminine wrap transitions effortlessly from day to evening. Finished with fringe, it features a woven “Louis Vuitton” signature.

These LV Showdown Sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and light rimless structure. Thin all-metal temples create a hyper-modern feel, while specific Monogram lenses inject a unique touch of branding. Engraved LV initials and Louis Vuitton signatures supply the finishing touches for this fashion-forward piece.

These La Boum sunglasses feature the classic cat-eye shape and an added line of studs evoking Louis Vuitton's iconic trunks. A new model in the collection, the accentuated frame gives a feminine effect while gold-color temples add a luxury feel. Rubber temple tips give a secure comfortable fit.

Oversized fluorescent letters stand out from a gray background on the pure-wool Fluo Louis headband – the extra-large logo and brilliant color are key menswear themes this season. Soft and warm, this vintage-style knitted piece can be worn over the ears or around the neck, to ward off winter’s chill.

The New Wave bag charm and key holder combines playful colors and graphic design, to reinvent the House’s iconic signature. Eye-catching lettering is framed with golden-finish brass for a distinctive look. This versatile piece serves a dual function as a bag charm or key holder.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.

This fashionable Lockme Bucket evokes the elegant yet solid bag custom-made by Louis Vuitton in 1932 for a wealthy vineyard owner to transport bottles of champagne. Its sleek design and signature LV Twist lock make it eternally modern.

Traditional craftsmanship and modern aesthetics merge in this LV Split scarf. The iconic LV signature appears split, with the upper half depicted in a lighter tone to create an animated allover pattern. Elegant color combinations enhance the design, which can be worn alone or with matching gloves and hat. Warm and soft, it is an ideal choice for cooler days.

The Yummy LV bracelet has been updated for the new season in fresh colors. Each version is embellished with a trio of metal studs etched with the Louis Vuitton signature. The clasp is finished with an intricate engraving of the iconic Monogram pattern.

These LV In The Pocket Sunglasses bring together innovation and design to create a strong Louis Vuitton style. Fashionable and timeless, their mixed-material frames feature a luxurious finish and an innovative foldable system. Metal inserts with a Damier design and metal rims laser-engraved with the Damier signature bring a refined branded feel to the piece.

In Louis Vuitton's supple Mahina leather with distinctive Monogram perforations, this compact wallet will slip into any bag with ease. Its softly rounded flap opens to reveal a practical interior, including slots for credit cards and a zipped pocket for coins.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.

Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers. It looks modern and elegant in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.
Understated and easy-going, this must-have tie features a delicate tone-on-tone LV logo in a semi-plain effect. A refined piece, it comes in four classic colours to match any formal look.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.

Combining two of the House's iconic patterns, the historic Karakoram on the front and signature Monogram on the back, the Switch City Scarf is a statement piece for cold weather. Inspired by Louis Vuitton's original 1920s Karakoram design, this reversible piece is crafted from pure cashmere and finished with delicate fringing.

The new mix of Damier Ebene canvas and lightly grained calf leather produces an urban-chic model with a decidedly youthful, modern vibe. A casual style with a fashionable twist, the Clapton is compact yet it holds a long wallet, a phone and other essentials with ease.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Pop V tie sees the House's V signature print reimagined as an allover cartoon motif for a touch of irreverence. Channeling the Pop Art movement, the pure silk tie comes in a range of vivid hues whose patterned 3-D effect immediately catches the eye.

The ultra-compact Zippy coin purse looks glamorous in glossy Monogram Vernis leather. Ideal for everyday use, it securely holds small change, credit cards and folded bills, and easily slips into a pocket.
A perfect gift, this stylish silk twill square is printed with emblematic Louis Vuitton details - leather straps, metal chains and padlocks - on a background of the iconic Monogram pattern.
This woven piece reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic V signature in a luxurious heavy jacquard. Available in a range of classic colours, it will brighten up both business looks and special occasions.

Crafted from Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, the extra-flat Pince Wallet easily slips into a jacket or trouser pocket. Its functional design features an articulated clip to hold tickets and notes.

Crafted in bold, contrasting colors of Epi leather this tote combines distinctive design and flawless functionality. The outside pocket features a double-zip closure with signature leather pulls; inside, three compartments keep belongings in order. The two Toron handles and detachable strap offer multiple carry options.   Reserve now by calling Client Services at +1.866.VUITTON

Lightweight and versatile, this sporty Matchpoint Backpack delivers both style and comfort. It flawlessly mixes nylon and mesh with iconic Damier Cobalt coated canvas and supple Taiga leather for a sporty chic bag that’s extremely body-friendy.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Zippy Organizer wallet in historic Monogram canvas combines sleek design with true functionality, all in an extremely compact format. Its all-round zipper opens to reveal an array of practical features, including multiple credit card slots, a zipped coin compartment and a large pocket for plane tickets.

The Matchpoint collection mixes sporty details with luxury know-how on stylish designs adapted to the lifestyles of modern men. The Multiple wallet in Damier Coastline canvas holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format.

These aviator-style Clockwise sunglasses have a modern look thanks to a rimless frame and a flat front. They feature a double bar at the brow, LV Initials engraved on the end pieces and the Louis Vuitton logo at the temples. The metal elements are contrasted with colored gradient mirror or signature Monogram lenses.

The Oliver briefcase, crafted from signature Epi leather, combines elegant details with contemporary lines for a refined business-to-city bag that accommodates office paperwork as well as a laptop in a separate padded compartment. The Oliver can be carried by hand, over the shoulder or cross-body on the detachable leather strap.

The Zoé compact wallet looks chic in softly grained Monogram Empreinte leather, which is embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern. Small enough to fit into even a tiny bag or clutch, yet with space for coins, notes and credit cards, this neat wallet is the ultimate mini companion.

A familiar pilot shape is reimagined with modern touches for Louis Vuitton's new aviator-style Grease sunglasses. The temples, keyhole nose and open-work top bar are crafted from polished gold-color metal for a luxury feel. Adjustable nose pads and flex hinges help ensure a comfortable fit.

Louis Vuitton's instantly recognizable hat box in a charming miniature format, the Boite Chapeau bag charm and key holder is a collectible piece. This petite accessory contains two mirrors and is encased in signature Monogram canvas with a gold-color metal trim. The stripes are a nod to the House's trunk-making heritage, and the design can be personalized.

The Time Trunk Monogram square features a key print from the Fall-Winter 2018 runway. Inspired by travel and trunks, thephotographic print is composed of buckles, locks, straps – with actual metal studs to heighten the trompe-l’oeil effect. Made from an all-silk jacquard weave, it complements the season’s leather-goods collection.

For the LV Stories seasonal collection, the Twist wallet in black Epi leather is embellished with colorful patches which playfully reference Louis Vuitton's travel and trunk-making heritage. Distinguished by its iconic Twist turn lock, this elegant flap wallet offers multiple pockets and credit-card slots.

Oversized fluorescent letters stand out from a gray background on the pure-wool Fluo Louis headband – the extra-large logo and brilliant color are key menswear themes this season. Soft and warm, this vintage-style knitted piece can be worn over the ears or around the neck, to ward off winter’s chill.

Part of a transversal theme across ready-to-wear and leather goods, the LV Upside Down bag charm and key holder playfully reinterprets the iconic LV Initials featured a coral finish. Color-matched with the leather goods collection, this stylish accessory can be hung from a bag or used as a fully functional key ring.
Lightweight but robust, this leather bag holder can be used to secure your bag on the top of your rolling luggage. This practical travel accessory facilitates any journey.

A new take on Louis Vuitton’s Monogram ID theme, the LV Tab bag charm and key holder features iconic padlock details and a masculine design. Vibrant Lava orange Epi leather combines with laser-cut LV Initials to make a street-style statement. This versatile accessory functions as a bag charm or key holder.

For the LV Soleil seasonal collection, the Capucines wallet in black Cuir Taurillon leather is embellished with a sun-ray motif inspired by the monumental sun sculpture on Louis Vuitton's Place Vendôme store in Paris. The silver and gold-tone studs stand out against the finely grained leather of this elegant and practical flap wallet.
As an elegant, modern bag for city living, the Roman PM in cross grained Taïga leather has no parallel. With its specially designed iPad pocket, it also makes an excellent choice for short trips.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in emblematic Epi leather with a colorful bonded lining, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.
Featuring a trendy round shape, this model exudes modern retro cool. Its mix of materials offers a play of contrasts, while Damier details on the rim add a subtle Louis Vuitton signature.
Launched in Fall 2017, the St Sulpice is already a classic LV chain bag. The smart metallic lock, contrasting leather edging, and adorable size make this BB version your go-to everyday chic solution.

Louis Vuitton invites you to travel with peace of mind, tracing your connected luggage in the main worldwide airports. Get notified on your smartphone or your Tambour Horizon after landing: to know whether your luggage has arrived in the right airport or not. The services are accessed exclusively by downloading and using the Louis Vuitton App application.

The LV Upside Down Discovery Pochette in Monogram Ink canvas is a stylish way to carry documents and other belongings. Printed in coral pink with the playful LV Upside Down logo, it features coordinating pink and navy hardware. It can be hand-held as a clutch or a document wallet, or slipped inside a larger bag.
Slender by name, slender by nature. This wallet in smooth Taiga leather is suitably compact and slim, will carry all the essentials and still fit into a front or back pocket with ease.
These stylish sunglasses feature on-trend round lenses and transparent frames integrating a flash of color. The round shape particularly suits square and oval faces.

Woven of a light, soft blend of cotton and wool, this new stole presents an on-point camouflage pattern, screen-printed on a background of Monogram jacquard. A perfect mid-season piece, generously sized to make a bold fashion statement.

The LV New Wave belt is a modern imagining of the Louis Vuitton signature. It features raised relief images for an interesting texture to touch, and a brass buckle with gold-color finishing. The LV New Wave captures both the history and art of the House's craftsmen.

Inspired by the space theme of Louis Vuitton's Fall-Winter 2018-19 fashion show, the Pochette Cosmos is a contemporary clutch with an outside zipped pocket and room inside for everyday essentials. It is crafted from black Dark Infinity calf leather, one of the key materials of the show, and embossed with the Louis Vuitton signature.

This slim-line version of the Danube city bag adds an on-trend touch to any casual outfit. Crafted from colorful Epi leather paired with Damier Graphite canvas and set off by silver metal hardware, it is a compact yet functional model with an adjustable strap, wide zipped opening and convenient front pocket. An ideal companion for everyday wear.

In a tribute to Louis Vuitton's travel inspiration, these trendy pearl bracelets are like souvenirs brought back from the beaches of Hawaii. Their precious mix of materials is a tribute to the Maison's savoir-faire.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this sporty piece features a pattern made up of colourful trunk stamps. Available in two colour options, it is a playful hat to wear alone or combined with its matching scarf.

Fall-Winter 2018 sees the Petite Malle Time Trunk handbag reimagined with a nod to the House's trunk-making heritage. Crafted from an elegant patchwork of transformed canvas and calfskin leather in contrasting tones, the piece features a playful mix of trompe l’oeil and trunk details. Gold-color hardware and a distinct S-lock clasp add extra luster to the compact handbag.

The Daily Confidential bracelet is crafted from calf leather and Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas for a two-tone effect. The materials are embellished with a metallic flower in a gold-color finish. A closer look at this new-season item reveals a clasp engraved in the House's iconic Monogram pattern.

The 2019 Agenda Refill collection celebrates a House icon – the Alzer trunk – as it turns up in a different international destination each month. The artistic gouache illustrations and colorful travel stickers are an invitation to record one’s personal adventures, from city to city and day to day. This full-featured model includes a world map and contact book.

Crafted from supple Monogram Empreinte leather, which is embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Daily Pouch is a modern, versatile accessory. It can be carried as a clutch for day or evening, or slipped inside a larger bag, and can also hold business essentials such as documents or a tablet.

The new Keep it bracelet is a calf leather version of an accessory from the Louis Vuitton permanent collection. It is crafted in a range of crayon-box colors, coordinating with the season's leather good and belts. Hardware with a silver finish adds a shimmering contrast to this piece.

Effortlessly practical, the Neverfull MM is an ideal tote whose laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag. This version with its trompe l'oeil LV trunk details brings a post-modern twist to a boldly versatile bag.

With its iconic Monogram Eclipse canvas sheathed directly onto metal, this must-have ring has a strong masculine feel. Its play of contrasts between Monogram Eclipse and black leather evokes the trimmings of the Maison's bags.

The Vivienne bag charm and key holder is intricately crafted from Monogram Eclipse canvas and calf leather. This version of Louis Vuitton's mascot has a soft, puffed up body, while her Monogram Flower head and eye make her instantly recognizable. A cute and collectible ornament, Vivienne Doudoune is also a practical key ring.
Your go-to necktie for sartorial panache: the signature Louis Vuitton Damier tie reworked in a more discreet tone-on-tone feel.

For Valentine's Day, a cute bird incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Sarah wallet in Monogram canvas. This envelope-style wallet features an ingeniously designed interior offering a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

LOUIS VUITTON 2018 FIFA WORLD CUP OFFICIAL LICENSED PRODUCT COLLECTION This special edition of the Slender wallet marks Louis Vuitton's association with the FIFA World Cup™ Russia 2018. Crafted from Epi leather, it is painstakingly embossed with a pattern of hexagons evoking the look and feel of classic footballs. True to its name, this wallet offers various slots and compartments in a slim format.

This must-have accessory offers a play on functionality that pays tribute to the innovative spirit of Louis Vuitton. Engraved with the Maison's iconic Monogram, this versatile ring holder allows you to hold your phone easily and with style.

Inspired by the key holders found on travel bags, this must-have accessory is a functional signature to please any taste. The Maison's new Monogram Eclipse icon combines with LV initials in ruthenium for a stylish piece.

Timeless and sophisticated, this silk square features a frame of Monogram flowers for a feminine semi-plain feel. The all-over Monogram jacquard creates an interplay of shiny and matte effects for this classic wardrobe must-have.

This LV City 35mm Reversible Belt combines plain calf leather with the House’s iconic Damier canvas to supply a choice of styles. The plain leather side is perfect for business occasions, while the reverse’s Damier canvas creates a more urban feel. The new LV buckle provides a tone-on-tone effect, while the 35mm width is ideal to wear with suits.

This elegant Pochette Metis is fashioned of supple Monogram canvas with patches sewn, embroidered, or directly printed onto the canvas to give the impression that they are an integral part of the Monogram motif. Trimmed in natural leather, its compact dimensions open up to reveal many useful pockets and compartments.

These Las Vegas Parano aviator sunglasses are an eye-catching evolution of a Spring-Summer 2018 showpiece. A shell detail around the outer frame adds a contemporary edge. The temples feature Monogram Flowers and gold-color studs, with studs also on the shells, which is a nod to the House’s iconic trunks. The gradient lenses are available with or without a signature Monogram motif.

Evoking the sport universe from the SS18 Men’s show, these trendy accessories reinterpret the Louis Vuitton signature in graphic and reflective lettering. Usable as both bag charms and key holders, they coordinate perfectly with the Maison’s other lines.

A perfect gift for the Chinese New Year, this playful yet refined bracelet celebrates the Year of the Dog. Its metallic medallion is mounted on a double-tour bracelet in Monogram canvas for a feminine and fashionable look.

Louis Vuitton's classic Brazza wallet is embellished by a daring twist between Navy Blue and Light Blue which will highlight any silhouette. The Brazza’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials.

The Zipped Handbag is a practical, on-trend bag made of Monogram Empreinte leather. Four golden studs and a pair of distinctive angled zippers adorn the front, the latter accented with contrasting leather pulls. Two handles and a detachable strap allow for multiple carry styles.

The Daily Pouch contrasts iconic Monogram canvas with subtly grained cowhide leather for a stylish, modern look. Spacious and versatile, it holds all everyday essentials and can be carried on its own or slipped inside a larger bag.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.
Your go-to necktie for sartorial panache: the signature Louis Vuitton Damier tie reworked in a more discreet tone-on-tone feel.
The Brazza is a wallet highly functional with its numerous credit cards slots and bills compartements. In the elegant and very supple Epi leather, it is the perfect everyday life companion.

The perfect summer companion, this effortlessly chic Girolata in Mahina calfskin is versatility incarnate. You can wear it in two ways, with the drawstring open, it can be carried as a large casual tote and without, it is an on-trend bucket bag.

Featuring detailing inspired by Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram Eclipse collection, the classic Monogram chain necklace is a luxurious accessory. The black leather embellishment references trims found on the House's leather goods. A matching chain bracelet in a silver-color finish is available.

The LV Upside Down necklace is part of a transversal theme taking in ready-to-wear and accessories. Playing with the iconic LV Initials, it can be worn on its own or together with other pieces from the collection. The supple chain has three rings enabling it to be adjusted to three different lengths.

Fashioned from Monogram canvas, this one-handled Georges BB bag boasts numerous details inspired by Louis Vuitton’s iconic trunks including a tufted bi-color stripe and signature gold colored lock. Its unexpectedly spacious and well-organized interior, with two separate compartments, make it the perfect bag for active women.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Matchpoint collection mixes sporty details with luxury know-how on stylish designs adapted to the lifestyles of modern men. The classic Brazza wallet in Damier Coastline canvas is elegant and streamlined, with multiple practical features.

This Petite Malle in supple Epi leather was inspired by custom trunks created for wealthy banker Albert Kahn in the early 20th century, personalized with his signature 3 white crosses. Timelessly elegant, it’s an exceptional small bag for evenings out.

The Astrid is an elegant one-handled city bag in delicate grained leather with a smooth leather stripe. Its structured shape and new signature metallic Monogram Flower lock make it a very practical yet ultra-desirable choice.
Inspired by archive posters and Louis Vuitton's travel universe, this cute bag charm creates a fun yet sophisticated look. The fur accessory of the season, it is a perfect summery gift.

Inspired by the Spring/Summer 2018 men's fashion show, the Jungle theme features a playful palm tree print and surfboard-style rainbow Louis Vuitton signature on Damier Cobalt canvas. The iconic Keepall 55 holdall, the original soft travel bag, is a stylish and practical choice for a weekend away.

LOUIS VUITTON 2018 FIFA WORLD CUP OFFICIAL LICENSED PRODUCT COLLECTION Louis Vuitton's iconic Epi leather is embossed with a distinctive hexagonal pattern inspired by classic footballs on this special edition of the Pochette Jour, which was created to mark the House's association with the FIFA World Cup™ Russia 2018. Featuring a wide zipped opening, this pouch can be used as a clutch or document portfolio.

Inspired by the Maison’s trunks, the Twin Locks collection reinterprets the distinctive lock signature in a must-have jewelry range. The pieces offer a refined play on symmetry, with contrasting metallic finishes and decorative details.
For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne MM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.

The ladylike Cherrywood PM in glossy patent leather features a top handle and removable strap trimmed with Monogram canvas. A fashionable daily companion, it opens wide for easy access to the roomy interior. An embossed LV logo and heritage tuck lock are discreet yet distinctive signatures.

Its slim design and pure lines make the Anton Briefcase’s elegant silhouette as appropriate for work as the weekend. Whether you carry it by hand or wear it over the shoulder with the removable strap, you’ll be right on-trend.

As part of the seasonal LV Stories collection, the Pochette Félicie in black Epi leather is embellished with silver-tone studs and elaborately crafted patches, some of which playfully reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage. This versatile pouch has a removable chain, enabling it to be worn on the shoulder or carried as a clutch.

Named after the music genre that defined the 1980s, the Louis Vuitton New Wave Zipped Compact Wallet is a lightweight wallet in quilted calf leather, signed with the distinctive LV Initials in aged metal. Its smartly organized interior easily holds a woman’s essentials and fits in most pockets and bags.

The Monogram Layers tie is a timeless piece that makes an ideal partner for business ensembles. It blends a subtle allover pattern, incorporating the Louis Vuitton Monogram print, with a gradient stripe for contrast. Available in a selection of deep hues, this tie is a classic piece.
This playful bag charm is inspired by Vivienne, the friendly mascot who encapsulates Louis Vuitton's savoir-faire. Highly collectible, it features contrasting coloured leather on the front and back.

Reinterpreting Louis Vuitton's classic LV Initials signature, this iconic accessory can be used as a key holder or bag charm. With its smooth round edges, it is a true must-have that can be paired with any bag from the Maison's collections.

Inspired by the iconic padlock from Louis Vuitton's trunks, this highly feminine piece makes a perfect Christmas or Valentine's Day gift. Mounted on a fine gold chain, it glitters with its sparkling micro-paving in white strass.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

Part of a collection inspired by the animals of the Chinese zodiac, this adorable Rabbit bag charm and key holder is crafted from calf leather and Monogram Eclipse canvas. Its padded body makes it particularly appealing, while it also serves a dual purpose as a key ring and bag ornament.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.

In supple Taiga leather, the discreet Clutch Kasaï can be carried under the arm or slipped around the wrist, thanks to its strap. Suitably compact yet practical with many sophisticated details, it delivers a refined, masculine look.

Composed of blooming Monogram Flowers, LV Eden is a romantic, feminine pattern, rendered in an arty “watercolor” style on pure silk fabric. The slim bandeau model can be worn as a head, waist, wrist or neck wrap, or rolled around the handles of a bag.

The sporty Discovery Messenger MM bag in extra supple Damier Infini cowhide leather is easy to wear and easy to match. Slightly larger than many of our Messenager bags, it has room for a laptop while the external zipper pocket means quick access to your essentials.

Influenced by the House's permanent Keep It collection, this stylish bracelet is a statement piece. The metal hardware is intricately engraved with the Louis Vuitton Paris signature. Crafted from Damier printed canvas, this bracelet is ideal as a statement accessory.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle meticulously inlaid with a blue lacquered piece , this reversible belt offers two looks in one: graphic and iconic on the Damier canvas side, bold and stylish on the calf leather side.

An openwork metal frame gives these cat-eye sunglasses a striking, on-trend allure. The Midnight in Paris model is embellished with a host of subtle yet unmistakable House signatures, including engraved studs, Monogram Flower details and LV Circle emblems.

The Metropole belt in Monogram Ink canvas references a design found in the Louis Vuitton archives. Its distinctive buckle, in calf leather with a coral-colored metal frame, is printed with the LV Upside Down logo. This is one of the key themes of the season, interpreted across shoes, accessories and leather goods.
