The best-selling My Fair Lady model is now offered in two fashionable new color combinations. House signatures – note the Essential V metal inserts, iconic trunk studs at the front and LV Circle end tips – lend a special elegance to this ultra-feminine style.

The Eden stole is abloom with Monogram Flowers handled in a romantic "watercolor" style. A perfect mid-season piece, the light silk-and-wool blend envelops the wearer in a cloud of softness. The fresh floral pattern adds an artful touch to any silhouette.

The envelope-style Sarah Wallet in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather has an ingeniously designed interior, featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots. As with all drummed leathers, Monogram Empreinte becomes slightly more supple with use.
This business buckle provides a perfect option for more understated looks. Coloured edge dying adds a twist to the Taiga leather strap, with an LV cutout contributing a subtle branded touch.

This eye-catching accessory reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram Flower signature in a playful spirit that evokes Japanese origami. Its sophisticated 3D design plays with volume and associations of materials and colours.

The Capucines Compact Wallet in grained Taurillon leather is embellished with a discreet row of printed Monogram Flowers on the top edge of the flap. The flowers are surrounded by metallic studs, giving them an edgy elegance. The well-designed interior features a variety of practical pockets and card slots.

Inspired by the key holders found on travel bags, this must-have accessory is a functional signature to please any taste. The iconic Monogram Macassar canvas combines with LV initials in matte black lacquer for a classic piece.
This classic striped tie combines a gradient effect with a contrasting Monogram motif. An ideal choice for business and formal looks, it makes a perfect gift.

The elegant, envelope-style Pallas wallet in Monogram canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by brightly colored leather trim. Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock guarantees security, while inside there is ample space for all everyday essentials.

This stylish and easy-to-wear messenger bag in Damier Graphite canvas edges toward sportswear thanks to its colored metallic parts and a bi-color textile strap. The District MM the perfect antidote to everyday life.
This must-have accessory reinterprets the Maison's iconic initials as a feminine bag charm. Small Monogram Flower charms complement the design for an extra touch of sophistication.

Part of a whole collection of Chinese zodiac animals, this friendly Tiger bag charm and key holder has a padded body in iconic Monogram canvas with calf-leather details. In addition to being a cute and collectible bag charm, it is also a perfectly functional key ring.
These sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and gradient Monogram lenses. They are available in a rainbow of colors, with studs adding an extra signature detail.

The Capucines Flower Smile wallet in softly grained Taurillon leather is a richly embellished design combining Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram Flowers with silver and gold-tone studs, while the signature LV Initials clasp is partially covered in precious python leather. The wallet's well-designed interior features a variety of practical pockets and card slots.

With its emblematic V pattern fashioned from a mix of grained beige and black calf leather and gray suede leather, this graphic version of the Nicolas Ghesquière's now-iconic City Steamer is the perfect upscale office bag. Large enough to hold A4 files, the removable shoulder strap and Toron handles allow two carrying options: hand and shoulder.

Composed of blooming Monogram Flowers, LV Eden is a romantic, feminine pattern, rendered in an arty “watercolor” style on pure silk fabric. Screen-printed in 12 colors the 90cm square has hand-rolled edges and comes in summery blue and peach versions.

The emblematic Twist bag gets an edgy rock feel thanks to the alternating studs and eyelets that adorn this model’s flap. The ultimate chic little bag takes a bold look at what’s happening on the streets.

The sunburst motif on this Capucines PM handbag is a nod to the monumental Sun sculpture that reigns over the Louis Vuitton store on Place Vendôme in Paris. Composed of silver- and golden-finish studs, the shining rays give a modern, metallic allure to the ever-chic Capucines, crafted from full-grain Taurillon leather and lined in calfskin.

The emblematic Twist Chain wallet in Epi leather is a stylish and versatile design which can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Crafted of supremely supple Monogram Empreinte leather, the Ponthieu PM shoulder tote makes a stylish daily companion. Effortlessly chic (note the hoop detail on the handles and signature zip pulls), it is versatile too, with a removable strap for cross-body wear.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton’s origins as a luxury trunk maker, this one-handled Cherrywood BB handbag is fashioned from Monogram canvas combined with modern Miroir Vernis patent leather and natural cowhide details. Discreet signatures such as the emblematic tuck lock and embossed LV bring understated elegance. This versatile bag boasts a top handle and a hands-free cross-body carry option thanks to the removable and adjustable strap. Easy-to-wear and trendy, it is perfectly suited for shopping afternoons or day-to-evening use.

Crafted from Louis Vuitton's iconic Epi leather with its distinctive grain, the Zippy Organizer is the perfect wallet for modern lifestyles. Its space-efficient design fits numerous essential features, including credit card slots, a secure coin pocket and two large bill compartments, into an extremely compact, zip-around format.
Matching our Leather Goods, this new belt suits both business silhouettes and more modern looks. The buckle features a sleek tone-on-tone plaque, with an LV logo adding a subtle signature.

A contemporary take on the classic schoolbag, the updated Mylockme is a sleek, ultra-fashionable model crafted of soft, supple calf. Versatile and functional, with a well-organized interior, it can be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body.

These cute accessories play with iconic Louis Vuitton codes to bring animals to life as playful bag charms and key holders. Ideal gifts, they coordinate perfectly with the Maison’s leather goods lines and can be personalized with hot-stamped initials.

With its trendy, large pilot shape this lightweight, metal design is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes. The cutout V design on the bridge offers a distinctive branded signature with a contrasting matt/shiny effect. Mirror or more classic lenses available.

Floral motifs inspired by 18th-century French tapestries were a strong story at the SS18 show. Transposed onto lightweight shawls, the colorful patterns make a romantic style statement. Offered in white, for a fresh signature, or black, for day-to-evening elegance.

The LV Upside Down necklace is part of a transversal theme taking in ready-to-wear and accessories. Playing with the iconic LV Initials, it can be worn on its own or together with other pieces from the collection. The supple chain has three rings enabling it to be adjusted to three different lengths.
These stylish sunglasses feature on-trend round lenses and transparent frames integrating a flash of color. The round shape particularly suits square and oval faces.

The Graceful PM looks fresh and feminine in supple Damier Azur canvas. This spacious hobo has a lightweight, body-friendly design that makes it perfect for every day. The flat handle sits easily on the shoulder, while emblematic details, such as the leather name tag, reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Inspired by Kansai Yamamoto's contribution to the SS18 Cruise collection, this notebook is a nomadic object for collectors everywhere. With their vibrant colours, its oversized stickers are playful symbols of good luck.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Monogram canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

Specifically designed for the iPhone 8, this modern wallet in Damier Graphite canvas combines a purse, a card holder and a phone case in one playful and versatile package. The different elements can be detached, while the removable strap enables the wallet to be carried stylishly around the wrist.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.

The Discovery backpack forms part of a special leather goods collection marking Louis Vuitton's association with the FIFA World Cup™ Russia 2018. The sleek design of the backpack lends itself to the eye-catching hexagonal pattern inspired by vintage footballs, which is embossed on the House's iconic Epi leather using an innovative three-stage procedure. LOUIS VUITTON 2018 FIFA WORLD CUP OFFICIAL LICENSED PRODUCT COLLECTION

The LV Pure hat is characterized by a contrasted knitted technique, which gives it a textured finish. Inspired by the Fall-Winter 2018 Pre-Collection, a distinctive feature is the LV Pure signature. Crafted from wool for a cozy feel, this versatile piece can be worn with the matching scarf or snood for a coordinated look.

The Morningram belt displays the Louis Vuitton signature on its elegant Monogram canvas strap. The versatile belt can be reversed, showcasing the stylish calf leather that gives the belt a new dimension. A bold brass buckle with gold-color finishing effortlessly completes the look.

This pocket square belongs to a capsule collection that features animals of the Chinese zodiac, constructed of Monogram and Damier motifs. Fashioned of pure silk, this playful piece coordinates with a matching tie as well as with the season’s leather goods and fashion jewelry. Definitely collectible.

In a tribute to Louis Vuitton's metalwork savoir-faire, this graphic necklace reinterprets the lozine details from the Maison's historic trunks. Inspired by the razor blade shape, it is a classic fashion item for any man's wardrobe.

This Alma PM in smooth glossy Mirroir patent leather with iconic Monogram canvas shines above all the rest. The oversized LV signature that adorns its instantly recognizable shape is embossed to perfectly disrupt the fashion status quo.

Made from luxurious silk, the Pop Confidential square features a new seasonal interpretation of the iconic Monogram Confidential pattern. The playful print includes a mix of Louis Vuitton's hallmark symbols from fashion jewelry and leather goods. This expertly crafted scarf makes an ideal gift for Monogram devotees.

This Surene MM handbag in Monogram canvas and grained calf leather, with colored-leather details on the sides and the name tag attached to the eyelet, is a functional and stylish chain bag. Big enough to fit A4 files and easy to wear thanks to the calf-leather shoulder pads on the two chains straps, the bag boasts a well-organized interior with three separate compartments.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

The Blooming Flowers chain bag charm and key holder is a tribute to Louis Vuitton's expertise in leather goods. A selection of charms inspired by Monogram Flower, one of the House's most recognizable prints, adorn the gold-color chain of this ornament. It also features a dual-function clasp to effortlessly attach onto a bag or keys.

Warm and enveloping, this voluminous wool-and-silk blend shawl features an allover of a new, larger Monogram pattern, which is sure to delight fans of the iconic motif. Finished with delicate fringe and a woven “Louis Vuitton Paris” signature.

On-point style and timeless design make the Boccador handbag a covetable complement to any wardrobe. Crafted from Epi leather, it is embellished with details inspired by classic House trunks, including a contoured top handle and a magnetic metal lock. A new signature, the lock provides easy access to belongings, while keeping them secure. The detachable strap offers the option of effortless shoulder or cross-body carry.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.

A bright palladium finish gives the Essential V jewelry line a modern look signed discretely. This supple bracelet combines Louis Vuitton's graphic V motif with the LV Circle signature on the chain and clasp.

A familiar pilot shape is reimagined with modern touches for Louis Vuitton's new aviator-style Grease sunglasses. The temples, keyhole nose and open-work top bar are crafted from polished gold-color metal for a luxury feel. Adjustable nose pads and flex hinges help ensure a comfortable fit.

The Telling Monogram stole pairs the hallmark Epi and Monogram prints with modern detailing for a versatile finish. This soft wool shawl is enhanced by a subtle gradient effect and contrasted fringes. Generous proportions allow a variety of styling options while making it a cozy cool weather essential.

It was on the Rue des Capucines in Paris that the first Louis Vuitton store opened its doors. As timeless as the House itself, the Capucines bag brings chic sophistication to any look. Full-grain Taurillon leather combines with precious python to create a luxurious handbag accented with heritage details: the LV initials, the distinctive side rings and the subtle Monogram flower on the closing flap. With its top handle, removable strap and signature flap, this timeless model can be worn in several ways, to fit any outfit or mood.
This generously sized towel in Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern comes in velvet-soft, jacquard-weave cotton for style and luxury on the beach.

The LV List all-cotton bandanna adds a dash of graphic style to any casual look. Inspired by the logomania theme of this season’s ready to wear, the scarf can be worn wrapped around the neck, tied loosely with the point down, or knotted on a bag strap for an edgy accent.

Inspired by the House’s early explorer clients and Gaston-Louis Vuitton’s drawings from the archives, Louis Vuitton brings the House’s timeless Karakoram pattern to the Speedy 30. A bright zigzag in small grained leather crosses the Damier Ebene coated canvas, bringing a graphic feel to an iconic bag. Engraved gold-color studs and padlock add luster.

The Monogram Layers tie is a timeless piece that makes an ideal partner for business ensembles. It blends a subtle allover pattern, incorporating the Louis Vuitton Monogram print, with a gradient stripe for contrast. Available in a selection of deep hues, this tie is a classic piece.

A bold frame on these La Piscine V sunglasses is softened with facet work for a well-pitched statement. The design is given a luxury finish with gold-color accents including V inlays at the temple and studs at the rim. The acetate structure features comfortable rounded tips.

The LV Circle reversible belt features a striking buckle with an iconic LV Circle logo. It is crafted from either Epi leather or signature Monogram canvas, with contrasting effects on the reverse. The oversized logo plaque enhances this belt with an eye-catching finish.

First created in Fall-Winter 2018, the Daily Confidential bracelet has been reworked in Rose Ballerine pink. It is crafted from patent leather and the House's classic Monogram canvas. A metallic folded flower in a gold-color finish fuses these materials together. The bracelet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Vernis Milkshake line of leather goods.

Practical yet feminine, the Victorine wallet in supple Monogram Empreinte leather is the ultimate compact companion. Every detail has been carefully considered to create a small wallet able to hold as much as a long one.

Carry your essentials with style in this sporty Discovery Messenger BB. This small bag’s distinctive Messenger shape and supple Damier Infini leather for super body-friendly wear make it the one. Perfect for a wallet and a smartphone.

The Magic Monogram stole features the classic Monogram pattern combined with a romantic floral print for a feminine update. This reimagined style comes in three versatile hues to complement a variety of moods. Crafted with a hint of cashmere, the stole's generous dimensions make it a cozy accessory on cooler days.

These Mascot Pilot sunglasses are a sophisticated mix of metal and acetate. The iconic V shape at the bridge is the central focus of these aviator sunglasses, with open metal work highlighting their strong silhouette. Distinctive House touches include the Louis Vuitton signature at the temples, LV Initials on the lenses and the Monogram design on the bar.

The delicate Miss LV bracelet displays the signature Monogram Flower pattern embellished on a bouquet of pastel-color enamel and metal discs. Reversing the piece showcases the LV signature etched on each charm. An adjustable gold-finish chain is further detailed with the LV Circle.

Presenting the Louis Vuitton New Wave Chain Bag PM, a statement piece destined to become a fashionable wardrobe staple. Made from smooth quilted calfskin, it features a removable handle with a colorful “Louis Vuitton” signature. An aged-metal finish adds richness to the bag’s hardware and sliding chain, which adapts to long- and short-shoulder or cross-body wear.

The Party goes on, now in an oversize square model and stylish colors, including a new gradient blue. Engraved studs outline the lenses, a nod to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage further underscored by LV Circle emblems on the lenses and end tips.

The Zippy Coin Purse looks fresh in pale-pink Epi leather with contrasting red corners as part of the Epi Blooming Corners limited edition. Inspired by Louis Vuitton trunks, the corner detail evokes the House's iconic Monogram flowers. With its zip-around format, this compact purse is a safe way to carry cash and cards.

A stylish essential to take everywhere with you, this notebook is covered in Damier Azur canvas printed with trompe-l'œil details inspired by Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. The pages are crafted from high-quality paper with the LV watermark and soft pink edges for a feminine touch.

The Discovery backpack forms part of a special leather goods collection marking Louis Vuitton's association with the FIFA World Cup™ Russia 2018. The sleek design of the backpack lends itself to the eye-catching hexagonal pattern inspired by vintage footballs, which is embossed on the House's iconic Epi leather using an innovative three-stage procedure. LOUIS VUITTON 2018 FIFA WORLD CUP OFFICIAL LICENSED PRODUCT COLLECTION

Nicolas Ghesquière updated the Chantilly bag on its 40th anniversary. Made of Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas trimmed with calf leather, it features a redesigned, embellished padlock. An edgy piece with a boho-chic spirit, for day to after dark.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers.
These sunglasses make a strong fashion statement with their mask shape and gradient Monogram lenses. They are available in a rainbow of colors, with studs adding an extra signature detail.

For Valentine's Day, an adorable dog incorporating iconic Louis Vuitton details adds a touch of fun to the Zippy wallet in Monogram canvas. Combining well-organized functionalities with a pure design, it is the perfect choice for a modern lifestyle.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.

These on-trend metal frames feature a thin openwork design that makes them light and comfortable to wear. Black lacquer adds a note of contrast, while the V signature at the bridge provides a subtle touch of branding.

A French garden blooms in light, fresh shades of pink and green on this luxurious silk jacquard scarf. Romantic 18th-century motifs mix with the modern LV Circle signature, for an accessory that will bring delicate color and sophistication to any silhouette.

The New Wave bag charm and key holder reinterprets the House’s instantly recognizable LV signature. Graphic design is a hallmark of the New Wave story and this playful accessory features eye-catching colors and the iconic Monogram Flower. With a brass golden-finish, this key ring and bag clip offers versatility.

The Monogram Classic tie in gray combines delicate craftsmanship with timeless House style. A dotted jacquard background sets off the Monogram print in a subtle combination. The fine silk creates a luxurious finish sure to complement any business outfit.

Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern forms the background of this elegant stole with an intriguing fade-out effect. Its generous dimensions make it easy to style in different ways, while its airy blend of silk and cotton is ideal for mid-season.

Customize your favorite Louis Vuitton bag with this strap in Monogram canvas adorned with contemporary redesigns of emblematic signatures such as the LV Initials and the Monogram Flower. A tribute to the House’s travel and trunk making heritage, these playful printed patches evoke the stickers that adorned trunks at the turn of the century.

The Epi Patchwork edition of the Christopher backpack makes a strong style statement with a mix of richly colored leather and Monogram canvas. Robust and functional, this PM model is equipped with adjustable shoulder straps, a top handle for another carry option, and multiple pockets, inside and out. The leather flap with a press-stud closure keeps belongings secure.

For Mother's Day, Louis Vuitton has created a collectible limited edition of cute animals featuring iconic House signatures. This bird key holder and bag charm is crafted from Epi leather and Monogram canvas.

Timeless and sophisticated, this silk square features a frame of Monogram flowers for a feminine semi-plain feel. The all-over Monogram jacquard creates an interplay of shiny and matte effects for this classic wardrobe must-have.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this sporty piece features an eye-catching pattern made up of colourful trunk stamps. Available in two colour options, it is a playful piece to wear alone or combined with its matching hat.

Showcasing the brand new Monogram White canvas, this new animation of the Reverso buckle makes a strong fashion statement. The reversible option makes it two belts in one, with a summery white side complemented by casual navy.

Adorned with this season's Hawaii-inspired signature print, this functional piece can be used as a bag charm or worn on a belt loop. Trendy and easy to wear, it is a perfect match for this season's ready-to-wear pieces.
Elegance is personified in the petite shape of the Pochette Metis. Made of supple Monogram empreinte leather, its compact dimensions open up to reveal many useful pockets and compartments.

Launched in Fall-Winter 2017, the Blurrygram Monogram shawl fuses the classic Monogram motif with an elegant gradient design. Crafted from a soft silk and cotton blend, this subtle piece is finished with a fringed hem for a modern feel. It comes in three complementary colors to accentuate an array of styles.

This new metal model offers an innovative blend of Monogram canvas and rubber on the temples, making it extremely comfortable to wear. Available in a choice of Monogram Ebene or Monogram Eclipse, it is ideal for round and oval face shapes.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière revisits the iconic Petite Malle  in a sophisticated blend of corduroy, Monogram canvas and leather paired with a bold leopard-skin print. The silver-colored S-lock clasp adds an additional touch of modernity. This bag’s combination of diverse materials is an example of Louis Vuitton’s exquisite craftsmanship.

An essential accessory for chic adventurers, this straw sun visor is meticulously woven to reveal the iconic Monogram pattern, while natural leather details recall Louis Vuitton's heritage and craftsmanship.

The Toiletry Pouch in iconic Monogram canvas is decorated this season with Louis Vuitton’s modern reinterpretation of traditional travel stickers. It offers a roomy interior and a wide opening while its washable lining makes it easy to clean up spills.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. Crafted of grained Taurillon leather, this city bag that takes care of business, with ample room for papers and files.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in emblematic Epi leather with a colorful bonded lining, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.

Whether you’re looking for discreet fashion statement or just a versatile everyday bag, this sporty Outdoor Messenger is the great choice. Inspired by the Spring Summer 2018 Show, it’s fashioned in our suppler Taiga leather for a surprisingly body-friendly feel.

Unveiled at the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, the patches depicting everyday objects such as watches and lighters that adorn this Petite Boite Chapeau in smooth Epi leather give it a playful modern feel. Inspired by Louis Vuitton’s iconic hatbox, the edgy Petite Boite Chapeau is a hard-sided day-to-evening bag that’s small yet practical (it fits an iPhone 7).

A masculine take on the valet tray, this versatile piece is adorned with the Maison’s new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Handy for storing everyday objects, it is inspired by some of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic details: the Monogram, trunk handles and rivets.

The Nil Slim Epi Patchwork bag offers a playful take on a House classic, a favorite with travelers and men on the go. Colorful Epi leather and Monogram canvas combine in a patchwork pattern, set off by silver-color hardware. With numerous pockets and an adjustable strap for hands-free wear, it is a practical and stylish companion.
Luxurious Epi leather makes the Neverfull MM suitable for every occasion. Effortlessly practical, it is an ideal tote or the laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in emblematic Epi leather with a colorful bonded lining, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.

A soft, hexagonal shape gives the LV Chamade model an original twist. The faceted acetate frame is accented with iconic “trunk” studs and Essential V inserts on the temples. Offered in black or tortoise shell, this style can be fitted with corrective lenses.
With numerous carry options, the Montaigne BB is a compact alternative for businesswomen who don’t wish to carry too much. And of course it looks beautiful in Monogram Empreinte leather.
This woven tie combines the Maison's iconic Monogram motif with a coloured gradient. Ideal for business looks, it offers a subtly twisted way of playing stripes.

Featuring the historical shape of the LV Cannes beauty case, designer Nicolas Ghesquière revives a long-standing classic with the Cannes handbag. Petite in size and presented in a mix of Monogram and Monogram reverse coated canvas, the elegant piece reanimates a traditional silhouette steeped in Louis Vuitton heritage. A removable leather strap and top handle provide a range of carrying options.

These Mascot Sunglasses combine trendy transparent mirror lenses with a design centered around the House’s iconic V signature. An intricate blend of acetate and metal, they are available in two stylish color combinations. Alongside the top bar’s metallic V and Monogram design, signatures include LV initials on the lenses and an engraved Louis Vuitton on the temples.

This version of the LV Pyramide 40mm Belt combines natural calf leather with the House’s iconic Louis Vuitton graphic details for a signed and edgy look. The calf leather strap’s embossed Monogram pattern delivers a subtle Louis Vuitton signature. Meanwhile, the LV Pyramide buckle incorporates aged ruthenium finish for a distinctive visual touch.

The ultra-compact Zippy coin purse looks elegant in Louis Vuitton's emblematic Epi leather. Ideal for everyday use, it securely holds small change, credit cards and folded bills, and easily slips into a pocket.

Crafted in luxurious silk, the That's a Wrap square evocatively illustrates the rich trunk-making history of Louis Vuitton. Leather goods, jewelry and iconic House symbols are interwoven creating a colorful graphic print. The merging of modern accents and classic elements gives this travel-inspired scarf timeless appeal.

Decorated with the iconic LV Circle signature first used on our historic trunks, this Bumbag is for the fashion conscious. Compact and crafted in supple Epi leather, it’s ideal for transporting your daily essentials.

Statement of Spring/Summer 2018, the Monogram Blossom story contrasts iconic Monogram canvas with an intriguing floral print. It brings a fashionable touch to the envelope-style Sarah Wallet, which combines an elegant exterior with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The Daily Pouch contrasts iconic Monogram canvas with subtly grained cowhide leather for a stylish, modern look. Spacious and versatile, it holds all everyday essentials and can be carried on its own or slipped inside a larger bag.

The thin strap of the new Snap bracelet wraps twice around the wrist, for an accessory at ease with both business and casual looks. Made of Damier canvas, it is finished with a metal square that echoes the Damier motif, engraved with the “Louis Vuitton” signature.

The Metropole belt in Monogram Ink canvas references a design found in the Louis Vuitton archives. Its distinctive buckle, in calf leather with a coral-colored metal frame, is printed with the LV Upside Down logo. This is one of the key themes of the season, interpreted across shoes, accessories and leather goods.
The Brazza Wallet is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men. It is a practical companion with several different pockets, slots and compartments.

These playful items evoke the spirit of summer, with their blend of seaside artifacts with iconic Louis Vuitton codes. Perfect and accessible gifts, they are ideal to mix and match, with the versatile bag charm doubling as a key holder.

Leopard-style motifs pair up with iconic Monogram and other House signatures on a chic new scarf with timeless appeal. Beautifully woven of pure silk and finished with hand-rolled edges, it adds a polished touch to any look, whether classic or directional.

Slim and sleek, with an inlaid LV clasp that lies flush to the strap, this new masculine bracelet is offered in black calfskin, Monogram or Monogram Eclipse coated canvas. All are calf-leather lined. Easy to wear, this signature piece makes a handsome little gift.

The Helsinki hat and scarf have a new look. Knitted from pure, precious cashmere yarns in an allover Damier pattern, these sporty, generous pieces will keep winter’s chill at bay. A leather patch embossed with the LV initials adds an elegant signature.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's travel heritage, this summery silk and wool shawl is printed with a trompe-l'œil trunk, complete with colorful details such as a Louis Vuitton luggage label and brass hinges and corners. The pale pink Monogram-pattern background makes it easy to match and brings a feminine touch to any outfit.

This adorable Dog bag charm and key holder has a padded body crafted from Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with calf-leather trim, while its eye is a trunk stud. One of a collection of animals celebrating the Chinese zodiac, it can be used both as a bag ornament and a fully functional key ring.

This Very Messenger handbag is fashioned from a combination of smooth leather and grained leather with a discreet Monogram pattern. Signed with a gold-color chain and Vuitton "V,"it is body friendly, lightweight, and easily holds all daily essentials. The adjustable strap allows for a hands-free cross-body carry or long shoulder wear.

This compact Bond Street BB in Damier Ebene canvas and Cuir Taurillon leather, with a central two-tone stripe signed “LV” and leather nametag, harks back to Louis Vuitton’s iconic trunks. The fashionable stripe is a theme this season also featured on the shoe collection. It brings a fresh edge to this feminine city bag.

Chic and understated, the Comete wallet is crafted from luxurious Taurillon leather with a subtle grain and soft feel. The design features an all-round zipper which opens to reveal a functional, well-organized interior with three separate compartments. In a final sophisticated detail, the zip pull is embellished with a tiny Monogram Flower.

A playful take on an iconic handbag, this Twist MM handbag pays homage to Louis Vuitton’s travel and trunk-making heritage. Fashioned from grained Epi leather, it is adorned with travel stickers, evoking House signatures, and finished with contrasting edge-dyeing. The emblematic LV Twist-lock adds a final touch of elegance.

The Reverso reversible belt surprises and delights. The elegant Monogram canvas on one side and calf leather on the other are tastefully offset with a contrasting leather trim. A robust polished silver-color buckle further highlights the understated elegance of this piece.

A masterpiece of craftsmanship, this Twist MM in Epi leather totally reinvents the House’s signature Monogram Flower motif. Decorated with layers of ayers and karung patches as well as LV engraved studs, its poetic floral feel emphasizes the Twist’s distinctive shape.

Created exclusively for the 2018 Summer accessory collection, this Illustrée bag charm and key holder displays a trompe l’oeil Trunk motif. A tribute to Louis Vuitton’s Art of Travel, the detailed design is silk-screened onto Monogram canvas. The reverse side features the signature Malletage pattern, and may be personalized with hot-stamped initials. Polished golden-brass fittings, finely engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature are finished with a miniature leather travel sticker. A stylish gift idea.

Made from luxurious silk, the Pop Confidential square features a new seasonal interpretation of the iconic Monogram Confidential pattern. The playful print includes a mix of Louis Vuitton's hallmark symbols from fashion jewelry and leather goods. This expertly crafted scarf makes an ideal gift for Monogram devotees.

This elegant wallet combines iconic Damier canvas with soft, fine-grained calf leather and a statement clasp inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks. Its well-designed interior offers an array of functional pockets and slots.

Inspired by the Art Nouveau style, the LV Windsor Pearl Bow Gold Earrings made a strong statement at Nicolas Ghesquière’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Decorated with gold-color bows and white pearls enveloped in engraved silver-color wings, they feature a thin chain that falls delicately from the ear, with a tiny leaf and LV Circle at its tip.

The Twist Epi MM steps out for Fall 2018 arrayed in Etain, a mesmerizing metallic shade. A glossy black LV Twist lock accentuates the bag’s pewter-gray signature leather. With its subtle sparkle and modern allure, this piece is perfect for evening, yet it also adds an edgy touch to daytime looks.

Show-stopping Monogram-embossed patent leather makes this Hot Springs Mini-Backpack adorable every day and in every way. As you glibe through the urban wonderland, your adventures in fashion’s upper altitudes will leave your best friends green with envy.

These square LV Player sunglasses present a sporty look with their laminated acetate frames, brow bar and two-tone color. Nods to the House's hallmarks include the Damier signature engraved on the temples and tips, a Louis Vuitton signature on the side and LV Initials on the lenses. Solid-colored sun lenses complete this elegant design.

The name says it all: beautiful and desirable, the Venus, inspired from the Steamer, a House icon (1901), for today's urban lifestyles. In Monogram canvas with colored cowhide leather trim, its generous capacity makes this bag ideal for day-to-office use.

Featuring the famous LV Initiales buckle meticulously inlaid with a blue lacquered piece , this reversible belt offers two looks in one: graphic and iconic on the Damier canvas side, bold and stylish on the calf leather side.

The LV Jungle sunglasses are reimagined in new season colors. These frames combine horn effects and solid acetate to create a sophisticated contrast. Their round shape and keyhole nose detail add retro accents, complemented by iconic House hallmarks, such as Louis Vuitton signatures on the temples and LV Initials engraved on the lenses.

Celebrate the return of LV Vernis leather with this Hot Springs Mini-Backpack in patent leather and Monogram canvas. As cute as it is versatile, this is the fashionable everyday bag you’ve been waiting for all year.

This Voyager 35mm Belt gives pride of place to the new Monogram Titanium canvas, introduced at the Men’s Fall-Winter 2018 Show. Lined with calf leather, it also features iconic natural leather details that will acquire a distinctive patina over time. The roller on the ardillon buckle is engraved with a discreet Louis Vuitton signature.

Coordinating with the Louis Vuitton leather goods collection, the Voyager belt in supple Monogram Eclipse canvas offers a smart-casual look. It is complemented by an LV-engraved metal buckle with a distinctive dark-green finish, and is fully lined with calf leather.

With its cool ”schoolbag” shape in a trendy small size, the Mylockme BB makes a big fashion statement. Crafted of soft calf leather, the bag’s long chain strap can be doubled for short-shoulder carry or worn cross-body. A sleek choice for every day, it has room for all the essentials.

The Clemence Wallet is decorated with colorful patches evocative of the House’s travel and trunk-making heritage. Vivid printed and embroidered ‘stickers’ brighten up the Damier Ebene canvas for a fresh take on this stylish wallet.  The zip-around closure and variety of pockets and credit card slots make it eminently practical.

Simple, yes, but very stylish, this new bracelet is crafted of braided calf leather in Navy or Chocolat. The barrel-shaped metal fastener bears the “Louis Vuitton” signature in finely engraved characters. Worn in multiples, it makes on-trend fashion statement.

This new jacquard shawl in a silk-wool blend features an oversize, high-contrast Monogram motif. Worn looped around the neck, its soft folds and graphic pattern lend effortless style to any look. Offered in edgy Silver, feminine Light Pink or fashionable Neon Pink.

The Cosmos ID holder is crafted from gray Monogram Titanium canvas, seen at Louis Vuitton's Fall-Winter 2018-19 men's fashion show, and complemented by natural cowhide-leather trim. Ideal for carrying essential cards and ID, it can be worn around the neck on its matching ribbon, or simply slipped into a pocket.

A fresh take on the hobo, the Mélie is a must-have addition to fashion-forward wardrobes. Light and body-friendly in Monogram Empreinte, the distinctive North-South shape gets extra style points for its modern zipped pockets with engraved metal pulls.

Spotlighting the iconic LV Twist buckle, the reversible LV Twist belt offers two different, stylish looks in one. On one side, glamorous leopard-print calf leather coordinates with the Prefall 2018 collection. On the other, Louis Vuitton's signature Monogram canvas offers a more relaxed, yet still elegant, option.

The essential accessory for the modern traveller, this passport cover in supple Taiga leather combines style with practicality. It boasts four credit card slots and two flying pockets for easier access to your passport.

The Noé can trace its roots back to 1932 – when a champagne producer asked Gaston-Louis Vuitton to create an elegant and solid bag to carry 5 bottles of champagne. Reshaped and crafted in emblematic Epi leather with a colorful bonded lining, this NéoNoé is today’s answer to yesterday’s longings.

A perfect (and perfectly feminine) bag for business, this functional tote is embellished with a distinctive Monogram Flower padlock in gleaming golden metal. The smooth leather handles and detachable strap provide a variety of carry options, and the well-organized interior easily holds files and a laptop.

This item has very limited availability online and in select stores. Please check back soon.

The Keepall travel bag is a Louis Vuitton icon: a timelessly elegant design first introduced in the 1930s. This special edition in Monogram canvas - part of the Trunk Summer 2018 collection of shoes, accessories and leather goods - pays tribute to the House's travel heritage with colorful trompe-l'oeil details inspired by the historic trunks and appliquéd leather patches.

color: ROSE BOUDOIR LIE DE VIN CREME
en_US_description: A contemporary take on the classic schoolbag, the updated Mylockme is a sleek, ultra-fashionable model crafted of soft, supple calf. Versatile and functional, with a well-organized interior, it can be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body.

Fashioned from smooth calf leather, quilted into a unique wave pattern, the Louis Vuitton New Wave Long Wallet is inspired by the disruptive music  genre from the 1980s. This long flap wallet has a large interior with multiple slots and pockets and a removable “Vuitton” embossed leather strap for clutch carry.

Made of colorful Taurillon skin in a charming BB size, the Capucines Flower Smile for Summer ’18 is embellished with leather Monogram Flowers and metal-studded Taïga leather patches. The motifs form a “V” for Vuitton along the top of the bag. The long strap, for shoulder or cross-body carry, is also accented with shiny golden and silver Monogram blossoms.

Available in two colours, this fashionable scarf combines the Maison's iconic Monogram signature with a camouflage pattern for a trendy look. Warm and easy to wear, it features a subtle gradient effect on the Monogram motif.

Available in timeless black or vivid Coquelicot, this reversible belt offers a choice between iconic Epi leather and Monogram canvas for a more casual look. The new LV Circle buckle adds an extra signature touch.

A versatile day-to-evening piece, this versatile shawl features an all-over Monogram motif embellished with a frame of shiny Monogram flowers. The innovative "fil coupé" technique adds femininity and refinement.

A tribute to the House’s trunk-making heritage, this City Pouch in Monogram canvas is adorned with printed and embroidered patches, reminiscent of the travel stickers found on trunks at the end of the 19th century. The removable wrist strap brings convenience and style to a versatile bag.

The Miss LV long necklace offers a delicate reinterpretation of the Monogram Flower pattern. The gold-color piece features five sets of pastel charms in enamel on metal, with the LV signature engraved on the back of each one. This feminine piece is part of an intricate line of jewelry.

A perfect gift for the Chinese New Year, this playful yet refined bracelet celebrates the Year of the Dog. Its metallic medallion is mounted on a double-tour bracelet in Monogram canvas for a feminine and fashionable look.

This iconic reversible belt is now available in two color combinations that perfectly match the Maison's leather goods. The association of Damier Infini leather with Damier canvases will suit both casual and more daring looks.

Edgy and daring, these new Split bracelets offer contrasting combinations of the Maison's iconic Monogram canvases for a unique bi-color effect. With their thin cord, they are ideal to mix-and-match and accumulate for a strong visual impact.

These innovative all-aluminum frames create a strong surf vibe with their easy-to wear, beach-style square shape. Mirror lenses in the same metallic colors as the frames give the pieces a fun and fashionable touch.

Combining two of the House's iconic patterns, the historic Karakoram on the front and signature Monogram on the back, the Switch City Scarf is a statement piece for cold weather. Inspired by Louis Vuitton's original 1920s Karakoram design, this reversible piece is crafted from pure cashmere and finished with delicate fringing.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

The Hina is two bags in one: gather in the sides on a central snap hook, and the tote transforms into a trendy bucket style. Crafted of perforated calf leather, it is light and comfortable, ideal for everyday wear. The MM model accommodates daily essentials as well as documents and files.
This elegant key holder and bag charm combines the iconic LV Initials signature with Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather for a look that is classic yet modern and colorful.

In a choice of two new colors, the LV Initiales belt is an update on a design from Louis Vuitton's permanent collection. It is crafted from Damier canvas with a calf leather border, in reference to the House's leather goods edit. LV Initials in silver-color brass, inlaid with lacquer, complete this refined piece.

A familiar pilot shape is reimagined with modern touches for Louis Vuitton's new aviator-style Grease sunglasses. The temples, keyhole nose and open-work top bar are crafted from polished gold-color metal for a luxury feel. Adjustable nose pads and flex hinges help ensure a comfortable fit.

The Nil Slim Epi Patchwork bag offers a playful take on a House classic, a favorite with travelers and men on the go. Colorful Epi leather and Damier Graphite canvas combine in a patchwork pattern, set off by silver-color hardware. With numerous pockets and an adjustable strap for hands-free wear, it is a practical and stylish companion.

For the Fall 2018 Pre-collection, Nicolas Ghesquière plays with a daring leopard-skin print, bringing it to the new Wild Petite Boite Chapeau and combining it with a sophisticated mix of  materials like warm corduroy, and iconic Monogram Reverse canvas. Small yet practical, this exclusive piece is an adorable day-to-evening bag.
Available in two timeless colours, this versatile silk stole is embellished with an all-over Monogram jacquard weave. Elegant and chic, it can be worn both as a headscarf and around the neck.
With its sleek, classic lines, the Anton Messenger in Taiga leather moves smoothly from office to off-duty pursuits. Plenty of pockets make it practical; discreet House signatures add refined style.

In contemporary Monogram Eclipse canvas, Louis Vuitton's Zippy Vertical wallet is a stylish and practical way to carry essential cards and cash. It has a secure zip-around design which features multiple credit card slots, a zipped pocket for coins and compartments for papers and banknotes.

The LV Tilt reversible belt features an eye-catching three-dimensional buckle. The sharp lines of the metal buckle contrast with the soft Taurillon leather of the strap. Combining classic and contemporary values, the belt showcases the skills of the Louis Vuitton expert craftsmen.
On this striking key holder and bag charm, the iconic LV Initials signature is inlaid with brightly colored lacquer for a playful, modern look.

The Graphic Paisley Monogram shawl in silk and wool features an elaborate floral pattern inspired by the Fall-Winter 2018 Women's Fashion Show. Its rich burgundy and blue tones are enhanced by precious strass embellishment. The LV initials feature at the center of the shawl, whose background is woven with the iconic Monogram pattern.
This smart yet chic cardholder in Taiga Leather slips easily into a pocket. It can hold credit cards, transport tickets and business cards in its four slots and central pocket.

In creating the Fragrance Travel Cases, Louis Vuitton applies its savoir-faire and mastery in custom-designing the perfect case for transporting and protecting each item of one’s personal belongings. The 100ML travel case conserves and protects your perfume bottle, closing securely with a buckle. Slip it into your bag in every situation.

Chic and understated, the Comete wallet is crafted from luxurious Taurillon leather with a subtle grain and soft feel. The design features an all-round zipper which opens to reveal a functional, well-organized interior with three separate compartments. In a final sophisticated detail, the zip pull is embellished with a tiny Monogram Flower.

With its eye-catching Monogram Flowers allover pattern, this version of the Capucines PM handbag, fashioned of supple Taurillon leather, is in tune with spring fashions. Shaped from cream-colored blossoms surrounded by studs, the Monogram Flowers perfectly complement the black leather.

This Surene BB handbag is an adorable mini-tote bag in supple Monogram Empreinte leather, featuring a subtle tone-on-tone embossed Monogram print. The gold-color chain handles with two calf-leather shoulder pads brings color and elegance to a classic comfortable bag. The removable leather nametag adds that final touch of LV sophistication.

Woven of a light, soft blend of cotton and wool, this new stole presents an on-point camouflage pattern, screen-printed on a background of Monogram jacquard. A perfect mid-season piece, generously sized to make a bold fashion statement.

The Vosges bag presents a supple yet structured shape. Its refined design will enhance every elegant silhouette. The Rose Fizzy Braided detail is a playful hint to the Couture spirit of the House and the contrast of colors adds a luminous touch to the bold Kaki bag.

The playful animal prints on these new Animalle bandeaus are part of a collectible capsule, new this season. Woven of pure silk, the skinny scarves can be worn looped around the neck or knotted on the handles of a favorite bag. A very cool gift idea.

Soft, warm and light, the new Daily Monogram stole displays a large-scale, contrasted version of the iconic House motif. Woven of a balanced blend of wool, cotton and silk, it is a timeless, all-season, must-have piece for every wardrobe.
Perfect to twist a business look, this playful tie combines classic dots with a tone-on-tone trunks pattern symbolizing Louis Vuitton. Available in a range of classic colours, it is a perfect gift.

Inspired by an iconic advertising stamp from the Louis Vuitton archives, this twisted classic offers a modern reinterpretation of the medallion theme. With its two different sides, it is a versatile and easy-to-wear item.

The Tribute to BB Bandeau scarf pays homage to classic Louis Vuitton bags using an inkjet printing technique for modern polish. A photographic treatment lends realism to the purse motif, printed across slim-cut silk. Allover Monogram Flowers on the reverse make for a timeless contrast, appealing to classic and experimental sensibilities.

With different designs on the front and flip sides, the pure-silk Pop Monogram bandeau offers lots of styling options. The Pop-inspired patterns – a key statement this season – feature Monogram Flowers mixed with dots and stripes. This skinny scarf wraps around neck, wrist, head or bag handle. It makes a fashionable gift.
Elegance is personified in the petite shape of the Pochette Métis. Made of supple Monogram empreinte leather, its compact dimensions open up to reveal many useful pockets and compartments.

This Matchpoint Messenger combines a distinctive messenger shape with high performance sportswear details like mesh and nylon. Crafted in iconic House Damier Cobalt coated canvas and supple Taiga leather, it’s nothing less than the everyday bag you’ve always wanted.

The Monogram Blooming Flowers Coquelicot special edition sees Louis Vuitton's Clémence wallet in Monogram canvas take on a bright poppy-red lining and feminine Monogram Flower charm. With its secure zip closure, this elegant wallet conceals a variety of pockets, compartments and credit card slots.
Real New Classic of the House, the Twist MM chain bag is the ideal size for a day-to-evening companion, worn either over the shoulder or cross-body on its long, sliding chain.

With its sharp design and refined lines, this chic modern belt has been specially designed to complement business suits. Featuring an embossed Damier pattern, this reversible piece is available in two easy-to-match colour combinations.

The Epi Initials theme reinterprets the historic LV Circle signature in a modern way to create a bold, distinctive look. Louis Vuitton's compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet, holding credit cards, bills and papers.

Inspired by our historical Congo bag, this messenger bag in Epi leather is a trendy yet discreet everyday bag. It’s signed with the classic LV circle signature first used on our trunks and reimagined for the Fall/Winter 2017 show.

This stylish version of Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet is part of the Epi Patchwork collection. The exterior combines blue and gray Epi leather with Damier Graphite canvas, while the interior features bright orange. Small enough to be slipped into a trouser pocket, this compact wallet offers a variety of credit card slots and compartments.

A perfect gift, this silk bandeau is printed with emblematic Louis Vuitton details - leather straps, metal chains and padlocks - on a background of the iconic Monogram pattern. This stylish accessory can be worn in many different ways.

The LV Stories bag charm and key holder features a cluster of colorful charms that echo the patches in the House's Leather Goods collection. The label and padlock graphics evoke Louis Vuitton's trunk-making heritage, while Monogram details add a classic touch. Fastened with a snap hook, this versatile piece can be used as a key holder or bag charm.

The Venice Card Holder is part of a seasonal leather goods collection which combines luminous Vernis Miroir patent leather with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas. This fresh, summery look complements the neat design of this practical card holder, which features slots for two credit cards.
Elegance is personified in the petite shape of the Pochette Metis. Made of supple Monogram empreinte leather, its compact dimensions open up to reveal many useful pockets and compartments.

The timeless Louis Vuitton Skyline reversible belt epitomizes the values of Louis Vuitton. The accessory can be worn two ways, either showcasing the iconic Damier Canvas on one side, or the soft calf leather on the other. A substantial metallic buckle is the centerpiece of this refined belt.
Louis Vuitton's Multiple wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts in an extremely compact format. It looks modern and elegant in emblematic Taiga leather, energized with bold contrasting edges.

The Zoé compact wallet looks chic in softly grained Monogram Empreinte leather, which is embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern. Small enough to fit into even a tiny bag or clutch, yet with space for coins, notes and credit cards, this neat wallet is the ultimate mini companion.

A variation on a classic Louis Vuitton design, the Reykjavik Gradient scarf features a refined gradation effect in two feminine colorways: pastel pink and blue or easy to match grey and black. Soft and warm in pure cashmere, this sophisticated scarf is woven using a jacquard technique to create a large-scale version of the iconic Monogram pattern.

With different designs on the front and flip sides, the pure-silk Pop Monogram bandeau offers lots of styling options. The Pop-inspired patterns – a key statement this season – feature Monogram Flowers mixed with dots and stripes. This skinny scarf wraps around neck, wrist, head or bag handle. It makes a fashionable gift.

The sweet Japanese treats known as “hanami” inspired the ultra-feminine details on this new Capucines model. The Monogram Flower is rendered in satin, lambskin and colorful beads, for a fresh, playful look that is totally in tune with spring silhouettes.

The Cherrywood compact wallet is distinguished by its unusual clasp, inspired by the locks traditionally used on Louis Vuitton trunks, and its combination of iconic Monogram canvas and smooth patent calf leather. This stylish design is also practical and space-efficient, offering an array of pockets and credit card slots within its compact dimensions.

Specifically designed for the iPhone 8+,this modern wallet in Damier Graphite canvas combines a purse, a card holder and a phone case in one playful and versatile package. The different elements can be detached, while the removable strap enables the wallet to be carried stylishly around the wrist.

This Zipped Tote is crafted from supple, high-gloss Monogram Glaze Eclipse, an innovative twist on the House’s signature coated canvas. Trimmed with natural cowhide and detailed with black metal hardware, this hybrid bag is equipped with two concealable straps that transform the tote into a body-friendly backpack. The roomy interior can hold a workday’s or weekend’s essentials.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity – and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket – is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

The House’s historic Karakoram pattern comes to the Bond Street handbag for Fall-Winter 2018. The bag’s classic Damier Ebene canvas is crossed by a bold zigzag stripe in Rubis red small-grained leather highlighted by a white border. This one-handled bag has a removable shoulder strap for multiple carrying options.

In supple Taiga leather, the discreet Clutch Kasaï can be carried under the arm or slipped around the wrist, thanks to its strap. Suitably compact yet practical with many sophisticated details, it delivers a refined, masculine look.

Stylish and cozy in cold weather, the Morningram two-in-one gloves come in pure wool in a chunky knit, and can be worn either as fingerless gloves or mittens. The design in black and beige features Louis Vuitton's Monogram Flowers and LV Circle signature. Team with the Morningram hat and scarf for a complete look.

An openwork metal frame gives these cat-eye sunglasses a striking, on-trend allure. The Midnight in Paris model is embellished with a host of subtle yet unmistakable House signatures, including engraved studs, Monogram Flower details and LV Circle emblems.

Inspired by the iconic studs from Louis Vuitton's trunks, this must-have bracelet is a twisted classic. Easy to customize with its replacement palladium and pink gold studs, it is the perfect go-to accessory.

A seasonal capsule of pure-silk squares, featuring screen-printed animal figures in three exclusive designs. Each is framed with a signature "trunk" motif and finished with oversized LV initials. These collectible pieces add a playful touch to work, weekend or dressy looks.
